	('prod_873971fc-e6df-4a46-ba68-57940a796078', 'wrist-watch-remote-control-mini-car-toy-for-kids-rechargeable-2-function-rc-car-with-usb-charging-cable', 'Wrist Watch Remote Control Mini Car Toy for Kids – Rechargeable 2 Function RC Car with USB Charging Cable', '<ul><li><p>WATCH RC CAR - This innovative toy combines a stylish wristwatch with a mini remote control car, allowing kids to carry their car anywhere. The transparent dome protects the car while doubling as a cool accessory, making playtime portable, exciting, and unique for children of all ages.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>SIMPLE 2 BUTTON CONTROL - Designed with beginner-friendly operation, the watch remote has just two easy-to-use buttons for moving the car forward or making turns. This simple control setup helps young kids enjoy driving fun without difficulty, boosting confidence and ensuring smooth operation for endless entertainment.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>USB CHARGING - This mini car supports USB charging. Watch car toy comes with built in 100mah rechargeable battery. The USB charging cable is included with the product. It can be connected to power outlet, computers and other commonly used USB devices to charge. Watch runs on 1 AAA battery (not included).</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>DURABLE AND CHILD SAFE - Made from high-quality, non-toxic materials, the toy car and watch are designed to withstand everyday play. Its safe, sturdy build ensures long-lasting durability, giving parents peace of mind while kids engage in safe, imaginative, and energetic racing adventures both indoors and outdoors.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>PERFECT GIFT FOR KIDS - Compact, lightweight, and entertaining, this watch car makes an excellent gift for birthdays, holidays, parties, and return gifts. Its interactive design encourages creativity and motor skills, keeping kids engaged for hours. Suitable for boys and girls, it’s an exciting and practical toy that brings endless joy.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 649, 'ht