	('prod_64cad7a5-c66c-4222-8e74-e3475af10c62', 'funny-milch-cow', 'Funny Milch Cow', '<p>Makes Perfect Sound. The Tail Shakes, The Legs Can Move Around. High quality, High performance, Walks around funny toy. Eyes With Light Head Makes Sound Non –toxic. Animal toy is an apt learning toy for your kids to spend time with and have fun. It not only just entertains your children, but also helps build their conscience by teaching them about the animal kingdom. It’s very easy to operate</p><p>Just install the AAA and turn on the switch, then you will enjoy the realistic sound, vivid color and high tech body movement.<br>This Cow toy is a great gift to inspire your kid’s creativity and imagination.<br>The glowing eyes and moving feet can quickly attract children’s attention and make they feel like a living Cow is coming towards them.</p>', 249, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/54165035-6f36-4456-b1fc-79e0652a121a.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 399}', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.622914+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.622914+00', 'cat_2e74411c-18bf-42c3-9e9d-4d86d22008d5', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/funny-milch-cow/17fc3592-adcf-4d17-8430-9ba43aa39def.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/54165035-6f36-4456-b1fc-79e0652a121a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0a412c91-5dd8-4d16-917f-3dfa7269944f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1d1dea1f-a87f-4a42-9214-7524f28bcf84.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c2bbfeb5-b14c-4860-9a11-14e69d40d4ce.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.023046134,0.0036242034,0.020609979,0.041608132,0.0678841,-0.0125191165,0.011368529,-0.01819219,-0.014785776,0.021581603,-0.005767144,0.008952128,0.04719203,-0.007535393,0.07877192,-0.031688616,0.01548398,-0.019811561,-0.061534557,-0.009726711,-0.01392825,0.025651174,0.02810394,0.06516797,0.017683694,-0.06078914,-0.034105048,0.042381655,0.062980056,-0.019700393,0.04874505,-0.016681328,-0.0034005758,0.047831118,-0.062110357,-0.053393055,-0.007177046,0.035590