	('prod_904c1766-6914-484a-9189-8c38901a1e15', 'beauty-set-suitcase-on-wheel-the-ultimate-beauty-set-on-wheels-for-girls-makeup-kit-is-easy-to-clean-and-use-portable-set', 'Beauty Set Suitcase On Wheel, The Ultimate Beauty Set On Wheels for Girls, Makeup Kit is Easy to Clean & Use, Portable Set', '<p>Make your little one feel like a real princess with this adorable and fun-filled <strong>Princess Vanity Playset</strong>. Designed to inspire creativity and imagination, this all-in-one beauty set provides hours of engaging role-play for kids.</p><p></p><p>💖 <strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p></p><p>✨ <strong>Charming Heart-Shaped Mirror</strong><br>A cute and stylish mirror that gives kids a magical princess-like experience.</p><p>💄 <strong>Complete Makeup &amp; Styling Kit</strong><br>Includes a realistic makeup palette, nail polish, perfume bottles, and hair styling tools for a full beauty setup.</p><p>👜 <strong>Cute Princess Handbag &amp; Accessories</strong><br>Comes with a portable handbag and a combo mirror &amp; comb set—perfect for on-the-go play.</p><p>🛠️ <strong>Easy Assembly &amp; Portable Design</strong><br>Quick and simple to assemble. Converts into a compact trolley case for easy storage and travel.</p><p>🪑 <strong>Strong &amp; Stable Structure</strong><br>Built with a sturdy base and durable materials to ensure safe and long-lasting use.</p><p>🎨 <strong>Encourages Creative Play</strong><br>Helps develop imagination, confidence, and role-playing skills in children.</p><p></p>', 899, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f83585e9-eaf5-4c2a-8795-fe3a53d0f3d5.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2026-04-01 06:30:28.673197+00', '2026-04-01 06:30:28.673197+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f83585e9-eaf5-4c2a-8795-fe3a53d0f3d5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dc1a494d-2235-48c3-9ddd-5f124a4087b8.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3f26f779-4a9e-4