	('prod_a20214f9-b649-4993-aef7-aff4a18c083f', 'gooyo-gaddi-remote-control-car-with-song', 'GOOYO Gaddi Remote Control Car with Song', '<p>Light up the race! The front LED lights offer a realistic touch to your driving adventures. Whether day or night, this toy car’s flashing headlights enhance the whole play experience.</p><p>This Gooyo remote control car toy is designed for smooth racing fun with forward, reverse, left, and right turns. Ideal for both inside and outdoor play, providing your children an exciting driving experience. The closed roof design enables immersive play experiences.</p><p>with its user-friendly remote controller, kids can steer this toy car in all directions. The Gooyo toy RC car provides a dynamic, fully functional experience whether it is racing forward, making tight curves, or reversing.</p>', 699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f0acd45c-f3cf-47aa-a3eb-e0124e9adee5.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 750}', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.996814+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.996814+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/gooyo-gaddi-remote-control-car-with-song/aed6e0f9-8eed-4d23-a87b-ac043747a65e.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f0acd45c-f3cf-47aa-a3eb-e0124e9adee5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/33b8410b-3acc-4d1d-b640-c05c298532d2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7116d71f-008a-4907-9548-4dbc14442c38.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.03317669,-0.029147774,0.013174525,-0.0037423458,0.05449061,0.017961219,0.07826175,0.021544006,-0.00810396,0.0063491524,0.026456548,0.023571802,0.029694725,-0.007844417,0.054481514,0.01808065,0.00027547797,0.044936325,0.018384492,-0.046123732,0.07686114,-0.019724727,0.0029135323,0.017632151,0.023873407,-0.0045853523,-0.000241571,0.052262716,-0.010390687,-0.025736572,0.0056376737,0.0069303573,0.04144576,-0.017262047,-0.0299511,-0.009802578,-0.035498004,0.0022940938,0.0061392826,-0.030191723,-0.03823509,0.063413054,0.