	('prod_48779740-edfd-48a7-8c3c-f4657fd8edda', 'remote-control-360-degrees-remote-control-car-gesture-watch-car-toy-gesture-sensing-rc-stunt-car-with-light-music', 'REMOTE CONTROL 360 Degrees Remote Control Car, Gesture Watch Car Toy, Gesture Sensing Rc Stunt Car with Light Music', '<p>Experience next-level fun with this advanced Remote Control Stunt Car designed for thrilling action and smart control. Equipped with 2.4GHz remote technology and innovative gesture control, kids can easily perform stunts, twists, and multi-directional movements.</p><p>This stunt car features 360° rotating wheels that allow it to drift, flip, and move sideways effortlessly. The built-in spray mist function combined with vibrant RGB LED lights creates a stunning visual effect, especially during night play.</p><p>Made with durable material and strong off-road tires, it can handle different surfaces smoothly. The intuitive remote includes functions like forward, backward, sideway driving, demo mode, music switching, and volume control for a complete interactive experience.</p><p>Perfect for kids who love action toys, this RC car enhances coordination, creativity, and motor skills while delivering endless entertainment.</p>', 2099, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b96c877e-409e-4360-8300-79901cf5cc37.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 3599}', '2026-04-15 13:02:35.328669+00', '2026-04-15 13:02:35.328669+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b96c877e-409e-4360-8300-79901cf5cc37.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/54a0937e-0113-4aaf-ba47-0d90d6a24378.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/51aee0e0-9e23-440d-ade7-9879405893cf.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/60a12cd9-6e32-440f-bf4f-e96bfff4cece.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/48bca48a-d461-459f-a429-269ae7dee427.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'High-speed RC stunt car with 360° spinning wheels, gesture control, spray mist effect, and colorful LE