	('prod_d1fe52bb-bf80-4828-b0f0-5c5728d7fa9f', 'toyotaa-land-cruiser-lc300-suv', 'Toyotaa Land Cruiser LC300 SUV', '<ul><li><p>Made of Fine Metal :- The Material of the car is used to give it absolutely clear finish.</p></li><li><p>High Quality :- Made of high quality zinc alloy material, Full metal body car which makes it very difficult to be damaged. Non-toxic water-based paint spray and doesn''t contain formaldehyde and any other harmful substances. Not easy to Wreck and scratches with the delicate touch.</p></li><li><p>Features :- The car model has the powerful functions, which the Childhood, tail and the doors can be opened. Also have the pull back function, you can pull back the car and then it will driving with strong Power. The simulation of the car makes the car look beautiful and cool!🏎️🎁</p></li><li><p>It can be used as a collection or gift for friends or family, Awesome gifts for your kids or your friends! Best choice for the car model.</p></li><li><p>Collectable Value: Reminiscence, hobbies cars by collection, original styling, wheels can rotate, best gift for adult collector.</p></li></ul>', 1049, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b4b5caf1-74fe-4de6-9e31-0a5e6d955de9.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1699}', '2025-12-28 10:59:22.086385+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:22.086385+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/toyotaa-land-cruiser-lc300-suv/00faa914-99bd-4c50-b059-2511d0d56995.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b4b5caf1-74fe-4de6-9e31-0a5e6d955de9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c992e028-5bc3-434c-85a2-8a9d8f17de5a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/28a046a6-c852-4076-af77-d21be88351cc.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7f29b268-d282-4def-a264-c34ee4eff6ae.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', 'https://youtu.be/BOq53MXMBwg', '[0.03176913,0.011522896,-0.00917366,-0.021973073,0.026226684,-0.011934334,0.0604614,0.01633829,-0.023309749,0.011407349,0.02007212,0.035199