	('prod_08d3cee1-fa19-4ada-b3f3-add59f2fcd31', '4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model', '4WD Off Road Die Cast Car Metal Model', '<ul><li><p>The Toyshine 1:24 4WD Off Road Die Cast is a toy car designed for children. It features a 1:24 scale and is designed to resemble an off-road vehicle. The toy car is made of die-cast metal, which makes it durable and resistant to damage.</p></li><li><p>One notable feature of this toy car is the opening doors, which add a realistic touch and allow children to play with the car more interactively. Additionally, the car is equipped with music and lights, which can make the playtime more engaging and exciting for children.</p></li></ul><p>The “4WD” designation suggests that the toy car has four-wheel drive capability, which may enhance its ability to navigate rough or uneven surfaces. This feature can make the play experience more adventurous and simulate off-road driving scenarios</p>', 1499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model/62212ac3-3f6d-48f8-9f3d-3aba8ceac860.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.15557+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.15557+00', 'cat_65960efd-3436-4822-89e6-6043c99610c3', 'col_3e7482c6-92fa-4798-9d71-b92e16e3f43b', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model/62212ac3-3f6d-48f8-9f3d-3aba8ceac860.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model/62212ac3-3f6d-48f8-9f3d-3aba8ceac860.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model/440549e4-bc3a-4b1a-be48-a1d9d4401b12.webp,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model/154531f5-f97b-4ecb-9a63-70b563c68e0d.webp,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model/c33551ea-00bf-4c91-b1d3-e5ea4b6c60e5.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model/cd0c3e54-f87c-43f4-9620-48fda6d6b9c2.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-off-road-die-cast-car-metal-model/73bf824d-2a01-