	('prod_73fc58cc-4cad-4e9a-9c1c-ce86838f7c3e', 'my-first-activity-book-a-busy-book-for-kids', 'My First Activity Book ( A Busy book For Kids )', '<p><strong>My First Activity Book – Interactive Fabric Busy Book for Kids (Age 2+)</strong></p><p>Make learning fun and engaging for your little ones with this soft <strong>fabric activity book</strong> specially designed for toddlers and preschool kids. This educational busy book helps children develop important early learning skills through interactive play.</p><p>The book includes colorful illustrations of animals, shapes, and everyday objects along with <strong>velcro-attached cut-outs</strong> that children can match and place on the correct page. This hands-on activity helps improve <strong>hand-eye coordination, object recognition, memory skills, and fine motor development</strong>.</p><p>Made from soft and child-safe fabric, the book is lightweight, durable, and easy for kids to handle. It keeps children entertained while also encouraging independent learning and creativity.</p><p>Perfect for <strong>home learning, travel activities, preschool preparation, and early education</strong> for kids aged <strong>2 years and above</strong>.</p><p></p><p></p><ul><li><p>Soft and safe <strong>fabric busy book</strong></p></li><li><p>Improves <strong>hand-eye coordination</strong></p></li><li><p>Helps develop <strong>fine motor skills</strong></p></li><li><p>Includes <strong>velcro matching cut-outs</strong></p></li><li><p>Bright and colorful learning pages</p></li><li><p>Suitable for <strong>toddlers (Age 2+)</strong></p></li></ul><p></p>', 599, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6c23b010-90c6-499b-8f85-f244dc544834.jpeg', 100, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2026-03-11 11:48:20.607839+00', '2026-03-11 11:48:20.607839+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6c23b010-90c6-499b-8f85-f244dc544834.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/produc