	('prod_fce09e3a-36ba-467c-9afc-236561adeb41', 'kids-walkie-talkies-toys', 'Kids Walkie Talkies Toys', '<ul><li><p>Easy to Use: With simple buttons and a push-to-talk feature, the walkie talkies are incredibly easy to use, making them the great toy for kids aged 3 and up. Locking in on a single channel, kids can have fun without any complex</p></li><li><p>Crystal Clear Communication: Advanced clear voice technology ensures that our child''s voice is always heard loud and clear. With non-static communication, the walkie talkies have a range of up to 1000 feet in ideal conditions, ensuring that kids always stay connected</p></li><li><p>Durable and Safe: Made from anti-fall ABS material, our walkie talkies can withstand drops of up to 5 feet, making it durable enough for our kids to use indoors and outdoors. Built-in lanyard hole makes our kids easy to carry their toys around with their favorite lanyard (Not lanyard included)</p></li></ul>', 850, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/36cad9de-7e50-407d-8e66-d9d1e4ac98c5.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1099}', '2025-12-28 10:59:13.390547+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:13.390547+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/kids-walkie-talkies-toys/da9bd9d1-b233-4ef1-8b0a-000909cb41c6.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/36cad9de-7e50-407d-8e66-d9d1e4ac98c5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b121ad2c-67af-422b-8d5c-5d19573db3e7.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a1e24efb-b98b-40c9-9f79-af96c27682db.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f3eeb9c3-9ded-428a-9844-3f73a311fe5a.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.056056272,-0.022426106,-0.047454607,-0.025999686,0.042911958,-0.0068267677,0.023464477,0.08170769,-0.00073310436,0.009229013,-0.01484898,-0.011876158,0.021973336,-0.04095469,0.07381598,-0.037392084,0.025626445,0.010473972,0.01173534,-0.019896546,-0.0075131785,-0.005347567,0.0015429803,0.02868918,-0.003831596,0.015399134,0.062317602,0.00872