	('prod_679542de-3301-489f-a7da-fa23e861b962', 'unicorn-soft-toy-for-babies-plush-toy-for-kids-cute-teddy-filled-soft-toy', 'Unicorn Soft Toy for Babies | Plush Toy for Kids Cute Teddy Filled Soft Toy', '<p>Cute unicorn soft toy pair with pastel blue and pink colors, made from ultra-soft plush fabric for kids and babies. Perfect stuffed unicorn dolls for nursery decor, gifting, and children’s bedroom decoration. High-quality plush unicorn toy set, safe, lightweight, and ideal for birthday and baby shower gifts. 🦄✨</p><p></p><ul><li><p>Cuddling Companion- The unicorn soft toy for kids is carefully crafted from a soft plush fabric, making it a perfect cuddling companion.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Sensory Development- The soft plush fabric of the cute unicorn soft toy enhances the sensory development of children and is gentle on little hands.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Imagination and Creativity- Children will strengthen their imagination and creativity as they will engage in pretend play, storytelling and create new adventures around the cute soft toy for kids.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fc780737-0f28-4e3d-a0b8-f6382924f218.jpeg', 0, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2026-01-28 05:03:06.409186+00', '2026-01-28 05:03:06.409186+00', NULL, 'col_3968e32f-f228-434a-9689-a07410b774d4', 'draft', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fc780737-0f28-4e3d-a0b8-f6382924f218.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/78c8167f-3124-4aef-8a90-7d72616f8302.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5ae9bc1f-0180-4253-973d-30872a99c262.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e8bb9a29-671c-4b99-bae9-4352abff06b5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/85c6c957-34c4-4813-be5e-0f266d69311c.jpeg}', 'inr', '', '', '', '[-0.047566935,-0.021352928,0.03517766,-0.008222231,0.061999187,-0.01681167,0.08520122,-0.005974151,-0.044924594,0.057825867,-0.006047717,-0.033832792,0.023530023,-0.055956364,0.055267394,0.0278617,-0.08614018,0.011437512,0.01329185,0.05655811,-0.075934