	('prod_9aa07458-424f-4551-a6de-dbeeb2c1cefe', 'gooyo-money-safe-piggy-bank', 'GOOYO Money Safe Piggy Bank', '<p>It is modern and stylish ATM Machine type toy cum saving bank with light and sound effects that make the savings game more enjoyable and fun. VGRASSP Piggy Bank toy is designed unique and very innovative to teach savings and management.<br>Combining modern technology with classic piggy bank functionality, the advanced security system offers peace of mind. Experience a unique and secure way to access your savings. The Gullak features a two-step unlocking process : Enter your number password then touch sensor for added security to open the door. This multi-layered approach ensures your money stays safe while adding an element of excitement.</p><p>A money bank toy is a fun and interactive way for kids to learn about saving money. It usually features a coin slot and a container for storing coins or bills, often with playful</p>', 799, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b7621839-f94c-4013-b4cd-ac291ad7be1c.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1099}', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.806293+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.806293+00', 'cat_06bc4112-ab3d-4f5a-a980-5d9ee0c2570c', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/gooyo-money-safe-piggy-bank/8330b3f5-1145-4a05-9e81-06f99b9a86c8.png', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b7621839-f94c-4013-b4cd-ac291ad7be1c.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9b8e0c21-c190-4a1c-ab98-07e9114041a5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/74175090-fd17-48de-a142-ce5a275a65fd.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3c994a65-0d4d-4af3-beee-d220ef0951af.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.02160394,-0.016142434,0.010087607,-0.0060893083,0.032508984,-0.0055632605,0.017364355,0.025118547,-0.028871564,0.012391194,0.030364012,-0.054761037,-0.014714065,-0.04129007,0.05255245,-0.029992325,-0.028840978,0.022008045,-0.03187969,-0.06565049,-0.06813494,0.013134402,-0.053022705,0.038966764,0.034254335,0.030011673,0.022016423,0.018191