	('prod_b3dac06c-8c6d-42b6-afc1-b1a17083eda8', 'f002-car-rider', 'F002 Car Rider', '<ul><li><p>Safe and secure: Sunny baby car Ride on ensures better safety prescribed for babies and toddlers; Heavy duty: The Sunny baby ride on toy has been designed in a way to handle weights of up to 15-20 kilograms. It is the ideal kids push toy for boys and girls ages 1-3</p></li><li><p>Made from durable materials: toy car is a very well-designed kids push car. Made using premium grade virgin PVC plastic material, it is completely non-toxic , ensuring a smooth ride for your little one every time</p></li><li><p>Convenient rear handle: Parents always prefer to be control of their kids safety. Keeping this in mind, the kids ride on baby toy has been designed with a solid rear handle, so that parents can steer the car and also enjoy easy transport</p></li><li><p>Dynamic steering controls: features a very responsive steering, which lets your baby steer the baby toy in any direction. Also, it comes with working horn buttons as well, along with a backrest for added driving comfort; Is Assembly Required: True</p></li><li><p>Theme: Animal</p></li></ul>', 949, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/16c7632e-34df-46bb-8b9f-28bfce2a07e1.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1500}', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.901502+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.901502+00', 'cat_956da411-a8cd-48ff-8b90-28c3e7b07e39', 'col_d27f16c3-8935-41d9-90af-5895ffef1e0c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/f002-car-rider/73e683b0-3a00-4250-8b84-009f57ab434e.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/16c7632e-34df-46bb-8b9f-28bfce2a07e1.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6a10f33f-df44-4c7d-b935-347794f94156.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/be71b213-09e0-4335-aebe-bb74966a3611.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6d1aad65-5dea-4950-891a-0983c205f64e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/25af71f3-1c6a-406b-baee-aef115deec91.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.015292861,-0.018769667,0.023674859,0.034055073,0.0726738,0.011732481,0.045600593