	('prod_ec69eb14-08b4-466a-a3e8-a495a830c3d3', 'face-mask-painting-kit-painting-kit-for-kids-create-your-own-customised-face-masks-using-paints-cool-funky-stickers-and-embellishments-diy-kits-for-kids-activity-kit-for-kids', 'Face Mask Painting Kit, Painting Kit for Kids', '<p>COMPLETE CONTENTS: This kit contains all the required material to decorate 3 Face Masks. It includes 3 White Face Masks, Paints, Glitter tubes, Paint Brush, Embellishments, Glitter foam stickers PERFECT FOR BEGINNERS: With all the material in one box, we have made it simple to make your own funky face masks. Use the material of your choice to create stunning face masks. FUN TO MAKE: This kit is a great activity to engage kids as well as adults and encourage the artist within them. Make cool face masks and flaunt the at carnivals, masquerades, theme parties, special events. DEVELOP SKILLS: The prime idea behind our DIY kits is to help develop very important skills in each kid along with a fun experience. This kit helps the child to increase FOCUS (by following each step with precision); encourage SELF EXPRESSION (by using the contents to create something unique), BOOST SELF ESTEEM by channelizing his/her energy into positive endeavors.</p><p><br></p>', 499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/face-mask-painting-kit-painting-kit-for-kids-create-your-own-customised-face-masks-using-paints-cool-funky-stickers-and-embellishments-diy-kits-for-kids-activity-kit-for-kids/7357d216-9755-4895-a1dc-87f5c2a78de0.webp', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 699}', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.184257+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.184257+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_dc923009-b2ef-4b9b-89fa-661db0df9b40', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/face-mask-painting-kit-painting-kit-for-kids-create-your-own-customised-face-masks-using-paints-cool-funky-stickers-and-embellishments-diy-kits-for-kids-activity-kit-for-kids/8f792e03-76b7-4aa0-8cde-99975188b98e.webp', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/face-mask-painting-