	('prod_bf9efec5-3b23-45b2-b723-13e47b507256', 'musical-guitar', 'Musical Guitar', '<ul><li><p>[ 4 Exciting Play Modes ] – This electric guitar features four unique modes, allowing kids to explore different sounds, rhythms, and musical effects, making playtime more engaging and entertaining.</p></li><li><p>[ Perfect for Young Beginners] – Specially designed for small hands, this guitar helps children easily learn basic strumming and rhythm skills, making it an excellent introduction to music.</p></li><li><p>[ Educational &amp; Creative Fun ] – Encourages early music learning, enhances hand-eye coordination, and fosters creativity while keeping kids entertained with fun melodies and interactive sounds.</p></li><li><p>[ Kid-Friendly &amp; Durable Design ] – Made with high-quality, child-safe materials, this lightweight and sturdy guitar is easy to hold and play, ensuring a safe and enjoyable experience for young musician</p></li></ul>', 899, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/43a206ec-e998-4ef9-82aa-c1712ddd41ae.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1099}', '2025-12-28 10:59:15.918199+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:15.918199+00', NULL, 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/43a206ec-e998-4ef9-82aa-c1712ddd41ae.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/43a206ec-e998-4ef9-82aa-c1712ddd41ae.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/e75fb98c-647b-45c3-b263-218e614b2e80.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/fe518bc7-e86f-45db-80be-c1a999e27e23.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/82cf7893-e1b5-487f-9a5c-869fbf37dbac.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/4d77575a-34c4-43c0-9225-9e749e947c51.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/530e4535-4266-4c10-b7c9-c61e10ad771a.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-guitar/efb1ca22-507b-4de2-93b3-df46f5547a23.jpg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.0014291597,0.015136672,0.02319994,0.009725248,-0.010259023,-0.00905