	('prod_47eb0b6b-e1fb-4194-9bcd-fbcc6ea3e562', 'cute-plush-doll', 'Cute Rabbit Plush Doll', '<ul><li><p>Ultra-Soft &amp; Huggable: Made from high-quality, plush materials, this bunny doll is perfect for snuggling and provides endless comfort</p></li><li><p>Perfect Size for Kids: The ideal size for little hands to hold and carry around, making it a great companion for naps, playtime, and bedtime</p></li><li><p>Safe &amp; Durable: Designed with safety in mind, this plush doll features securely stitched details and is made from non-toxic materials, ensuring it''s safe for all ages</p></li><li><p>Machine-washable and easy to clean with a damp cloth. Rich cotton filler and skin-friendly soft plush for a comforting touch</p></li><li><p>Ideal gift for children, couples, and friends. Provides comfort, companionship, and endless playtime fun.</p></li></ul>', 1399, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6046c559-0fca-497d-a0dd-14822faac108.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1800}', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.709073+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.709073+00', 'cat_aef0da25-a920-495d-af0a-9ce132e7c89c', 'col_3968e32f-f228-434a-9689-a07410b774d4', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/cute-plush-doll/2d8cdb3b-d8c6-4c17-a419-f105406ad95a.webp', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6046c559-0fca-497d-a0dd-14822faac108.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f63dd4a2-b8f3-4256-a5cb-a70ef02a6b06.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/082107eb-1cd8-48fd-ad19-2ab4e63edd23.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/56ff4639-ff45-406e-a7aa-d53bdf58d669.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.0664182,0.015038327,0.008714133,0.06047713,0.03628509,0.017192258,0.050985787,0.0007431633,-0.06346495,0.035887297,0.008945399,-0.008608725,0.026696552,-0.0007752038,0.081040226,-0.010302322,-0.09791081,-0.012075806,0.0030614098,0.006026612,-0.07091931,0.01820652,-0.0022292025,0.038449816,-0.02264168,0.030312546,-0.050117873,0.025115341,0.005659042,0.016093599,-0.014865332,-0.0035697655,-0.023684595,0.026777316,-0.005050064,0.03975576