	('prod_67f72561-2363-4897-913b-2dfda9a33e80', 'double-round-spinner', 'Double Round Spinner', '<ul><li><p>Double-Sided Flipping Magic Bean Toy : It is double-sided, adding more fun. It is suitable for all strong enough for children to play, and complex enough to arouse the interest of adults. You can move the beads freely with both hands and change the beads to different colors. and then let them return to the same color again color.</p></li><li><p>Operation Method : Carefully designed different O-shaped concave grooves, each groove has a number of small beads, which can move the small beads by pushing the middle module, disrupt the position of beads of different colors, then start thinking about how to match and restore the small beads of the same color in the same groove.</p></li><li><p>Product Features : The Rotating magic bean toy has grooves on both sides, colors of beads,and a horizontal axis moving in the middle. Disrupt the order of the beads of different colors, move the middle horizontal axis, and restore the beads of different colors to the same groove based on memory and spatial imagination. The puzzle and interesting gameplay can stimulate the brain to think, and exercise the coordination of hands, brain and eyes. It is a great educational toy.</p></li><li><p>3D Puzzle Toy : Magic Bean Cube Toys is also suitable for restlessness, anxiety, attention deficit, can help you relieve stress and anxiety. You can play with it anywhere anytime during travel, office, airport, or school to help you concentrate and stress relief. The stress relief toy with a variety of functions can keep your fingers busy, help you have a happy mood, help to concentrate and relax the body and mind</p></li><li><p>Material : The magic bean is made of high-quality ABS, and the overall shape is sleek, without sharp edges. There are a total of four colors on two sides, and the beads are firmly inlaid and will not fall off.</p></li><li><p>GIFT OPTION : Easter basket stuffers, Christmas 