	('prod_11c477b8-5250-4427-b527-79ee51537dc1', '1-24-scale-maybach-s600-pullman-car', '1:24 Scale Maybach S600 Pullman Car', '<p>Feature highlights:This&nbsp;1:24 scale alloy model die-cast car toy&nbsp;features&nbsp;doors opening, pull-back action, and sound and lights effects, crafted from ABS, zinc alloy, and rubber for durability. Suitable for kids aged 2 years and up, it comes in black and red color options with a compact product size of 21.5*6.5*5.5cm. The toy supports OEM/ODM customization, including logo and packaging design, ensuring versatility for buyers.&nbsp; 00000</p>', 1799, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3734116a-bd91-4fe3-9584-ef6cb238bef4.png', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2299}', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.266783+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.266783+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/1-24-scale-maybach-s600-pullman-car/295aafd9-6d69-4189-b37c-2bfd5207c040.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3734116a-bd91-4fe3-9584-ef6cb238bef4.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/160fa389-c989-474c-87b8-d46fe9b344eb.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/20fca89d-1835-46e4-aa7b-50f5dd2d735b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/463476e8-97cb-41e9-9d6c-3d3b58fcf9ab.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c1398831-9e88-4e2a-9f63-0d560b47d431.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.00994342,0.06285026,0.028584903,-0.023944968,-0.008602933,-0.019958908,0.01786211,-0.00555083,0.07425328,0.022257892,0.0053267023,-0.013633368,-0.0034802158,-0.010393393,0.030347113,0.013155577,0.021328824,0.004738833,-0.0030026478,-0.030509222,0.07284944,0.024688773,0.0067365686,-0.009936162,-0.012553,-0.015725616,0.0346011,-0.01005259,-0.015265813,-0.018226383,0.02516347,0.016009746,-0.0029784215,-0.0062822765,-0.07438663,0.002985114,-0.01417597,0.010860997,-0.020338736,0.07967476,-0.01184424,0.02736547,0.0077937976,-0.05166288,0.021713642,-0.018546434,0.050017815,-0.013749176,0.059497625,0.025420053,-0.08682