	('prod_26564a2f-2ee7-431b-b209-30f9c03d45bb', 'mini-alloy-mini-ev-coper-1-32-car', 'mini alloy Mini EV coper 1.32 car', '<p>This 1:28 Scale DC Metal Diecast EV Car Model is a premium collectible and toy designed for both kids and adults. It features a metal alloy body, openable doors, working headlights and taillights, and a charging station setup for pretend play. The car also includes a mini bicycle mounted on the roof, giving it a sporty and realistic look. With sound effects and pull-back action, this model provides a fun and engaging experience. Whether you’re buying it as a gift, collection piece, room décor, or toy, it stands out with impressive detailing. Perfect for birthdays, return gifts, car lovers, and EV enthusiasts!</p><p></p>', 699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/12e47c57-8efe-46e7-b516-95499d39f98b.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:16.458867+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:16.458867+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mini-alloy-mini-ev-coper-1-32-car/ca3fa750-c509-4bfe-8265-3eea2b1862e8.webp', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/12e47c57-8efe-46e7-b516-95499d39f98b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4bb82dff-65c8-4ab4-b372-4f274b17bac4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c8586c39-0c3f-4113-b73b-db42ff34b428.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2c419648-dd33-4739-b08e-18650686f5d5.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.04000926,0.022791041,-0.018955028,0.027069202,0.006711648,-0.012602492,0.0626678,0.014065088,-0.04709959,0.026006646,0.0006213608,0.0052191042,0.010218961,0.00020274764,0.06834979,0.00821525,-0.0112977605,0.049758147,0.013264597,-0.046458866,0.059063997,0.015016588,-0.007895225,0.011584404,-0.016409151,0.026138695,0.015815733,0.020005036,-0.016834896,0.006044517,0.041250087,-0.00015906944,-0.010088852,0.0014718903,-0.055348486,-0.01579504,-0.008263927,0.024373043,-0.0059157517,0.040457353,-0.010742662,0.017576458,0.002670539