	('prod_74d1cb05-52ac-48a0-8c9f-705dc5ce6feb', '1-32-ram-mammoth-pick-up-model-car', '1:32  RAM Mammoth Pick-Up Model Car', '<ul><li><p>This 1:32 scale model features fully functional doors, hood, and trunk, along with realistic engine sounds and lights activated by pressing the front wheels. Opening the doors illuminates the front and rear lights, enhancing the authentic experience. The pull-back action allows the car to zoom forward for hours of fun. Made from durable die-cast metal, it''s built to last and perfect for collectors and car enthusiasts of all ages.</p></li><li><p>Ideal for gifting to children or friends, this model car creates cherished memories of thrilling playtime. It''s also a wonderful collectible, perfect for displaying in your home or office.</p></li><li><p>Our model car boasts an intricately detailed interior with exquisite workmanship, including a simulated cab, steering wheel, and dashboard that replicate real car details for a superior experience. The four-door design enhances interactivity, with realistic sound and light effects triggered by pressing the front wheels or opening the doors. Additionally, the pull-back functionality allows the car to slide forward after being pulled back, providing engaging and dynamic play.</p></li><li><p>Joy Junction is a premium brand dedicated to offering top-quality Educational and Child Development Toys on Amazon. Established in 2023, we have consistently upheld our commitment to delivering high-quality products that inspire and educate. Our vision is to become a beloved household name in the toy industry, known for excellence and reliability. We are deeply grateful to our customers for their unwavering support and trust, which have been instrumental in our growth and success.</p></li></ul>', 1149, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d939f769-6beb-4a48-b674-1aed6c31c23e.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1500}', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.007335+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.007335+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-4