	('prod_bd1de985-5228-48a7-a3a0-334d06dd071d', 'chanak-premium-doctor-set-trolley-for-kids-pretend-play-doctor-set-trolley-for-kids-above-3-years-doctor-kit-for-boys-and-girls', 'Chanak Premium Doctor Set Trolley for Kids,  Pretend Play Doctor Set Trolley for Kids Above 3 Years, Doctor Kit for Boys & Girls', '<ol><li><p>Innovative Stethoscope: Chanak’s Doctor Set contains a brand-new and unique stethoscope. It makes the sound of a heartbeat when pressed against the body. It comes with an attractive LED light along with a heartbeat sound. These unique features will make our doctor set your child’s favorite playtime toy.</p></li><li><p></p></li></ol><ul><li><p>Imaginative play: Chanak Kids doctor kit encourage imaginative play, which is important for children''s cognitive and social development. Children can pretend to be a doctor or a nurse and use medical tools to diagnose and treat imaginary patients. These tools with LED lights will keep the kids occupied for hours.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Contents: The Doctor Set contains 10 pieces including a stethoscope, tweezers, autoscope, thermometer, hammer, scissors, eyeglasses, etc. Our aim is to educate the kids with all the modern doctor tools.</p></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><p>2-in-1 design: Trolley + Doctor Table</p></li><li><p>12+ medical toy accessories</p></li><li><p>Safe &amp; durable ABS plastic</p></li><li><p>Easy to carry with wheels &amp; handle</p></li><li><p>Encourages role-play &amp; learning</p></li><li><p>Perfect gift for kids</p></li></ul><p></p>', 899, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5f62bc1a-d10e-4624-a213-40b92b640308.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2026-04-01 05:51:01.325248+00', '2026-04-01 05:51:01.325248+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5f62bc1a-d10e-4624-a213-40b92b640308.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7ccc66cf-bcd8-4ce1-948a-a19dcf3a0725.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/p