	('prod_47d8a3d8-3246-467e-a469-13711e4e3ec7', 'h6-hoverboard', 'H6 HOVERBOARD', '<p>FREE ACCESSORIES – Free Carry Bag, Charger, and Remote with the Product.</p><p>START-UP BALANCE 2.0 – Assists in Balancing the Hoverboard with the 5th GEN Control Board</p><p>BLUETOOTH ENABLED – Play Music while riding with a built-in speaker</p><p>LED FLASH WHEEL – Attractive-looking LED Wheel Hub Motor with Cool LEDs.</p><p>PLUS SPECIAL – Bigger Battery (20% More than H6 Classic) and Lifting Handle and More Motor Power with More Load Taking Capability.</p><p>POWERFUL PERFORMANCE – Race up to 15km/h and climb inclines up to 20 Degrees</p><p>FOR ALL RIDERS – Perfect for all Ages 7+ and up to 90kg Load<br><br></p><p>WEIGHT: 9 KG</p><p>DIMENSIONS: 65 × 23 × 23 CM</p><p>STARTUP BALANCE 2.0: YES</p><p>CONTROL BOARD: FIFTH GENERATION SUPER INTELLIGENT CONTROL PANEL WITH US-BASED ST CHIPSETS – AUTO BALANCE</p><p>BATTERY: 108WH 36V WITH QUICK CHARGE 2.0 BATTERY MANAGEMENT SYSTEM</p><p>MOTOR: 200W X 2 DUAL MOTORS – DOUBLE TORQUE (100% COPPER)</p><p>TYRE: 6.5" SOLID RUBBER TUBELESS TYRE</p><p>CHARGING TIME: QUICK CHARGE 2.0 (1-2 HOURS MAX)</p><p>MAXIMUM SPEED: 15KM/H (AS PER USER WEIGHT LOAD)</p><p>MAX LOAD CAPACITY: 90KG</p><p>MINIMUM LOAD: 15KG</p><p>BLUETOOTH: YES (PLAY MUSIC BY CONNECTING WITH ANY BLUETOOTH DEVICE)</p><p>FRONT LEDS: YES</p><p>REAR LEDS: NO</p><p>WHEEL ARCH LEDS: YES</p><p>BATTERY INDICATOR: YES</p><p>LED WHEEL: YES</p><p>REMOTE: YES</p><p>BAG: YES</p><p>GRADABILITY: 20 DEGREES</p><p>MATERIAL: SOLID ALUMINIUM MAIN FRAME + ABS BODY</p><p>NET WEIGHT: 11KG</p><p>DELIVERY TIME: READY STOCK – SAME DAY QUICK DISPATCH (SHIPPING TIME 2-4 BUSINESS DAYS)</p><p>GROUND CLEARANCE: 46MM</p>', 10999, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/h6-hoverboard/623d75bf-5242-4393-9045-bbbe269b36a6.webp', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 13999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.789048+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.789048+00', NULL, 'col_d27f5db1-f6f6-4565-b0da-885ae6a4e45c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/h6-hover