	('prod_83959fac-72f6-452e-b59a-3be281d1fd66', 'water-turtle-toy', 'WATER TURTLE TOY', '<p>Bath Toys Water Toys for Kids Bath Cute Swimming Bath Toys for Toddlers 1-3 Year Boy Girl</p><p>About this item<br>💦 Wind Up and Let Go: Wind up the Bath Toys, then put swimming toys for kids into water to see they flapping their flippers and propelling themselves through the water, making your little ones giggle with glee.<br>💦 Make Bath Fun&amp; Interesting: Only happy without crying! Kids always prefer to choose the brightly colored bath toys! Bright colors help to train children''s ability to distinguish colors, exercise the baby''s hands activity and improve the coordination of hands and brain ; Also assists with development of cognitive ability and an understanding of physical buoyancy.<br>💦Use with Confidence: The Baby Bath Toy is powered by hand turning.Water swimming toys for kids can swim around in the water, no batteries needed, and the smooth edge won’t hurt your baby’s hands.<br>💦Great for Play Anywhere: This baby bath toys are great both for in or out of the water; You can play with swimming turtle bath toy in the bathtub, pool, beach or even just on the floor.The cool thing is that you can take it with you when you play at the beach, it will be a multifunctional water toy.<br>💦 Let Baby Enjoy Bath -- Only happy without crying!The bath tub toys for baby boy could be a good way to divert your baby''s attention and allow them to enjoy water. Whether bathing or swimming, let your child splash with the tortoise team.<br></p>', 119, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6ebb8ef6-9a7e-4027-aa8f-6a23a3163f49.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 169}', '2025-12-28 10:59:20.873503+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:20.873503+00', 'cat_5ae74dd4-6a65-47ae-a155-00434fc18e2a', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/water-turtle-toy/8cb83197-10a1-4732-998f-2e27e120ecd8.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6ebb8ef6-9a7e-4027-aa8f-6a23a3163f49.jpeg,h