	('prod_f7a15dbf-d4d1-455b-855b-0f40b77e851e', 'alpha-numeric-puzzle-game', 'Alpha Numeric Puzzle Game', '<p>EARLY LEARNING MADE FUN – Introduce your toddler to the world of letters and numbers with this vibrant Alpha Numeric Puzzle, designed to make learning exciting and interactive for kids aged 2 years and above…..<br>26 LETTERS &amp; 10 NUMBERS – Includes all uppercase alphabets (A-Z) and numbers (0-9) in bright, eye-catching colors that help children easily identify and memorize shapes….<br>SAFE &amp; CHILD-FRIENDLY MATERIAL – Crafted from high-quality, non-toxic materials with smooth, rounded edges to ensure safe play for little hands…..<br>PERFECT GIFT CHOICE – An ideal educational gift for birthdays, holidays, preschool activities, and return gifts, loved by parents and teachers alike…..<br>DEVELOPS ESSENTIAL SKILLS – Encourages fine motor development, hand-eye coordination, color recognition, and early literacy and numeracy skills…..</p>', 269, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/alpha-numeric-puzzle-game/13005e3c-b534-4294-a65f-ccbb920ded0c.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 350}', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.560405+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.560405+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/alpha-numeric-puzzle-game/d28f2a30-3d6b-4682-8615-41446c37f03e.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/alpha-numeric-puzzle-game/13005e3c-b534-4294-a65f-ccbb920ded0c.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/alpha-numeric-puzzle-game/58c50589-536c-44da-87de-a44145ff91e5.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/alpha-numeric-puzzle-game/4863207b-7989-4a56-bf77-d3e3ffe7ed92.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/alpha-numeric-puzzle-game/7bddbca1-d023-46df-a371-8bd18c0d573f.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/alpha-numeric-puzzle-game/ece8149f-0b1c-4def-b5a2-0a4fce1496bd.jpg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.041817058,-0.004985485,-0.0067890664,-0.022275146,0.004342933,0.008933552,0.006816241,0.044765856,0.04878463,-0.