	('prod_3ba9d813-5a84-41c2-ab98-d20cf7a9d49d', 'dancing-crab-toy', 'DANCING CRAB TOY', '<p>Decor style Crawling Crab Baby Musical Kids Toy Dancing Crawling Baby Toys Crawling Crab Toy for Kids Learning Educational Toys for Kids Boys and Kids Girls<br></p><p>Electric Crawling Crab Toy: These decorative crawling crab toys transform your child''s tummy time into a delightful and joyful experience. With vibrant colors, sparkling lights, cheerful music, and sideways movement, they captivate babies aged 3 and up, drawing their attention. Babies adore the music, enthusiastically moving their arms and legs in sync with the rhythm. This toy makes an ideal gift for your little one.<br>Premium Quality Material: Crafted for children aged 3 years and older, this walking crab toy caters to toddlers, infants, boys, and girls, offering entertainment across a broad age spectrum. Constructed from non-toxic ABS plastic, this toy guarantees safety during play and is designed for enduring durability.<br>Sensing Crawling Crab: This crab toy is equipped with an electric crawling feature that enables it to move sideways, imitating the natural movement of a real crab. Activated by cheerful songs, the walking crab baby toy crawls joyfully; when it encounters obstacles, it autonomously changes direction, captivating babies who enjoy chasing after it. Moreover, it encourages infants to sit up and engage in extended play sessions, fostering exploration and development.<br>Rechargeable Battery: This toy is powered by a dependable 3.7V lithium battery, providing extended playtime for your children. With a built-in rechargeable battery, it offers convenience and eliminates the hassle of frequent battery changes.<br>Built-in Light &amp; Sound: Featuring vibrant lights and engaging sound effects, this crab toy provides a multisensory experience that enhances enjoyment and excitement. Tailored for children aged 3 years and older, this walking crab toy is suitable for toddlers, infants, boys, and girls, ensuring entertainment across a broad age group. &nbsp;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', 699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a5d15858-11fb-430a-acc9-337dd3d66838.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.307252+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.307252+00', 'cat_1ff574c2-bfb1-4b77-b9c7-ae54ed7fa4e5', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/dancing-crab-toy/c874764f-b0cb-404c-b8b9-d9d6f8f4557a.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a5d15858-11fb-430a-acc9-337dd3d66838.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a179c1a5-8e4a-406c-84c6-d00ce272d4a9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f67d85ba-d313-404c-95f2-7850838e7f24.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/bc2ca4c6-2ef1-4215-ac26-d2005d14dd22.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8205f400-1fab-42a0-82e3-d5346a0dbf28.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6ae8727e-af2a-4098-b9dd-a81474fb75e2.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.028304843,-0.052425694,0.024965957,-0.027445395,0.043536127,0.0106195,0.030340074,0.05142395,0.007553578,0.012441746,0.021105712,0.030573508,0.02769746,-0.01801282,0.021959845,-0.009701872,0.016333753,0.049695197,0.001829768,-0.0020111674,-0.033166457,-0.015150364,-0.005471436,0.06404537,-0.03504266,-0.015735038,-0.013370014,-0.026511714,0.00035472473,0.008054214,0.00869388,-0.02679302,-0.0013179509,0.027779728,-0.06349881,-0.043808322,-0.04257338,0.02514831,0.082986765,-0.021855636,-0.003015141,0.06572874,0.007174237,-0.0023779226,0.03113824,-0.108462505,0.05526211,-0.046463136,-0.03309277,0.062423967,-0.011934896,0.013793244,-0.018132944,-0.006028728,-0.07634089,-0.05028574,0.023926215,0.0048198034,0.02213499,-0.029655084,0.084769696,-0.047901828,-0.05223858,0.012572837,-0.0004703953,0.01122414,0.01690449,0.107368134,0.008750877,-0.0027120162,-0.020905951,-0.08049655,-0.016088935,-0.0102261305,-0.027612947,-0.015908973,0.01135939,0.0005006095,-0.011536603,0.010050589,0.030576192,0.0017009348,-0.02969662,-0.04353966,0.006032704,-0.0014975225,0.06518165,-0.