	('prod_7bd9859a-f73d-4d6e-bf4c-79e255e3e1c1', 'mini-projector', 'Mini Projector', '<p>• “Safe and high-quality materials： It is made of high-quality ABS environmentally friendly materials, and the smooth edges will not harm children’s small hands. Easy to use. The slide rail can be replaced by simply sliding the plastic cover.”<br>• “sleep companion for children: The children’s slide projector is composed of multiple modes and is easy to use. You only need to pull the plastic cover to replace the slide, then insert the selected disc and rotate or adjust the disc to observe the projected image.”<br>• “Children’s slide projector: Unlike most projectors on the market, our projectors have more pictures and more vivid colors. 24 different pictures and 3 groups of themes.”<br>• “Early education of toys and sleep stories ：Let children understand common sense of optics. The projected images at different distances will look different, which is amazing!”<br>• “NOTE: Random colors with random slides will be sent as per availability.”</p>', 99, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9c50ed6c-07e4-42d2-9dbf-90c59295a1fb.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 149}', '2025-12-28 10:59:16.363867+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:16.363867+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_04bb80c5-eeb4-4ae7-bfdd-2c8f71f76f95', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mini-projector/67f0e570-518a-4498-b30a-b43deb135c37.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9c50ed6c-07e4-42d2-9dbf-90c59295a1fb.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dc7182af-6165-4723-a680-179da850f937.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6f5ad773-f2ce-4060-8242-452afb2d405a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fbb0399f-8b5e-4aa4-a07a-f7818ce96dc4.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.023312684,-0.0035775078,-0.0029230549,0.017591933,0.008188017,-0.013945941,-0.012179075,0.06103133,-0.03236472,0.03176692,0.004190069,0.0068501537,0.021026932,-0.024710402,0.023079865,-0.012757957,-0.03720105,0.0067336564,0.01107125,-0.048190605,-0.029163532,-