	('prod_b4727265-92aa-487a-a869-fbf0a354b725', '1-32-scale-bwm-i8-model-car', '1:32 Scale BWM i8 Model Car', '<ul><li><p>Durable Die-Cast Metal Body: Made from high-quality alloy with some plastic parts for added detailing, this toy car features a sturdy, realistic build designed to last.</p></li><li><p>Pull-Back Action Toy Car: Easy to operate just pull back and release. The smooth motion and controlled speed make it safe and fun for young children.</p></li><li><p>Realistic Lights and Sounds: Equipped with front and rear LED lights and realistic engine sounds that activate when doors are opened, creating an engaging play experience.</p></li><li><p>Openable Doors and Hood: Both the doors and hood can be opened, allowing kids to explore the interior and enjoy an authentic model car feel.</p></li><li><p>Ideal Gift for Kids &amp; Collectors: Perfect for birthdays, Christmas, or return gifts. This car’s lifelike features, sounds, and lights make it a favorite among kids and collectors alike.</p></li><li><p>Suitable For Birthday and Christmas Gifts: The sound of model will sound like an engine sound, there is no doubt that the cool car model will attract children''s attention. Perfect gifts for kids</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1149, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d23b2613-a46b-4e0e-84b4-9f3d8d0d130a.png', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:03.579153+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:03.579153+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/1-32-scale-bwm-i8-model-car/b48203b5-74db-460f-89e8-e47ff9494a16.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d23b2613-a46b-4e0e-84b4-9f3d8d0d130a.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7b3fe8a2-38f8-4db1-ad22-c780ae53996f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e3f1c5bd-b3a2-4b70-81ed-04aed1686f6f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1178ea09-304d-47b5-a4ce-079ec761c22d.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.0028610772,0.00032245435,-0.02372407,0.005333438,0.0541