	('prod_b72f7f3b-a066-4644-8426-374960581ead', 'musical-rescue-helicopter', 'MUSICAL RESCUE HELICOPTER', '<p><strong>Product information :</strong></p><p>Toy Simulation Helicopter Die Cast Playset Planes Toy for Early Learning Age 3+ White Contemporary Manufacture</p><p>Equipped With Multiple Early Education Contents: 16 Nursery Rhymes, 2 Stories, Airplane Sound Effects<br>All Kinds Of Simulated Aircraft Parts Are More Realistic; Including: Cockpit, Propeller, Sliding Door, Night Light, Lifeline, Tail, Inertia Wheel, And Early Education Button, Etc.<br>Flashing Lights In The Dark Night: Soft Light, The Baby Is No Longer Afraid Of The Dark Night; The Night Navigation Light Can Be Turned To Emit A Variety Of Lights<br>Inertia Wheels, No Motor Required, More Fun To Drive<br>Made Of Abs, Safe And Durable, Educational Gift For Boys And Girls Over 3 Years Old.</p><p>Number of Puzzle Pieces &nbsp; &nbsp;‎1<br>Assembly Required &nbsp; &nbsp;‎No<br>Batteries Included &nbsp; &nbsp;‎No<br>Material Type(s) &nbsp; &nbsp;‎Abs Plastic<br>Colour &nbsp; &nbsp;‎White<br>Recommended age ‎24 months - 10 years</p>', 649, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cbac7ca2-2423-4ea4-bce8-a35517bb5078.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 799}', '2025-12-28 10:59:17.95082+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:17.95082+00', 'cat_e8d304ee-124d-409f-b02f-9a0b6824b9de', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-rescue-helicopter/56857234-6b90-4183-b2c6-e6b11ae07543.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cbac7ca2-2423-4ea4-bce8-a35517bb5078.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/78769471-e112-473b-95fa-3fa84d1552b6.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/81812438-953d-42f7-93b0-edc862ab90bf.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ad45003c-5fb1-4806-84c5-38ce828e16d7.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.093005605,-0.048353493,0.030212417,0.07318557,0.019651571,0.0005131407,0.06724839,0.02257913,0.03542716,0.027446758,0.046341196,-0.0026219208,0.027012406,-0.03131304,0.07385942,-0.037