	('prod_14bce3ee-5f3f-45b6-92fe-7e5992b0081f', 'mandala-art-kit', 'Mandala Art Kit', '<ul><li><p>&nbsp;OUR ARTS AND CRAFTS KIT FOR KIDS is suitable for AGES 7+ With ready-to-paint coasters,is it very easy to do Painting with the help of a color set, paintbrush, and color kit provided with the craft set.</p></li><li><p>DIY KIT FOR KIDS This painting kit brings you to know more about Mandala Art and it pulls out your passion for painting. Painting your own Coasters becomes a unique and meaningful art set.</p></li><li><p>These Mandalas can painted or filled in with paints and then sprayed with a sealer or lacquer to be used as custom coasters. If you do not ‘seal’ the color before using it as a coaster, condensation could cause the colors to bleed or rings to appear in the wood.</p></li></ul>', 449, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mandala-art-kit/be752c3e-d327-43c2-9bc2-9b0d2de25467.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2025-12-28 10:59:16.017048+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:16.017048+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mandala-art-kit/240e245d-fd77-44d0-bef9-e7be8a798813.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mandala-art-kit/be752c3e-d327-43c2-9bc2-9b0d2de25467.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mandala-art-kit/80e6fd4c-e772-4263-bc30-0ce4f82a09df.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mandala-art-kit/597eb4f9-b536-46a9-bcce-ce07804e404c.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mandala-art-kit/0530629e-f6e8-443d-8ee7-881316f7cf19.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mandala-art-kit/55197d2e-5b05-486b-ab65-cad58feb7692.jpg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.0032469565,0.00998182,0.016053107,0.012616832,-0.0112002455,-0.01514199,-0.03410203,0.03746769,0.006417455,0.019359142,0.03080254,0.009614928,-0.015764633,0.0076647014,-0.02267383,-0.039560772,0.039675154,0.024051387,-0.040919717,-0.028169813,-0.016221428,0.022542575,-0.027949108,0.003527736,-0.03577262,0.014644227,-0.038259912,-0.013864792,