	('prod_154fcea7-6d3f-4b35-aaa7-38eb7938091b', 'musical-piano', 'Musical Piano', '<ul><li><p>Interactive Musical Fun – Equipped with multiple buttons that play melodies, illuminate keys, and guide kids to play. The built-in microphone lets children sing along, making music time more engaging and enjoyable.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>Educational &amp; Developmental – Enhances hand-eye coordination, auditory skills, and creativity. Guided key illumination helps kids learn rhythm, melody, and musical memory while encouraging interactive play.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>Interactive Melodies &amp; Key Illumination – The Musical Note and Headphones Button play short and long melodies with illuminated keys, while the Piano Button produces a piano tune, helping kids recognize sounds and develop musical skills.</p></li><li><p>Guided Play &amp; Singing Fun – The Conductor &amp; Arrow Buttons light up keys to guide kids in interactive play, encouraging them to follow along. The Microphone &amp; Plus Button allows volume adjustment and microphone control for an engaging singing experience.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>Kid-Friendly &amp; Safe Design – Made from durable, child-safe materials, with a lightweight design perfect for little hands to play comfortably and safely.</p></li><li><p>Perfect for Young Learners &amp; a Great Gift Choice – Designed for kids 18 months and older, this fun and educational musical toy introduces rhythm, melody, and interactive music learning. It makes an ideal gift for birthdays and special occasions, providing hours of entertainment and musical exploration.&nbsp;</p></li></ul>', 1249, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7b65ac94-83cf-4aee-80dd-0f0119166a55.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1499}', '2025-12-28 10:59:17.128123+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:17.128123+00', 'cat_e8d304ee-124d-409f-b02f-9a0b6824b9de', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/musical-piano/c27537f1-2ef1-430e-9bd5-e93026a33848.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in