	('prod_afa5d5cb-aac1-4446-9be4-0251eb445345', 'cartoon-plane', 'CARTOON PLANE', '<p>Toys Push n Pull Mini Aeroplane to Converting Transforming Robot Toy For Kids are Made from non toxic and safe material, enhances creativity and imagination.Develops Eye Hand Coordination and Motor Skills.Helps in learning and recognizing colors and shapes.<br>• SPARK YOUR CHILD’S IMAGINATION-Let your kids enrich their intelligence and imagination with this educational toy.Understanding how things work is one of the best parts of the game.<br>• SHAPE RECOGNITION – Getting to know the different shapes that exist not only expands their knowledge of shapes, but also helps develop fine motor skills and their spatial recognition.<br>• COMPACT SIZE: Perfect dimensions for small hands to grip and play with, making it ideal for toddlers and young children</p>', 149, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/04fb4439-bc33-42a6-9c19-c4ae7e3c575f.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 250}', '2025-12-28 10:59:08.3207+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:08.3207+00', 'cat_65d2f8ce-019c-463c-b266-45616a6d092b', 'col_add0b190-2d6f-4576-99cd-1b94a7d0f0af', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/cartoon-plane/bb3e9f3f-92f2-4c1d-9c80-5abb1fd64bee.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/04fb4439-bc33-42a6-9c19-c4ae7e3c575f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/51f2b0bc-ab74-4d42-a45e-30730ca33c88.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b6f66b3f-b50a-4e28-ba99-13b1c25a9af2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0c736bae-110e-4114-a4b3-1b67ca0c8ce5.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.0383583,-0.023797804,0.034971204,-0.019655284,0.03679864,0.014671555,0.061604798,0.029002361,-0.053382445,0.011217337,0.02954707,-0.021948472,-0.011227115,-0.0013323306,0.01916318,-0.0077009113,-0.011799492,0.015891865,-0.0010069574,0.0068046786,-0.0759904,0.011062742,-0.013242268,0.08405554,-0.028140085,0.020362359,0.0121593075,0.035810024,0.0093916515,-0.022427734,0.04804356,0.0052499045,0,-0.003438961,-0.045285087,-0.026255138,-0.021579623,0.050747205,-0