	('prod_51ecf0d4-ad6a-4ae2-96e4-767733978287', 'birds-jigsaw-puzzle-game', 'Birds Jigsaw Puzzle Game', '<ul><li><p>Ratnas Jigsaw Puzzle for Kids above 2+ Years: Engaging brain-boosting activities for children aged 3 and up, offering fun challenges and opportunities for learning.</p></li><li><p>Whether you enjoy the challenge of a good puzzle or you want to keep your mind sharp, our jigsaw puzzles for kids and adults are the way to go! The puzzle can help to improve problem-solving skills and memory, boost focus and attention, and promote hand-eye coordination.</p></li><li><p>The trial and error involved will teach the children to be patient and develop problem-solving skills.</p></li><li><p>A wonderful way to sharpen one’s mind and focus. A fun activity alone or with family and friends.</p></li><li><p>Superior Quality: The product is made with good quality materials and printed using non-toxic inks.</p></li></ul>', 99, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/birds-jigsaw-puzzle-game/21561234-13ac-42f1-8e09-3276abcbc5fa.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 199}', '2025-12-28 10:59:06.925362+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:06.925362+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/birds-jigsaw-puzzle-game/9a7212b9-3bee-4ca3-9f0c-8e9d649d3ed0.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/birds-jigsaw-puzzle-game/21561234-13ac-42f1-8e09-3276abcbc5fa.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/birds-jigsaw-puzzle-game/5f0cbd07-e29c-4291-a942-a473af5be3af.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/birds-jigsaw-puzzle-game/31e74301-72d7-4d00-a350-66620965ad09.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/birds-jigsaw-puzzle-game/9a7212b9-3bee-4ca3-9f0c-8e9d649d3ed0.jpg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.032550562,0.017699433,0.05013404,-0.028770205,0.01693692,-0.0051494436,0.022205345,0.029511312,-0.017754247,0.07534567,-0.069174446,0.015460576,-0.0512239,-0.048645858,0.032667167,0.020435568,-0.0002783423,0.009082446,-0.049568024,0.01866412,-0.0223328