	('prod_38c3f1c4-375a-4b0c-8d4f-e4f693baa402', 'magnetic-drawing-board-for-kids-80-pcs-educational-toy-zuppy-megnetie-board', 'Magnetic Drawing Board for Kids – 80 PCS Educational Toy ( Zuppy Megnetie Board )', '<p><strong>Magnetic Drawing Board for Kids – 80 PCS Educational Creative Toy</strong></p><p>Let your child explore creativity with this fun and engaging <strong>Magnetic Drawing Board Toy for Kids</strong>. Designed with colorful magnetic beads and an easy-to-use magnetic pen, this <strong>educational toy for kids</strong> helps children create shapes, patterns, and pictures while learning through play.</p><p></p><p>This <strong>magnetic bead drawing board</strong> encourages imagination and improves focus, patience, and hand-eye coordination. The cute animal-shaped board design makes it even more attractive for kids, while the colorful beads provide endless possibilities for creative learning.</p><p></p><p>The set includes <strong>80 colorful magnetic beads</strong>, allowing children to design different shapes, objects, and patterns. It is a perfect <strong>early learning toy for kids age 3+</strong> that helps develop fine motor skills and cognitive abilities while keeping children entertained without screen time.</p><p></p><ul><li><p><strong>80 PCS Magnetic Beads Set</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Magnetic Pen for Easy Drawing</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Educational Learning Toy for Kids</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Improves Creativity &amp; Focus</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Safe &amp; Durable Material</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Perfect Gift for Kids Age 3+</strong></p></li></ul><p></p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8b847311-3e2d-46e5-8203-a29e995e3a42.png', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2026-03-14 12:29:27.927706+00', '2026-03-14 12:29:27.927706+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8b847311-3e2d-46e5-8203-a29e995e3a42.