	('prod_ab38253a-d1eb-4188-94b7-e53ab41cc579', 'small-shape-sorting', 'SMALL SHAPE SORTING', '<p>Sturdy construction, premium craftsmanship, soft and elastic rope It’s easy to put all in, fun and limitless options,Their hands can reach in and grab the toys inside and out them back, they will do it again and again, offers a huge imagination for your little baby. keeps them entertained and helps them with being patient.</p><p>Blocks and the cube are designed in different bright colors, babies tend to love colorful things and being attracted. they can learn about the ability of color and spatial reasoning when playing. the string around the box gives enough tension for the baby to strengthen their fine motor skills, great for the baby’s physical and mental development.</p>', 399, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d13d26ca-dccf-4ddb-9d82-f8452136bf77.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 549.97}', '2025-12-28 10:59:19.831445+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:19.831445+00', 'cat_1ff574c2-bfb1-4b77-b9c7-ae54ed7fa4e5', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-shape-sorting/dde843f0-edf6-4021-92f5-2aa06eda6e95.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d13d26ca-dccf-4ddb-9d82-f8452136bf77.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/deb812db-b3bb-4f33-add6-54dfd6ef4673.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/38731bea-3204-46b8-a02a-16d23c8ef234.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.011928581,-0.003727208,0.041709475,-0.0075901155,0.03606179,-0.00056768593,0.013982933,0.04316189,0.03228753,0.033603232,-0.043948423,0.012868702,-0.018373825,-0.051822748,-0.02339556,0.009976067,-0.07315592,0.009470713,-0.024522329,-0.0487549,-0.011553521,-0.06263012,0.04751714,0.047340646,0.045355003,0.0061210054,0.008454526,0.03620209,-0.037920095,0.031131387,-0.019023804,-0.009105223,0.009718226,0.026805028,-0.04683649,-0.03711262,-0.04064718,0.05000778,0.031892553,-0.081206165,-0.04847547,0.039550275,0.025655884,-0.029233105,0.0005478176,-0.09543281,0.007576005,-0.02001375,-0.