	('prod_a5758875-2312-4696-826a-4e150220bbdc', 'match-pop-think-fast-pair-fasteer', 'Match Pop ( Think Fast - Pair Fasteer )', '<p>Get ready for a visual scramble with MATCH POP, the speed-observation game that tests your eyes and reflexes! Players must race to identify and match geometric patterns from their design cards onto the vibrant, colorful game mats. Includes unique pattern mats, 27 detailed design cards featuring various styles (like the ''jockey'' style seen), and a signal bell.</p><p></p><p><strong>How to Play (4 Steps):</strong></p><p></p><ol><li><p><strong>FLIP A CARD:</strong> Turn over a design card.</p></li><li><p><strong>FIND THE MATCH:</strong> Be the first to locate the identical pattern on a mat.</p></li><li><p><strong>RING THE BELL:</strong> Press the bell instantly to claim your find.</p></li><li><p><strong>WIN THE CARD:</strong> The first to match wins the card. The player with the most cards wins!</p></li><li><p></p></li></ol><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><p></p><p>Perfect for developing quick thinking, focus, and visual-spatial skills.</p><p></p><p><strong>What''s Inside the Box:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li><p>27 Design Cards</p></li><li><p>2 Play Mats</p></li><li><p>1 Bell</p></li></ul><p></p>', 549, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7c5c5cb2-b11d-4be8-9c9b-b07ee6a71715.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 748.99}', '2026-03-11 11:57:59.786566+00', '2026-03-11 11:57:59.786566+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7c5c5cb2-b11d-4be8-9c9b-b07ee6a71715.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/11f4d8d3-de9d-4725-89a5-558599b30221.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/bbde3f4d-5ff2-41d8-bca9-9a87d9e397ef.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/160d36c0-bef0-4bb1-9996-d35597ed6819.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/44a0788a-76fa-4de3-9358-6e117f699eff.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/896d48b2-7a8b-4a7b-84e8-3ea298cbbed3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in