	('prod_6a4b1692-6064-4b38-a773-df2a31b0a700', 'shape-matching-game', 'Shape Matching Game', '<ul><li><p>🧩 Shape Matching Game for Kids 2+ TinyPlay shape matching puzzle game is designed to help children recognize shapes and patterns while enhancing focus and logical thinking. Perfect for kids aged 3 years and above.</p></li><li><p>🎨 Fun and Learning Toy for Children This educational toy encourages color recognition, matching, sorting, and early problem-solving. A great way to develop fine motor skills through hands-on pla</p></li><li><p>📘 Includes Puzzle Board &amp; Illustrated Cards The set features a sturdy matching board, colorful shape pieces, and activity cards for guided learning. Helps kids play independently or with friends and parents.</p></li><li><p>👶 Safe &amp; Durable Construction Made with high-quality, child-safe materials. All pieces are smooth-edged, lightweight, and easy to handle, making it safe and engaging for toddlers and preschoolers.</p></li><li><p>🎁 Ideal Gift for Boys &amp; Girls A thoughtful and educational gift choice for birthdays, return gifts, or preschool learning. TinyPlay shape matching toys are perfect for kids who love learning through play.</p></li></ul>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/97bfd538-0189-4aef-8324-e503d3e463fc.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 520}', '2025-12-28 10:59:19.728175+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:19.728175+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/shape-matching-game/3e6b3fc2-1fd3-4330-b5e9-128aeeaaa3d9.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/97bfd538-0189-4aef-8324-e503d3e463fc.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e0553a8a-cf5d-4819-b35a-6e06935b76ed.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c62ecad9-596f-4bee-b9f4-38cfb2724010.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f4945959-3145-4ea8-87e7-211a2780ab7b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/255a60fd-2e74-443c-b07a-83c6ef5ae536.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.020782944,-0.