	('prod_6fa31b02-a8a8-4505-a154-32672e492d20', 'toy-train-with-track-set', 'Toy train with track set', '<ul><li><p>Safe design in train toys for kids: the steam train is made of safe raw materials, the surface is smooth, the safety pigment is integrated, the colours are pure and the driving colours contribute to the development of the soft and cheerful personality of the baby. Baby can play with confidence train toy.</p></li><li><p>kids train kit: bluebell pretend to play toys the product is equipped with a variety of body variants, twelve-track combinations and four cars so that children can assemble a larger selection of track train set models to have more fun assembly, children to touch and train creatively.</p></li><li><p>Educational toy for kids: This train toy for boys can promote children coordination skills, promote children intellectual development and cultivate children room imagination. Maintain children interest in exploring the unknown world. As well as cultivating children interest and hobbies, and influence the growth path of children.</p></li><li><p>Involved train toys for kids: this train set with track includes 1 head of a locomotive, 1 coal tank, 1 cargo car, 1 passenger car. The requires 4 AA batteries but not included, which you can easily replace. After the train is turned on, it has a realistic steam engine sound and simulated electric smoke technology.</p></li></ul>', 1045, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0732ec40-cf6d-4b10-83dc-48c0e5731230.png', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1498.98}', '2025-12-28 10:59:21.267627+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:21.267627+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/toy-train-with-track-set/7974c50c-8fbb-423c-aeaf-e5b9b76bb5df.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0732ec40-cf6d-4b10-83dc-48c0e5731230.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/07badbf6-c385-4475-9785-3140397d4861.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/toy-train-with-track-se