	('prod_587cc465-6cea-4d50-a355-b95ec2aa1f9e', 'rolls-royce-cullinan-die-cast', 'Rolls Royce Cullinan Die Cast', '<ul><li><p>➤ ALLOY DIECAST METAL CAR : 1:36 Rolls Royce Cullinan Die Cast collectible toy car model has the powerful functions, which the Childhood, tail and the doors can be opened. Also have the standard quality pull back function, you can pull back the car and then it will driving with strong Power. The simulation of the car makes the car look beautiful and cool!</p></li><li><p>➤ LIGHT SOUND AND MUSIC : You can open the left and right doors of the car model, the hood and trunk can also be opened. To press the front wheel or open the door, it will cause light and sound effects, and pull the car model back and do it automatically.</p></li><li><p>➤ HIGH QUALITY MATERIAL :1:36 Rolls Royce Cullinan Die Cast car is made of zinc alloy, plastic parts, rubber tires. Our products 100% Non-toxic, no harm to children. Install a strong pull-back device. The car is made of same material and has no sharp edges.</p></li><li><p>➤ PULL BACK METAL CAR : Pull back to work, easy to operate, don''t worry about it no working; Speed is not fast enough to prevent a child from falling. The pull Back Vehicles all doors ,front cover and back cover could be opened, highly detailed interior and exteriorthe.</p></li><li><p>➤ GREAT GIFT AND DECORATION : 1:36 Rolls Royce Cullinan Die Cast Metal Toy Car Very sturdy, fine workmanship, nice toy car, Birthday present Vacation Diwali Holiday Gift and Christmas gifts Toy for boy’s age 2 and Above years old. Perfect gifts for kids. Colors will be dispatched as per availibility.</p></li></ul>', 1249, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/563597a0-8f65-40fc-a3e2-3a08656628a6.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2025-12-28 10:59:20.529139+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:20.529139+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/rolls-royce-cullinan-die-cast/edd8e37f-6