	('prod_c48212d1-7887-4501-8c1d-9398fbdc70a9', '13-in-1-family-board-magnetic-game', '13 in 1 Family Board Magnetic Game', '<p>• Perfect for schools, home, work, playrooms, travel, gifts &amp; so much more!<br>• Develops Imagination, Motor, Eye-Hand Co-Ordination Skills.</p><p>A Fun Game for the entire family. This 13 in 1 Game has all of your choices. Enjoy a splendid evening with your family and friends playing these games 13 in 1 family game: magnetic chess set with dices &amp; resin chess magnetic pieces &amp; colored resin pieces with removable stands which board games you can play: 1. CHESS 2. CHECKERS 3. 9 MEN’S MORRIS 4. SNAKES AND LADDER 5. STEEP &amp; LADDERS 6. STEEPLECHASE 7. TRAVEL BINGO 8. FOOTBALL 9. BACKGAMMON 10. LUDO 11. TIC-TAC-TOE 12. RACING GAME 13. SPACE-VENTURE IN THE BOX: 5PCS CARD PAPER BOARD GAMES(PRINTED BOTH SIDES), 1PC MAGNETIC BOARD WITH BOTH SIDE PRINTED , 4 REMOVABLE CLIP STANDS, 2 PCS DOT DICE , 1 PC NUMBER DICE , 16 PIECES BLUE RESIN MAGNETIC CHESS PIECES. 16 PIECES TRANSPARENT MAGNETIC CHESS PIECES, 16 PIECES TRANSPARENT CHECKER COINS, 16 PIECES BLUE RESIN CHECKER COINS, 4 PIECES GREEN RESIN CHECKER COINS, 4 PIECES RED CHECKER COINS.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 219, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/13-in-1-family-board-magnetic-game/52a83715-e2ca-46f6-9ef4-a0a681591190.png', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 299}', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.859058+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.859058+00', 'cat_faea0711-a3b3-422e-a496-772919c14df6', 'col_d3648e6d-cf26-493f-9cd3-1803de78bf8c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/13-in-1-family-board-magnetic-game/52a83715-e2ca-46f6-9ef4-a0a681591190.png', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/13-in-1-family-board-magnetic-game/52a83715-e2ca-46f6-9ef4-a0a681591190.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/13-in-1-family-board-magnetic-game/b84246e9-4280-480a-a34a-5842195d41b1.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/13-in-1-family-board-magnetic-game/8a811b9a-c848-4792-af74-fa10e2f81f91.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/13-in-1-family-boa