	('prod_459d2506-ddb1-4806-9a2a-68dd808c315f', 'toyz-kitchen-set-for-girls-light-and-sound-portable-trolley-18-pcs-kitchen-toys-for-girls-big-cooking-set-for-kids', 'Toyz Kitchen Set for Girls | Light & Sound Portable Trolley 18 pcs Kitchen Toys for Girls | Big Cooking Set for Kids', '<ul><li><p>👩‍🍳 2-in-1 Portable Kitchen Set: Smart design converts from a compact suitcase into a full-size standing kitchen. Easy to assemble and carry for travel or playdates.</p></li><li><p>🎵 Light &amp; Sound Cooking Fun: Realistic stove lights and cooking sounds add excitement to pretend play! Requires AAA batteries (not included).</p></li><li><p>🍅 Complete Kitchen Accessories: Includes cutlery, pots, pans, cups, bottles, vegetables, and utensils – everything your little chef needs to cook up imagination.</p></li><li><p>💼 Compact &amp; Easy to Store: All parts neatly fit inside the trolley case. Lockable suitcase design with rolling wheels and handle for convenient storage and portability.</p></li><li><p>🎁 Educational &amp; Safe for Kids: Made of non-toxic, BPA-free plastic with smooth edges. Encourages creativity, role play, hand-eye coordination, and social skills in kids aged 3+.</p></li><li><p>🔎 COMMONLY SEARCHED TOPICS: kitchen set for kids girl trolley kitchen set modern electric kitchen set for kids mini kitchen real cooking set miniature kitchen set pretend to play toy set untensils toy pretend play cooking kitchen play set toy portable indoor game for girls kids cooking set with accessories toy kitchen set with lights and sounds kids kitchen play set portable kitchen play set with lights</p></li></ul><p></p>', 899, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/88bd456e-dfea-46a2-b9fe-4a1d3728763b.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2025-12-28 10:59:05.384129+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:05.384129+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/beauty-set-trolly/44d0674d-b878-480e-958b-9e7c511e0f1d.jp