	('prod_7f7b61a2-cff4-43c5-aefd-db676392afc3', 'big-shape-sorting', 'BIG SHAPE SORTING', '<p>WireScorts Baby Shape Sorting Toy is designed to captivate your child’s imagination while fostering key developmental skills. Featuring colorful blocks, alphabet letters, and an innovative elastic band design, this Montessori-inspired toy offers an interactive way for babies and toddlers to explore shapes, colors, and textures</p><p>This sorting brain toy features soft elastic bands, and 6 bright-colored shapes with different textures, which help to develop color recognition and shape sorting skills.</p><p>Stimulate learning through funny games. With this baby shape sorting toy, babies not only can practice motor skills, coordination, color and shape identification, but also can develop spatial reasoning, cause &amp; effect reasoning, and problem-solving skills.</p>', 399, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-shape-sorting/fc5348e8-ecd0-4b17-bdf5-a116afe0d53f.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 499}', '2025-12-28 10:59:06.40199+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:06.40199+00', NULL, 'col_1ed8436d-f24e-4723-8ad3-e50ca8ea9e71', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-shape-sorting/fc5348e8-ecd0-4b17-bdf5-a116afe0d53f.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-shape-sorting/fc5348e8-ecd0-4b17-bdf5-a116afe0d53f.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-shape-sorting/ea3275ae-2219-4e7b-bd12-1b38c432e101.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-shape-sorting/e25cc142-1a83-442a-a305-19a440a5d399.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-shape-sorting/9c7a6666-1af2-4511-a4c4-f0d8dfc821d6.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-shape-sorting/ac4e74e7-b9b6-40f7-a478-0f679b27a1ac.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-shape-sorting/3131bfc7-a61e-43e5-91a2-f1be6e249efd.jpg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.012806305,-0.008684642,0.04417141,-0.049424108,0.009571501,-0.032177296,0.059064653,0.055587534,0.03276597,0.04171868,-0.023391528,-0.040596213,-0.03177784,-0.034565996,-0.035703965,-0.02674165,-0.035851054,0.