	('prod_7e09c4fd-0134-4d23-b1e8-bdb1bb71d61f', '4wd-kids-radio-gaming-cars', '4WD Kids Radio Gaming Cars', '<ul><li><p>Precision 4WD Control &amp; Low-Center Gravity Dominate every drift with four-wheel drive traction and a low-center gravity design for ultra-stable handling on tabletops, floors, or smooth pavements. Compact 1:64 scale (7.5cm) delivers pro-level performance in tight spaces</p></li><li><p>Smart Throttle Curve Adjustment Tailor your speed! Switch between gentle acceleration (ideal for beginners) and aggressive power bursts (for advanced drifts) with the adjustable throttle curve system</p></li><li><p>Type-C Fast Charging &amp; Extended Play Power up in 30 minutes via the universal Type-C port for 20+ minutes of nonstop action. The 3.7V 100mAh battery keeps races going longer, perfect for quick sessions</p></li><li><p>2.4GHz Multi-Car Racing Host epic battles! The interference-free 2.4GHz remote (20m range) supports racing multiple cars (sold separately). Perfect for family competitions or solo practice</p></li><li><p>Pro Steering &amp; Lighting Control Proportional Steering: Fine-tune turning angles for razor-sharp drifts. Dynamic LEDs: High-brightness headlights (spotlight mode) and brake-activated taillights add realism. Use the remote’s long/short press to toggle lights</p></li></ul>', 2099, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-kids-radio-gaming-cars/09cb8892-7429-4fea-9b84-ba26ed2000de.png', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 2499}', '2025-12-28 10:59:03.696212+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:03.696212+00', NULL, 'col_3e7482c6-92fa-4798-9d71-b92e16e3f43b', 'draft', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-kids-radio-gaming-cars/4b4167f7-741f-46a1-9fbe-f1858b53e3b2.png', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-kids-radio-gaming-cars/09cb8892-7429-4fea-9b84-ba26ed2000de.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-kids-radio-gaming-cars/109a1b58-126c-454d-9805-170561b9fc9e.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/4wd-kids-radio-gaming-cars/73cf7055-0c90-4288-9e98-4fbc0a41a5f8.jpg,https:/