	('prod_8b2c9047-4763-4b92-807e-21304adcf6e1', 'big-carrier-trucks-with-small-cars-pink-transport-truck', 'BIG CARRIER TRUCKS WITH SMALL CARS || PINK TRANSPORT TRUCK', '<p><br>Toddler Truck Toys for 3 4 5 6 Year Old buoys - 5-in-1 Friction Power Vehicle Car Toy for Toddlers 1-3, Carrier Truck Toys for Kids 3-5, Christmas Birthday Gifts for Age 3-9</p><p>5 in 1 Truck Toy: TEMI construction carrier truck toy includes a larger transport truck and 4 mini car. The working part of these small engineering vehicles can be moved, and children will be immersed in building base. Toddler boys toys age 3-6 years old.<br>Pull Back Cars: Just pull it back, then release your hand, car can run a long distance. Separate the cab and the traction compartment, and then open the tailgate to transport the vehicle down.<br>Real Sound Effect and Light: Press the button above the truck can play the sound and turn on the headlight, enhance kids'' gaming fun. The truck toys will bring lots of joy and surprise to the children! Please be assured that every time you press the button, the whistle will only last for about 8 seconds, don''t worry about it making noise.<br>Size for Small Hands: Our engineering vehicle toys of mini car toys toddler boy toys are designed for 3-6 year old kids'' small hands to hold and push, very handy to carry wherever you go, not too big or small.<br>Construction Trucks: The working parts of 5 vehicles can be rotated and moved, which make your little architect more realistically feel the fun of building his own base. You can lead your kids to learn construction knowledge, simulate transport the sand and other materials in the construction site, inspire their imagination, build their own construction base.<br></p>', 999, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/big-carrier-trucks-with-small-cars-pink-transport-truck/af93c18a-701f-419c-9bb9-c5ef53ed908d.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": null}', '2025-12-28 10:59:05.987798+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:05.987798+00', NULL, 'col_854e0262-c