	('prod_7009c838-5afc-434e-ad57-237d855debae', 'kitchen-hand-bag-set', 'Kitchen Hand Bag Set', '<p>Let your kids cook up imaginary feast for the whole family with the Kitchen Playset. The young chefs in your life will sure love this almost realistic kitchen with included kitchen accessories.<br>Interactive Little Chef Kids Kitchen Play Set with Light &amp; Sound. Your kids will love to pretend as chef. While real kitchen is dangerous for kids to play.</p><p>This Kitchen kit set comes with a durable Kitchen carry case, all the Kitchen items can be easily stored. It is suitable for outdoor playing and indoor playing<br>There’s a handle on the side of the kit so that you can lift it, and it’s also a trolley with wheels that you can pull, so kids can easily take it anywhere .Comes In A Compact design.</p><p>Kitchen cook toys are interactive playsets that allow children to simulate cooking and food preparation. These toys often include miniature versions of kitchen tools, utensils, pots, pans, and pretend food items, encouraging imaginative play and role-playing. They help develop fine motor skills, creativity, and an understanding of everyday tasks, while allowing kids to engage in fun, pretend cooking activities.</p>', 499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cb62ca08-41fc-489f-b570-8b6d8e714257.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 699}', '2025-12-28 10:59:14.826659+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:14.826659+00', NULL, 'col_64ba526c-0c27-4be8-bea3-3fbc9d30ffc2', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/kitchen-hand-bag-set/748e12b7-ea7b-4091-87b6-f19f25bbe55c.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cb62ca08-41fc-489f-b570-8b6d8e714257.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5098e127-d16f-4873-9eb3-f0098731c916.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2d85e9b4-88e1-4614-b100-2fd8be489e6b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b8d82338-d063-4cf7-bf2d-8b984d45b0d1.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ebf400c8-066b-4739-8759-a125a9b801d2.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.011664911,-0.041512758,-0.