	('prod_68843939-2936-4950-acfc-e26617623530', 'audi-rs6-metal-alloy-model', 'Audi Rs6 Metal Alloy Model', '<ul><li><p>🚘【MATERIALS】: Made of high-quality materials, these cars are durable, safe, non-toxic and lead-free toys. Can be moved. You can trust the quality and use it safely without worrying about your child ’s safety.</p></li><li><p>🚘【PREMIUM QUALITY】: This stunning toy car with open doors is made with alloy and ABS, heavy-duty and durable materials that will pass the test of time. The rubber tiles have a real and solid structure for more sturdiness.</p></li><li><p>🚘【SPECIAL FEATURES】: This collectible toy car has special lighting and music effects that all kids will love. It provides a realistic engine sound and dazzling lights for a real experience. This scale model car has a pullback system that allows it to catch great speeds.</p></li><li><p>🚘【COLLECTIBLE PIECE】: Our authentic car model is not just a great toy for kids but it can also be part of your car model collection. The precise detailing and premium finishing touches make this Model Replica a must-have in your toy car display.</p></li><li><p>🚘【Suitable For Birthday and Christmas Gifts】:The sound of model will sound like an engine sound, there is no doubt that the cool car model will attract children''s attention. Perfect gifts for kids</p></li><li><p>🚘【Types】: Diecast cars cover a wide range of vehicles, from classic cars to modern sports cars, trucks, motorcycles, and even fictional vehicles from movies and TV shows.</p></li></ul>', 1149, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b5ba8a3e-620e-4c67-816a-5e7de76bc3db.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.359026+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.359026+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/audi-rs6-metal-alloy-model/0150cb0b-c18e-4251-ae02-1f67dfe599b8.webp', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b5ba8a3e-620e-4c67-816a-5e7de76bc3db.jpeg,https://cdn.t