	('prod_edbe6739-2366-492a-8de7-86b2fa574f01', 'flare-remote-control-car-1', 'RC Drift Car with Remote Control, 2.4GHz Racing Car Kit, Pink, with Spare Tyres and Traffic Cones - Flare', '<ul><li><p>RACING FEATURES: 2.4GHz remote control system ensures responsive handling and precise control for exciting drift racing action</p></li><li><p>COMPLETE KIT: Includes RC car, remote controller, spare tyres, traffic cones, screwdriver and charging cable for comprehensive racing experience</p></li><li><p>DESIGN ELEMENTS: Sporty exterior with racing decals and aerodynamic body styling creates an authentic drift car appearance</p></li><li><p>PERFORMANCE: Specially engineered drift tyres and suspension system enable smooth drifting manoeuvres and high-speed cornering</p></li><li><p>PRACTICE SET: Comes with training accessories including 4 traffic cones and 2 marker barrels for setting up custom drift courses</p></li></ul><p></p>', 2199, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/16ff2e61-cbe9-49ac-9a33-ac49a539eae5.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": null}', '2026-01-28 05:02:50.763847+00', '2026-01-28 05:02:50.763847+00', 'cat_65960efd-3436-4822-89e6-6043c99610c3', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/16ff2e61-cbe9-49ac-9a33-ac49a539eae5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7aa3a1fc-0043-4b73-92db-dae7cbf58ab9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7da77d22-3a08-4b57-8cf9-0ea9596f9eb2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/82d52ce4-1226-4258-aa40-a469762a0ed5.jpeg}', 'inr', '', '', 'https://www.youtube.com/shorts/T1t6Xukwzs8', '[0.0017025842,-0.06825399,-0.028089352,0.004059601,0.058258295,0.031742126,0.049568474,0.024226043,0.001722618,-0.010397432,0.03338117,-0.006942812,0.017807905,-0.02598622,0.07911815,0.00440244,0.011092893,-0.016684404,0.013897007,-0.033626296,0.030051986,0.04162256,-0.013058565,0.07455848,-0.046057146,-0.0042113587,0.03846652,-0.011149462,-0.025610091,-0.052371077,0.03616992,0.024788652,-0.053022046,-0.012449607,-