	('prod_07f09807-07cd-44a2-80e5-4820e5a6a22b', '360-rotational-remote-control-police-stunt-car-toy-for-kids-boys-girls-rechargeable-4wd-rc-toy', '360° Rotational Remote Control Police Stunt Car Toy for Kids Boys Girls, Rechargeable 4WD RC Toy', '<p>Bring excitement and action-packed fun to your child’s playtime with this <strong>Remote Control Police Stunt Car</strong> 🚓. Designed with powerful motors and a sturdy build, this RC car performs <strong>360-degree flips, spins, and smooth drifting</strong>, making it perfect for indoor and outdoor adventures.</p><p></p><p>Equipped with <strong>bright LED lights</strong> and a <strong>realistic police car design</strong>, it enhances the play experience and keeps kids engaged for hours.</p><p></p><p>The easy-to-use <strong>2.4GHz remote control</strong> ensures stable connection and responsive handling without interference.</p><p></p><p>This stunt car comes with a <strong>rechargeable battery and Type-C charging</strong>, making it convenient and cost-effective. The durable wheels and shock-resistant body allow it to run smoothly on different surfaces like tiles, roads, and carpets.</p><p></p><ul><li><p>360° stunt flips &amp; spinning action</p></li><li><p>2.4GHz remote control – smooth &amp; long-range control</p></li><li><p>LED lights for cool effects</p></li><li><p>Rechargeable battery with Type-C charging</p></li><li><p>Strong motor &amp; durable build</p></li><li><p>Anti-slip wheels for all terrains</p></li><li><p>Perfect gift for kids (boys &amp; girls)</p></li></ul><p></p>', 399, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/178df663-5e77-42f0-9023-86f97685d163.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1399}', '2026-03-19 04:08:42.739082+00', '2026-03-19 04:08:42.739082+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/178df663-5e77-42f0-9023-86f97685d163.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/52c35ca5-1145-4f6b-adb1-e9b35c749ccd.jpeg,https://cdn