	('prod_a32836b0-d1d9-4e01-9ad3-ef47e4391b26', 'double-ineritica-insect-beetle', 'DOUBLE INERITICA INSECT BEETLE', '<p>the toy car includes cute insect-shaped cars in bright colours: ladybird, beetle and dragonfly with fun faces that easily attract the child''s attention. Perfect for children aged 1-5 years.<br>🚗 Available in two modes: No batteries required. The wind-up car has two modes. Push and walk mode. Simply press the top of the car toy down and release and the boy''s toy car will drive. Pull back car mode: the rear wheels have a built-in threaded gear to pull back and the car drives forward.<br>Safe and durable: the best toy car for children aged 1-5 years. Made from durable, non-toxic ABS plastic, the toy car is drip-proof, eco-friendly and child-friendly. With its compact design and no sharp edges, the toy car won''t hurt your child''s little fingers and won''t scratch their smooth skin.<br>Educational and fun: the pull back toy car can be run indoors or outdoors. Children can have a fun-filled racing game. Most importantly, they can practise and learn physical coordination, sensory perception, motor skills, teamwork in a subtle way. It is also a great idea to decorate a room as a collector''s item or as a birthday or party gift.<br>🚗 The perfect gift: Colourful pull-back car, perfect size and shape, easy to grasp through a small child''s hands. A wonderful birthday gift, Christmas present, party accessory and any other celebratory gift toy for babies and girls aged 1 2 3 years.</p><p><br>Technical Details<br>Product Dimensions &nbsp; &nbsp;‎9 x 8 x 5 cm; 200 g<br>Manufacturer recommended age &nbsp; &nbsp;‎1 month - 2 years<br><br></p>', 149, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/acbdf6d6-ef6a-4fd7-b57a-c7c7bdf6a3cc.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 250}', '2025-12-28 10:59:10.588597+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:10.588597+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_237aa57b-2292-4dca-a106-d04a60ce9d38', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/double-ineri