	('prod_ba301363-e98f-44e6-bf96-0416378e44f5', 'home-kitchen-play-sink-with-running-water-utensils-kitchen-set-for-girls-kids-play-electronic-wash-basin-sink-with-live-running-water', 'Home Kitchen Play Sink with Running Water, Utensils, Kitchen Set for Girls, Kids Play Electronic Wash Basin Sink with Live Running Water ', '<ul><li><p>Kitchen Toy with Various Accessories-Our play kitchen comes with kitchen sink, base,upgraded electric faucet, dish rack, play detergent, plastic cup, plastic plate, brush, plastic knife, spoon, fork, rag, dish washing sponges and play food. The toy sink is easy to assemble and requires 4 AA batteries, not included.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Upgrade Electric Faucet - Our sink toy set comes with an upgraded faucet with automatic water cycle system. Our waterproof design faucet is more powerful and lasting than others. And the play sink will pump water automatically when you turn on the electric faucet. It makes the water circulation and does not waste water. Furthermore, the faucet can be rotated 180 degrees and can flush two sinks.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Quickly Drain with Dish Rack-The storage basket and the hanging hook design effectively drain the small drops of water from the tableware, it will help the kids to organize the tableware. Meantime, large size of sink area not only let your kids has more capacity for water play ,but also can be a storage box after playing.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Realistic Role Play Sink Toys Set- This is a pretend play wash up kitchen sink toy for kids to learn washing dishes. Children can not only enjoy doing housework but develop their hands-on ability. Let them learn to help their parents share housework. It can also encourage kids to wash their hands properly to keep healthy.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Super Value Kitchen Play Set for Toddlers &amp;Girls- Made of ABS material,smooth and no smell. It is perfect for birthday party, Christmas, holiday or Impulse <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="http://gift.Kids">gift.Kids</a> can play with warm water and avoid catching cold. It is also a perfect kitchen toy in winter.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1199, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e5319a55-ba95-4f88-ac85-98dff26657fb.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2599}', '2026-04-01 12:45:48.792747+00', '2026-04-01 12:45:48.792747+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e5319a55-ba95-4f88-ac85-98dff26657fb.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5fcb41ac-934b-4e09-bcf8-8742d4804bda.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dc4ef800-137a-4890-add6-16508f00f161.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b8919d0d-a83d-46b0-9cc1-2b57be61be82.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8a39068f-9aa0-4dd5-90e9-849582df5615.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2f9c1614-79c2-4855-b0c7-4c80177da993.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6a8acf44-eba3-479a-9e63-ed0d67310b8f.png}', 'inr', NULL, 'Kitchen Toy with Various Accessories-Our play kitchen comes with kitchen sink, base,upgraded electric faucet, dish rack, play detergent, plastic cup, plastic plate, brush, plastic knife, spoon, fork, rag, dish washing sponges and play food. The toy sink is easy to assemble and requires 4 AA batteries, not included.', 'https://youtu.be/3-ZCIhv4l0o', '[-0.050980978,0.0018724676,0.044801537,0.03248613,-0.01700368,-0.0035238874,0.040211286,-0.014766028,0.025604883,0.010454615,-0.026795153,-0.086003594,-0.05228575,-0.016441194,0.05103489,-0.030315464,-0.116784714,0.007493449,-0.030287301,-0.035550725,-0.03771332,0.036022484,0.03771486,0.039960913,0.0026526381,0.010486806,0.020198602,0.015025531,-0.018993722,0.010494564,-0.013347251,0.015946573,0.0016382127,0.019465528,-0.06982404,0.010240155,-0.03272274,0.043157447,-0.0056542284,-0.088800356,-0.022460192,0.038645703,0.03300379,0.0058500767,-0.017960481,0.0071697948,0.04594895,-0.04809087,0.029510431,0.048373573,0.012238335,0