	('prod_f9bf84db-1808-4c05-8123-eaafa6077229', 'flip-match-game', 'Flip & Match Game', '<ul><li><p>Boosts Memory &amp; Cognitive Skills – Helps children enhance memory, recall, and attention span through fun matching play. Animal &amp; Fruit Series Included – Comes with themed stickers to teach vocabulary and recognition of animals and fruits.</p></li><li><p>Fun Educational Game for Kids – Combines playtime with learning for ages 3+, ideal for toddlers and preschoolers. Encourages Logical Thinking – Helps build pattern recognition, problem-solving, and decision-making skills.</p></li><li><p>Promotes Brain Development – Designed to support early childhood intellectual growth and critical thinking. Montessori-Inspired Design – A hands-on game that aligns with Montessori teaching principles for independent learning.</p></li><li><p>Perfect for Solo or Group Play – Great for playdates, siblings, classrooms, or parent-child bonding time. Customizable with Sticker Sheets – Includes removable stickers so kids can change themes and learn new items.</p></li><li><p>Safe, Durable &amp; Kid-Friendly Materials – Smooth, non-toxic plastic for safe and long-lasting use. Vibrant Colors to Keep Kids Engaged – Eye-catching design maintains interest and attention during play.</p></li><li><p>Portable &amp; Travel-Friendly Size – Lightweight and compact – perfect for on-the-go learning or vacation trips. Screen-Free Entertainment – Encourages real-world play without electronics or screens.</p></li><li><p>Improves Fine Motor Skills – Supports hand-eye coordination, grip strength, and dexterity. Ideal Educational Gift for Kids – Makes a thoughtful birthday, holiday, or back-to-school gift.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 299, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0f9bdaba-da23-4330-953b-e5224c37caea.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 399}', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.693916+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.693916+00', 'cat_faea0711-a3b3-422e-a496-772919c14df6', 'col_d3648e6d-cf26-493f-9cd3-1803de78bf8c', 'active', 'ht