	('prod_f8d48f6a-4409-4afa-b0a8-3831abd57240', 'h11-hoverboard', 'H11 HOVERBOARD', '<p>LARGER 10.5” WHEELS – Perfect for Riding Indoors and Outdoors.</p><p>FREE ACCESSORIES – Free Carry Bag, Charger, Free Protection Kit, and Free Remote</p><p>START UP BALANCE 2.0 – Assists in Balancing the Hoverboard with the 5th GEN Control Board</p><p>BLUETOOTH ENABLED – Play Music while riding with a built-in speaker</p><p>PREMIUM FEATURES – Bigger Battery, Lifting Handle, More Motor Power, and Led wheels (All Terrain Wheels)</p><p>POWERFUL PERFORMANCE – Race up to 18km/h and climb inclines up to 20 Degrees</p><p>FOR ALL RIDERS – Perfect for all Ages 7+ and up to 100kg Load<br><br>DIMENSIONS: 12 × 18 × 20 CM</p><p>STARTUP BALANCE 2.0: YES</p><p>CONTROL BOARD: FIFTH GENERATION SUPER INTELLIGENT CONTROL PANEL WITH US-BASED ST CHIPSETS.</p><p>BATTERY: 158WH 36V PACK WITH QUICK CHARGE 2.0 BATTERY MANAGEMENT SYSTEM</p><p>MOTOR: 300W X 2 DUAL MOTORS – DOUBLE TORQUE (100% COPPER)</p><p>TYRE: 10.5" OFFROAD AIR-FILLED TYRES</p><p>WARRANTY: 1-YEAR WARRANTY AS PER WARRANTY DETAILS. (PLEASE REFER TO WARRANTY SECTION)</p><p>CERTIFICATION: CE CERTIFIED</p><p>CHARGING TIME: QUICK CHARGE 2.0 (1-2 HOURS MAX)</p><p>MAXIMUM SPEED: 20KM/H (AS PER USER WEIGHT LOAD)</p><p>MAX LOAD CAPACITY: 100KG</p><p>MINIMUM LOAD: 15KG</p><p>BLUETOOTH: YES (PLAY MUSIC BY CONNECTING WITH ANY BLUETOOTH DEVICE)</p><p>FRONT LEDS: YES</p><p>REAR LEDS: YES</p><p>WHEEL ARCH LEDS: YES</p><p>BATTERY INDICATOR: YES</p><p>LED WHEEL: YES</p><p>REMOTE: YES</p><p>MOBILE APP: NO</p><p>BAG: YES</p><p>GRADABILITY: 20 DEGREES</p><p>MATERIAL: SOLID ALUMINIUM MAIN FRAME + ABS BODY</p><p>NET WEIGHT: 16KG</p><p>DELIVERY TIME: READY STOCK – SAME DAY QUICK DISPATCH (SHIPPING TIME 2-4 BUSINESS DAYS)</p><p>LIFTING HANDLE: YES</p><p>PROTECTION KIT: YES</p>', 14999, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/30e73088-2c31-4a1d-a5e4-8c5fbdc4d6b6.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 16999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.594242+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.594242+00', NU