	('prod_ac77a215-583d-4af7-b3ab-34a6be2eb454', 'kids-kitchen-set-toy-with-suitcase-cooking-pretend-play-kit-with-utensils-cups-and-accessories-3-years', 'Kids Kitchen Set Toy with Suitcase – Cooking Pretend Play Kit with Utensils, Cups & Accessories (3+ Years)', '<p>Let your child explore the joy of cooking with this Kids Kitchen Set Toy with Suitcase. Designed for children aged 3 years and above, this colorful and engaging pretend play set includes a variety of kitchen accessories such as a cooking pot, frying pan with lid, cups, spoons, plates, fork set, ketchup bottle, fried egg toy, and more.</p><p>The set comes with a convenient suitcase featuring an attachable handle and smooth wheels, making it easy for kids to carry their mini kitchen anywhere. This toy encourages imaginative play, creativity, and helps develop social and motor skills as children pretend to cook and serve food.</p><p>Made from safe, durable, and non-toxic materials, it is perfect for both boys and girls. Ideal for gifting on birthdays, return gifts, or special occasions, this kitchen set keeps kids entertained while learning basic cooking concepts in a fun way.<br></p><ul><li><p><strong>Complete Kitchen Play Set:</strong> Includes cooking pot, frying pan with lid, cups, plates, spoons, fork, knife &amp; more</p></li><li><p><strong>Portable Suitcase Design:</strong> Easy to carry with handle &amp; wheels for travel and storage</p></li><li><p><strong>Attractive &amp; Colorful Design:</strong> Bright colors that attract kids instantly</p></li><li><p><strong>Realistic Cooking Experience:</strong> Helps kids enjoy pretend cooking &amp; serving</p></li><li><p><strong>Boosts Creativity &amp; Imagination:</strong> Encourages role play and storytelling</p></li><li><p><strong>Safe &amp; Durable Material:</strong> Made from non-toxic, child-friendly plastic</p></li><li><p><strong>Improves Social Skills:</strong> Great for playing with friends and family</p></li><li><p><strong>Perfect Size for Kids:</strong> Lightweight and easy to handle</p></li><li><p><strong>Ideal Gift Option:</strong> Perfect for birthdays, return gifts &amp; special occasions</p></li><li><p><strong>Easy to Assemble &amp; Store:</strong> All items fit neatly inside the suitcase</p></li></ul><p></p>', 299, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/393a34d4-33c6-414b-b92a-3ffa93a8378f.png', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 699}', '2026-04-13 12:29:03.97057+00', '2026-04-13 12:29:03.97057+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/393a34d4-33c6-414b-b92a-3ffa93a8378f.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c3a8071c-fc10-43ac-8591-f507f55072d5.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/bada8ea7-68e1-4e75-8b35-a0c0cba29e07.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3999f6fb-1e00-4fa9-8918-7dc12010f2f3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/61116d6d-1f72-423b-8774-06f9bc9aa631.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7b0b5a29-ee60-4434-b3db-7692d8248ffd.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Fun and creative kitchen play set for kids with portable suitcase. Includes cooking pot, frying pan, cups, spoons, plates, and more for realistic pretend cooking play.', '', '[-0.020110706,-0.0035609256,0.041575484,0.006473383,0.038628913,0.008767971,0.027446674,-0.0060204007,-0.002358731,0.026716212,0.038343266,-0.046990607,-0.037019093,-0.0053597647,0.036087587,-0.02508126,-0.11861639,0.01135529,-0.008553034,-0.037390098,-0.071096696,0.04372613,-0.00013298223,0.034569386,-0.0053990562,0.03513859,0.015562007,0.022982255,0.014492118,-0.0035832452,-0.016263843,0.024919795,0.011472547,-0.035820767,-0.08492312,-0.06742388,-0.053350005,-0.006774961,-0.010106735,-0.015663197,-0.01634971,0.01515021,0.012275557,0.035208628,-0.01362969,0.004920198,0.042479083,-0.017254382,0.029235577,0.014097635,0.012273751,-0.0055549094,0.021883223,-0.019432914,-0.031829566,-0.013609662,-0.052797522,-0.008604715,0.04623798,-0.014975343,-0.017219208,-0.027274933,-0.040101916,0.013623796,-0.011