	('prod_83400d6a-c6cc-4c90-ad8f-e2784a5f07f8', 'dancing-miracle-princess-toy-doll', 'Dancing Miracle Princess Toy Doll', '<ul><li><p>Dancing Miracle Princess Doll comes with Music and Lights, It projects flashy and colorful 3D light effects , just like the fairy princess. It will be more beautiful to play at night..</p></li><li><p>This very special Miracle Princess Fairy sings while gliding, spinning, moving on her own while displaying an exciting light show showering the floor and walls with colorful lights and hearts, creating a dance party.</p></li><li><p>The doll''s bump-n-go movement means children are free to dance and enjoy the light show as the doll moves on her own about the room, redirecting away from obstacles so it''s easy to play with her maximizing the fun!It definitely will bring smile to your child''s face.</p></li><li><p>This is a very interesting toy gift for your daughter this year. Interactive Musical Toy - Helps children with color and shape recognition in addition to learning music during playing.</p></li><li><p>Note: Before playing, Make sure to properly close the battery cover before use.</p></li></ul>', 649, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3804cc03-adf7-4b49-ad15-afea891ee225.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.80864+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.80864+00', NULL, 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/dancing-miracle-princess-toy-doll/c38300db-925c-4bd8-beb4-665dd75c6187.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3804cc03-adf7-4b49-ad15-afea891ee225.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ed0e4455-a927-49e8-942c-d968f9404373.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e1a2655c-7d3b-4485-b162-fb8da896f765.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4bbc1caf-ef9f-4ac6-9b10-65449c38dd5a.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.017261056,0.030133028,0.028788816,0.00773343,0.019212024,-0.011142568,0.024808547,0.00519128,0.0063553955,0.018680245,0.011200276,0.008612149,0.046433996,-0.051780436,0.019069688,