	('prod_555f02a6-c049-4acb-b319-b5a6dc6844d8', 'h9-hummer-hoverboard', 'H9 Hummer Hoverboard', '<p><strong>LARGER 8.5” OFF-ROAD WHEELS –&nbsp;</strong>Perfect for Riding Indoors and Outdoors.</p><p><strong>FREE ACCESSORIES –</strong>&nbsp;Free Carry Bag, Charger, Free Protection Kit, and Free Remote</p><p><strong>START UP BALANCE 2.0 –</strong>&nbsp;Assists in Balancing the Hoverboard with the 5th GEN Control Board</p><p><strong>BLUETOOTH ENABLED –</strong>&nbsp;Play Music while riding with a built-in speaker</p><p><strong>PREMIUM FEATURES –</strong>&nbsp;Bigger Battery, Lifting Handle, More Motor Power, and All Terrain Wheels (Wider Wheels)</p><p><strong>POWERFUL PERFORMANCE –</strong>&nbsp;Race up to 18km/h and climb inclines up to 20 Degrees</p><p><strong>FOR ALL RIDERS –&nbsp;</strong>Perfect for all Ages 7+ and up to 100kg Load&nbsp;<br><br></p><p>WEIGHT: 15 kg</p><p>DIMENSIONS: 12 × 18 × 20 cm</p><p>STARTUP BALANCE 2.0: YES</p><p>CONTROL BOARD: Fifth Generation Super Intelligent Control Panel with US-based ST Chipsets – Auto Balance</p><p>BATTERY: 158wh 36V with Quick Charge 2.0 Battery Management System</p><p>MOTOR: 300W x 2 Dual Motors – Double Torque (100% Copper)</p><p>TYRE: 8.5" Solid Rubber Tubeless Tyre</p><p>WARRANT: 1-year warranty as per warranty details. (please refer to warranty section)</p><p>CERTIFICATION: CE Certified</p><p>CHARGING TIME: Quick charge 2.0 (1-2 Hours MAX)</p><p>MAXIMUM SPEED: 20Km/h (As per user weight load)</p><p>MAX LOAD CAPACITY: 100kg</p><p>MINIMUM LOAD: 15kg</p><p>BLUETOOTH: YES (Play Music by Connecting with any Bluetooth device)</p><p>FRONT LEDS: YES (White BIG LEDs Audi Style)</p><p>REAR LEDS: YES (Red)</p><p>WHEEL ARCH LEDS: NO</p><p>BATTERY INDICATOR: YES</p><p>REMOTE: YES</p><p>GRADEABILITY:20 Degrees</p><p>MATERIAL: Solid Aluminium Main Frame + ABS Body</p><p>NET WEIGHT: 15kg</p><p>DELIVERY TIME: Ready Stock – Same Day Quick Dispatch (Shipping time 2-4 Business Days)</p><p>CARRY BAG: Yes</p><p><br></p>', 19999, 'https