	('prod_d4b025cc-c430-4dc9-a58a-1858b7cd25a9', 'color-set-46-pcs', 'Color Set – 46 Pcs', '<p>This 46 piece art set will inspire to make creative designs and perfect to keep your young artist. The art set consists of a plastic box with several pull-out trays containing 46 different art items, including paints and brushes. Make flowers, characters, landscapes, and even personalised greeting cards all with your own fingers by using this kit. Use these coloured pencils and paints to enhance your artwork. It’s a great way to let your child express him or herself as well as create beautiful art projects.</p><p>BULLET POINTS :<br>• Easy to sharpen standered sized colored pencil with spiral lines. | Best result can be seen on drawing paper; Amazing 46 Piece Color Kit Art Set for kids and girls. | Color box with multiple coloured pens,crayons,water coloures,oil pastes and pencils<br>• Children Watercolor Painting Set Stationery Set Pen Gift Set birthday gifts Christmas gifts 1box = 46pcs.<br>• Color box with 46 pieces art set, multiple colored pens, crayons, water colors, pencils Easy to Sharpen Standard Sized Colored Pencil with Spiral Lines Best result can be seen on Drawing Paper. These colors can adhere easily to surfaces like textured paper, sketching paper or even smooth tinted paper.<br>• These colors can adhere easily to surfaces like textured paper, sketching paper or even smooth tinted paper Best use for gifting in birthdays Product color, design and character will be assorted.<br>• Color box with multiple colored pens, crayons, water colors, oil pastes, pencils Easy to sharpen standard sized colored pencil with spiral lines Best result can be seen on drawing paper.<br>• Good result can be seen on drawing paper. These colors can adhere easily to surfaces like textured paper, sketching paper or even smooth tinted pap</p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3db9abaa-b92b-466b-aa80-6ccfa9c63cf3.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 499.01}', '2025-12-28 10:59:07.434034