	('prod_5412e42b-ef18-4e78-a6c5-52bf07c2f4b3', 'gobble-game', 'Gobble Game', '<ul><li><p>ENGAGING STRATEGY GAME FOR KIDS &amp; FAMILIES – This fun and colorful Gobble Game adds a smart twist to traditional tic tac toe. Great for developing memory, logic, and focus while spending time with family.</p></li><li><p>THRILLING 3D GAMEPLAY – Stack, cover, and outsmart! Larger gobblers can cover smaller ones—adding surprise and strategy to every move. A perfect mix of fun and thinking for young minds.</p></li><li><p>BOOSTS SKILLS THROUGH PLAY – Supports brain development, critical thinking, hand-eye coordination, and fine motor skills. Ideal for ages 3+ and early learners at home or in preschool.</p></li><li><p>KID-FRIENDLY &amp; EASY TO LEARN – Simple rules and fast-paced play make it perfect for kids and adults alike. Encourages screen-free fun and builds social interaction skills.</p></li><li><p>WHAT’S INCLUDED – Includes 1 sturdy plastic grid, 18 colorful plastic gobblers, and easy-to-follow instructions. A perfect gift for birthdays, holidays, or family game nights.</p></li></ul>', 179, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/abe4819c-c444-4615-890b-c5d6fc5c56c3.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 250}', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.716028+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.716028+00', 'cat_faea0711-a3b3-422e-a496-772919c14df6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/gobble-game/0ff375a0-ac67-4402-83ad-06957692a7c1.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/abe4819c-c444-4615-890b-c5d6fc5c56c3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/991c288f-70a9-4378-9c82-8fc1c60435b0.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1548cb0a-b86f-4ff1-8f4a-5fd5a11c27b5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/52eebf98-c61c-4109-9146-23070a33915e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3e05c9b0-c9c9-4abc-8c17-397ed4501f96.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c1cfa8ab-b77f-4402-82cc-5389cd98aafd.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.030589484,-0.020551896,0.021715906,0.029974064,-0.0013622752,-0.