	('prod_65536f0a-e37c-4d6b-bb37-48545bdfecdb', 'mercedes-benz-gls-600-suv-maybach-1-24-scale-model-car', 'Mercedes Benz GLS 600 SUV Maybach 1:24 Scale Model Car', '<ul><li><p>【SPECIAL FEATURES】: This collectible toy car has special lighting and music effects that all kids will love. It provides a realistic engine sound and dazzling lights for a real experience. This scale model car has a pullback system that allows it to catch great speeds.</p></li><li><p>【COLLECTIBLE PIECE】: Our authentic car model is not just a great toy for kids but it can also be part of your car model collection. The precise detailing and premium finishing touches make this Model Replica a must-have in your toy car display.</p></li><li><p>【MATERIALS】: Made of high-quality materials, these cars are durable, safe, non-toxic and lead-free toys. Can be moved. You can trust the quality and use it safely without worrying about your child ’s safety.</p></li><li><p>【PREMIUM QUALITY】: This stunning toy car with open doors is made with alloy and ABS, heavy-duty and durable materials that will pass the test of time. The rubber tiles have a real and solid structure for more sturdiness.</p></li></ul>', 1699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/518af0d4-2783-465b-83ad-2541b93f9018.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2199}', '2025-12-28 10:59:16.647258+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:16.647258+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/mercedes-benz-gls-600-suv-maybach-1-24-scale-model-car/6d579460-adbb-44d8-acbf-00a22264103e.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/518af0d4-2783-465b-83ad-2541b93f9018.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/32c56433-bdc6-4f14-ae6a-b218f01be1e3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/990a948e-0d81-40b7-9296-787066ef1afe.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a9e3e95a-26b0-4447-a789-6c18d87e9b8d.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.0121821845,-0.002435263,0.04563933,-0.019957984,0.011890695,0.003489638,0.04509995,