	('prod_c27150c2-2004-4bc8-9c2f-0e76590483d6', 'off-rode-wild-beast-open-for-adventure', 'Off Rode Wild Beast ( Open For Adventure )', '<p>Powerful dual-motor remote control off-road car with monster tyres made for rough terrain adventure. Turbo speed, forward-backward control, and right-left turning with bright lights make playtime more exciting. Strong body, shock absorbers and rechargeable battery give kids long-lasting fun on every trip.<br><br>High-speed remote control off-road monster car with dual motor power, strong tyres and exciting lights for ultimate adventure play.<br><br>CAUTION:<br></p><ol><li><p>1 : THIS BOX CONTAINS A LI-ION RECHARGEABLE BATTERY INSIDE THE CAR</p></li><li><p>2 : TO CHARGE THE CAR: PLUG THE C TYPE CABLE PROVIDED IN THE BOX INTO THE CHARGING SLOT AT THE BOTTOM OF THE CAR.</p></li><li><p>3 : RECHARGE THE BATTERY FOR 3 TO 4 HOURS FOR A FULL CHARGE.</p></li><li><p>4 : TO CONNECT THE CAR AND REMOTE: KEEP THE CAR AND REMOTE CLOSE TO EACH OTHER. SWITCH THE CAR ON. HEADLIGHTS WILL BLINK, SWITCH ON THE REMOTE IMMEDIATELY. HEADLIGHTS WILL STOP BLINKING. CAR AND REMOTE IS READY TO PLAY</p></li><li><p>5 : THE REMOTE REQUIRES 2X15V (AA) BATTERIES (NOT INCLUDED). PLEASE USE NEW BATTERIES TO ENSURE PROPER WORKING.</p></li><li><p>6 : ENSURE THE RC CAR IS SWITCHED OFF WHILE NOT IN USE.</p></li><li><p>7 : DO NOT PLAY IN WATER TO AVOID MALFUNCTION OF THE CIRCUIT</p></li><li><p>8 : THE PRODUCT CONTAINS SMALL PARTS SUCH AS BATTERIES, BATTERY COVER AND SCREWS THAT MAY CAUSE SUFFOCATION IF SWALLOWED BV CHILDREN.</p></li><li><p>9 : SPECIFICATIONS COLOURS AND CONTENTS MAY VARY FROM ILLUSTRATIONS.</p></li></ol><p></p>', 1099, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a306848f-b4e6-4efc-95e4-d157def1a802.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1499}', '2026-03-11 11:20:25.415983+00', '2026-03-11 11:20:25.415983+00', 'cat_061cfdbf-29d0-4ad7-97b1-39fb9aaf1ca0', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a306848f-b4e6-4efc-95e4-