	('prod_70285447-b6c3-470b-b0e9-f0cb151f8aa0', 'honda-first-generation-nxs-model-car', 'Honda First Generation NXS Model Car', '<ul><li><p>【Lots of fun 】The car has a pull-back function. Pull the toy car backwards a certain distance with your hand, then release your hand and the toy car automatically glides forwards a certain distance. The lights can be switched off, the car seat can be moved forwards and the back of the car can be moved forwards.</p></li><li><p>【Quality Material】 This beautiful toy car is made of zinc alloy, plastic and rubber. High quality materials, non-toxic, harmless and free of formaldehyde, will not cause harm to your children.</p></li><li><p>【Realistic sound and light effects】 There are three different sound effects in total. When you open the door and press the front of the car, various sound effects and dazzling light effects are triggered. Come and enjoy parent-child time in endless laughter.</p></li><li><p>【Gift ideas】 This toy car is a Christmas, birthday and first birthday gift for boys or girls aged three and over. Playing with the toy car can develop your baby''s hands-on skills, activate your baby''s mind and encourage endless discovery and exploration. It is also ideal for car model toy collectors, room decorations and office stress relief toys.</p></li><li><p>【Excellent service】We offer an excellent pre- and after-sales service for the model cars purchased in our shop to make your shopping experience even more enjoyable.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1149, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/76e3bdab-eaeb-49d3-a235-f51b57dff54a.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1549}', '2025-12-28 10:59:13.892799+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:13.892799+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/honda-first-generation-nxs-model-car/26359a9e-7405-4571-95f9-ed81086ed65a.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/76e3bdab-eaeb-49d3-a235-f51b57dff54a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/prod