	('prod_0a42a07f-f29d-43a1-823f-1fcad6100a7a', 'cartoon-car', 'Cartoon Car', '<p>Transformer Robot Car Is Very Strong And Durable And Long Lasting Car | Transformer Car Toy Is Specially Design For The Children | It Can Convert From Car To Robot And Robot To Car Easily With The Help Button | Made Of Non-Toxic Abs Plastic Material Which Is Strong And Durable | Dimensions Are 11.5cm X 7.1cm X 6.1cm | Package Content: 1 Pc Of Robot Toy Car. This Super Speedo Car Has An Adorable Bright Colors Car Which Make It Attractive To Children And Even If Your Kid Bangs It On The Floor, It Wont Break Easily. All Tyres Have Friction Power. It Means It Is A Friction Powered Push And Go Toys. It Is Designed Specially For Baby’s Hands So That They Can Easily To Grasp And Take And Having A Good Playing Time With This Robot Car. It Is 100% Safe And Eco-Friendly And Does Not Required Any Remote Control Or Batteries.<br>Creative Design: Press The Car Front Button And They Automatically Convert Into Transformer Robot Car. It Is A Pull Back Cartoon Toy For Kids. The Finishing Of The Car Toy Looks Like A Funny Vehicle Toy. The Attractive Make And Function Of This Robot Toy Can Engage Your Child Playing And Having Fun In Leisure.<br>🔘 Toy Car To Robot Toy Is Crafted From Premium Quality Plastic Material, This Racing Kid Toy Vehicle Is Durable Enough To Withstand Heavy Use Without Breaking Or Chipping Just Press It Towards Forward, It Will Run And When It Touch With The Wall, It Will Convert Into Robot And Start Revolving On 360 Degree Angle. Kids Will Love Playing With This Toy Gadi For Hours Without Getting Bored.</p><p>Bright colorful vehicles help kids to learn about different colors, vehicles name ,their purpose &amp; shapes. The main function is to enhance their practical ability, artistic cognitive, cognitive ability, imagination and creativity skills</p>', 149, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/cartoon-car/d407eea5-0589-4567-8103-6838afbae7ca.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 299}', '2025-1