	('prod_0c9be6fa-a3b8-493e-b728-bc82bcdadc19', 's11-hoverboard', 'S11+ Hoverboard', '<p><br>FREE ACCESSORIES - Charger, Protection Kit&nbsp;</p><p>DISPLAY SCREEN – Shows Battery, Speed, and Status on LCD.</p><p>BLUETOOTH ENABLED – Play Music while riding with a built-in speaker</p><p>LARGE 11” LED WHEELS – Super smooth ride across even bumpy terrain with Inflatable Tyres.</p><p>HEIGHT ADJUSTABLE HANDLE – 115-140 Cms Adjustable Handle which helps anyone to drive from a small kid to a big adult.</p><p>POWERFUL PERFORMANCE – Race up to 20km/h and climb inclines up to 30 Degrees</p><p>FOR ALL RIDERS – Perfect for all Ages 7+ and up to 100kg Load<br><br></p><p>WEIGHT: 16 kg</p><p>DIMENSIONS: 65 × 32 × 37 cm</p><p>CONTROL BOARD: Fourth Generation Super Intelligent Control Panel with US-based ST Chipsets.</p><p>BATTERY: 158wh 36V Pack with Quick Charge 2.0 Battery Management System</p><p>MOTOR: 300W x 2 Dual Motors – Double Torque (100% Copper)</p><p>TYRE: 10.5" Air Filled Tube Type Tyre (Wheel Cup Also)</p><p>WARRANTY: &nbsp;1-year warranty as per warranty details. (please refer to warranty section)</p><p>CERTIFICATION: CE Certified</p><p>CHARGING TIME: Quick charge 2.0 (1-2 Hours MAX)</p><p>MAXIMUM SPEED: 20Km/h (As per user weight load)</p><p>MAX LOAD CAPACITY: 100kg</p><p>MINIMUM LOAD: 15kg</p><p>BLUETOOTH: YES (Play Music by Connecting with any Bluetooth device)</p><p>FRONT LEDS: YES (White Projectors as well)</p><p>REAR LEDS: YES</p><p>WHEEL ARCH LEDS: NO</p><p>BATTERY INDICATOR: YES (With Display on Handle Bar)</p><p>LED WHEEL: No</p><p>REMOTE: Yes</p><p>MOBILE APP: NO</p><p>BAG: NO</p><p>GRADABILITY: 15Degrees</p><p>MATERIAL: Solid Aluminium Main Frame + ABS Body</p><p>NET WEIGHT: 16kg</p><p>DELIVERY TIME: Ready Stock – Same Day Quick Dispatch (Shipping time 2-4 Business Days)</p><p>ADJUSTABLE HANDLE: Height Adjustable</p><p>PROTECTION KIT: Yes</p>', 22999, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6e459cd2-3ae0-42da-8e64-ba032b3b0178.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 25999}