	('prod_9cc42572-c95e-4aaa-8363-a9c99a68e979', 'g-wagon-police-toy-car', 'G Wagon Police Toy Car', '<ul><li><p>➽ Diecast Metal Car Size: 1/32 scale metal car die cast car model car with display base, Product size: 16.5CM * 6.5CM * 7CM.</p></li><li><p>➽ Function: Pull back model car, engine sound and light. Press the two wheels of the front car to trigger the engine sound and lights, and open the door to trigger the lights of the front and rear lights. Place the car on the ground, hold down the car body and pull it back, the model car will drive forward about 10 meters; Simulation interior, body frosted texture.</p></li><li><p>➽ Material: Made of high-quality''s Metal body with plastic parts, rubber tires, detailed interior and exterior trim. These cars are durable, safe, non-toxic and lead-free toys. Metal car can move. You can trust the quality and use it safely without worrying about your child’s safety.</p></li><li><p>➽ Collectible Pieces: This authentic Metal car model is not just a great toy for kids but it can also be part of your car model collection. The precise detailing and premium finishing touches make this Model X replica a must-have in your toy car display.</p></li><li><p>➽ Great gift and decoration: Very sturdy, fine workmanship, nice toy car, not big, not small. Birthday present and Christmas gifts Toy for boy’s age 2 years old.</p></li></ul>', 1699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fb73a20c-7117-41f0-9d25-16ed2a778789.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 2099}', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.481512+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.481512+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/g-wagon-police-toy-car/6dc68430-c651-40a2-aff5-a75f5cafe6e6.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fb73a20c-7117-41f0-9d25-16ed2a778789.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0c6db5d5-edb1-4c94-88aa-9a8f16cb8854.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9733e4ad-871b-439f-aa4f-43624b9e1268.jpeg,https://cdn.to