	('prod_76669d15-31c5-4f18-9139-412793328057', 'inline-skating', 'Inline Skating', '<p>• Inline Skates are loved by children of all ages and fun for adults, too. Leave the video games and phone inside. Enjoy hours of outdoor fun!<br>• Soft liner provides good sweat absorbent ability, extra padding in the front prevent kid’s toes from hurting.<br>• Adjustable inline skates can be adjusted to different sizes by pushing a button as kid’s feet growing to ensure years of fun. 3 sizes (S/M/L) are available for your choice, please check size chart in the product image and choose the proper size.<br>• Reinforced aluminium alloy frame, ABEC-7 bearings, durable PVC wheels, high rebounded 82A polyurethane heels and rubber (TPR) stopper. High quality skates provide you a smooth, quiet and confident ride</p><p>Illuminating wheels will be lighted up automatically when you start to skate which offers more fun for kids to hangout.</p>', 949, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7bc4670f-43ab-4308-82bf-827616526737.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1299}', '2025-12-28 10:59:13.498203+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:13.498203+00', 'cat_fdb2b9a9-5153-40f2-bfb6-8c92dc02d7c4', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/inline-skating/c1286e47-b7d5-42eb-a5a9-3c016674f96d.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7bc4670f-43ab-4308-82bf-827616526737.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2242fa46-0004-45cd-9d1a-85d9e49619a4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1f65e98c-09b7-49a0-90e9-3a07067607f6.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f4144598-02af-4980-8483-e15ed517479b.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.019667327,-0.038349494,0.032028113,-0.013295709,-0.001038866,0.018435944,-0.011349423,0.020612845,0.057690367,-0.003112679,0.001691737,0.0032516113,-0.081448875,-0.021362752,0.034382075,-0.021593282,0.0043922663,0.024328252,0.014194452,-0.0148450015,-0.074026875,-0.006146953,-0.022369318,0.030192425,-0.022309553,0.009390477,0.08774869,0.001128575,0.03373216,-0.05039