	('prod_764833b9-d0b6-47ab-803b-50c3aadabc3c', 'audi-rs6-alloy-die-cast-car-model-with-door-activated-light-sound-openable-doors-hood-trunk', 'Audi RS6 Alloy Die-Cast Car Model with Door-Activated Light & Sound | Openable Doors, Hood & Trunk', '<ul><li><p>Product Material: This die-cast car model, made of durable materials, such as: die-cast metal and high-quality rubber tires. Beautifully finished inside and out and very sturdy.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Door-Activated Light &amp; Sound – Lights and sound effects turn on automatically when the doors are opened</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Product Size: scale vehicle model, beautifully packaged, very suitable for toddlers to play and carry. Car collectors will appreciate the perfect small size, which allows them to collect an entire collection of cars without taking up too much space.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>No Pull Back Function – This is not a pull-back car; movement does not activate lights or sound</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Openable Parts – Doors, hood, and trunk can be opened for realistic play</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Looks : Original Cars Look &amp; 4x4 four Wheel Drive. Doors can be opened.</p></li><li><p>Lights and Music : Front and Tail lights &amp; Sounds when doors are opened.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/749f770c-f832-4656-8426-2669029e5ba8.jpeg', 200, '{"compare_at_price": null}', '2026-03-25 06:41:21.620301+00', '2026-03-25 06:41:21.620301+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/749f770c-f832-4656-8426-2669029e5ba8.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/22f16026-1a09-4da3-b7f3-b38826b57d3e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/22f88d0a-659b-4e47-8aef-e6c08de4878d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/239cf4ef-3ab2-479e-b7d3-20211cff22ac.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9f2730bf-bab4-4bc2-b3ca-1315fa45f638.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5