	('prod_3185c2ce-8df0-42bc-a71e-29e085b42502', 'wooden-blocks-coloring-zenga-toy-small', 'Wooden Blocks Coloring Zenga Toy (Small)', '<p>It’s the perfect game for everyone that is sturdy and floor game which promotes friendship, communication and logic between players. Only using one hand to remove blocks helps hand-eye coordination and self-control.&nbsp;It utilizes skills taught in math (counting blocks), science (engineering and stabilizing a structure), social studies (social skill development), language arts (communication skill development), health (stress relief through fun and laughter) and physical education (motor skill development)</p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a2fda77a-4f0f-489d-958a-92a7b1f69465.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 549}', '2025-12-28 10:59:22.893362+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:22.893362+00', 'cat_19958301-f61f-4ea4-9a5a-5af9fe70808e', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/wooden-blocks-coloring-zenga-toy-small/498ba563-4f7a-40d2-ba11-d21b180ffe95.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a2fda77a-4f0f-489d-958a-92a7b1f69465.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b854a1ac-5412-43f9-85b3-e9386aae7742.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/277f18f3-3d3b-48b3-8e68-5f14891b9767.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/36c002fc-d322-4c2e-ad55-5066050d2ccb.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e27dc67b-d7ea-424a-8007-6370e9206b0b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/eafc1fef-931f-409c-b5b5-6cbe15e26580.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.009271927,-0.03283194,0.019962339,0.018591974,0.010206482,-0.040603694,0.027582746,0.030364105,0.014406869,0.048245057,-0.020214668,-0.014951432,-0.029043231,-0.04335916,0.013886253,-0.0088896975,-0.08333734,-0.014041109,-0.042820822,-0.06731624,0.0019264304,0.009501287,0.052594267,0.029695552,0.0022691858,0.045938462,0.035671107,0.024548853,-0.012368246,0.06392288,-0.0023087512,-0.008431869,0.01969871,0.025978899,0.022058517,-0.04850721,-0.02204624,0.049824454,0.00052911