	('prod_1754b549-f3e8-4bf7-9745-ea91d529896d', 'launcher-bike', 'Launcher Bike', '<p>This pull-back motorcycle toy with a launcher provides an exciting speed challenge, delivering thrilling action with every launch. Designed with a friction-powered mechanism, this racing bike play set allows for effortless movement without the need for batteries, ensuring continuous fun. The two-wheel design enables smooth motion across different surfaces, making it suitable for both indoor and outdoor play. Crafted for durability, the structure withstands repeated use while maintaining performance. The interactive launcher adds an extra layer of excitement, enabling high-speed action with a simple pull-back motion. The compact size ensures easy handling, allowing for convenient portability and storage. Featuring a dynamic design, this play set encourages interaction, keeping engagement levels high through every race. The sturdy build ensures resilience against impacts, making it a reliable option for extended play. With an intuitive mechanism,</p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/52eb2331-852c-4a2c-b834-d47d4d80285d.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 499}', '2025-12-28 10:59:13.092069+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:13.092069+00', 'cat_08a7eeb8-150f-4240-96a2-6b19edba0667', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/launcher-bike/a71b79eb-5714-4c60-8152-a94c26c87189.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/52eb2331-852c-4a2c-b834-d47d4d80285d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5e2c56bb-8dee-4c1a-b887-f73f74ecc639.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9851cff2-1a91-4bea-87b9-dba7b9d18b51.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c5257082-3730-404c-ac93-7a3032e435fa.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.012027103,0.00497235,0.0134931775,0.004611723,0.021730121,0.031793933,-0.0010645052,0.02321297,-0.0027329128,-0.0073351683,0.020882903,0.002569267,0.02366986,-0.014261214,0.04339892,-0.0055354326,0.05358606,0.0411119,0.0065474804,-0.05027435,-0.026859418,