	('prod_7c08031a-ce16-42e1-8967-f27c1943fa37', '3-in-1-mini-pull-back-spinning-gyro-toy-childrens-gift-ring-combat-plastic-watch-spinning-body-interactive-gyro-toys', '3-In-1 Mini Pull Back Spinning Gyro Toy Children''S Gift Ring Combat Plastic Watch Spinning Body Interactive Gyro Toys', '<p>Make every moment more exciting with this adorable Kids Fire Car Spinner Watch. Designed with a cute cartoon fire car look, this toy is more than just a watch – it is a spinning top and a two-way pull-back car in one.</p><p></p><p>The watch features a strong and flexible adjustable strap that fits comfortably on children’s wrists. Kids can easily remove the toy from the strap and enjoy spinning it or racing it like a mini fire car. Its lightweight and child-friendly design make it perfect for everyday play.</p><p></p><p>Made from high-quality ABS plastic, this kids toy watch is durable, safe, and built to handle regular use. The included accessories allow children to change the design and enjoy different ways to play.</p><p></p><p>This fun and interactive spinner watch is a great choice for birthday gifts, return gifts, school prizes, party favors, and everyday entertainment.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Product Features</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Multi-functional 2-in-1 kids toy</p></li><li><p>Converts from wrist watch to spinning top toy</p></li><li><p>Two-way pull-back fire car action</p></li><li><p>Adjustable strap for a perfect fit</p></li><li><p>Comfortable and lightweight design</p></li><li><p>Made from durable ABS plastic</p></li><li><p>Includes extra accessories for more fun</p></li><li><p>Suitable for boys and girls</p></li><li><p></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Product Size</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Watch Strap Length: 22.5 cm</p></li><li><p>Strap Width: 4.5 cm</p></li><li><p>Toy Size: 4.8 cm x 3.5 cm</p></li></ul><p></p>', 199, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a47dc378-a07d-446e-a726-35324fb1fac6.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2026-03-31 06:14:27.813841+00', '2026-03-31 06:1