	('prod_5d547963-fd3c-4666-a142-c6381460228c', '42-pcs-fashion-kitchen-set', '42 pcs Fashion Kitchen set', '<p>Interactive Play Kitchen Set: This play kitchen set for kids includes realistic features like a functioning sink with running water, stove, cookware, blackboard, play food, and other accessories. It also has built-in storage spaces for convenient organizatio.;Realistic Cooking Experience: When the stove is turned on, it produces realistic cooking Gas sounds and lights up. Additionally, lifelike steam adds to the authenticity, providing children with a more immersive cooking experience.<br>• Educational Water Circulation System: The sink toy is equipped with a water circulation system. Kids can wash play food before cooking and clean utensils after, promoting awareness of water conservation through play and fostering environmental consciousness.<br>Imagination and Creativity Development: The multifunctional kitchen toy encourages children to play the role of a chef, enhancing their imagination, creativity, and hands-on skills. Involving parents or friends can create a delightful family bonding experience.</p>', 1199, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/42-pcs-fashion-kitchen-set/ce969419-f4a7-4719-a28b-a4bb1cba30ff.jpg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1499}', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.960335+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.960335+00', 'cat_7d7907ef-9aab-435c-a230-a5f52ab93cd5', 'col_64ba526c-0c27-4be8-bea3-3fbc9d30ffc2', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/42-pcs-fashion-kitchen-set/43fc29ca-fccb-4453-8f40-658d7d68e053.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/42-pcs-fashion-kitchen-set/ce969419-f4a7-4719-a28b-a4bb1cba30ff.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/42-pcs-fashion-kitchen-set/2a035cb9-c25c-482a-aea7-6af8013f9326.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/42-pcs-fashion-kitchen-set/ae8942fb-e032-48dc-95d0-42e66435204d.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/42-pcs-fashion-kitchen-set/58beef34-3d2b-4e9a-9924-83a9b615ce4e.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/42-pcs-fashion-kitchen-set