	('prod_91f9af5f-0d70-483a-b359-8ae3c401e9d9', '150-piece-color-art-set', '150 Piece Color (Art) Set', '<ul><li><p>You can achieve an eye-catching and appealing piece of artwork by using a variety of colors.</p></li><li><p>Wide Application: The art set has a variety of types and colors making it ideal for multipurpose usage. Sketching, drawing, coloring, illustration, calligraphy, hand lettering, mixed media art, craft projects, writing, doodles, thumbnail sketches, preliminary drawings, coloring books, color theory practice, and highlighting.</p></li><li><p>Portable Case: The carrying case has colorful prints making it extremely visually appealing. Simply place all of the drawing supplies within the portable case and take this art set with you. The handle has the right amount of weight so that you won’t be burdened too much while carrying it. The handle of the case has a smooth surface making it easier to carry. The case has a buckle lock that ensures your bag stays securely fixed.</p></li><li><p>Ideal Gift: This art and craft set of colors has all the coloring materials that are required to produce an excellent piece of artwork. Hence this can be considered a perfect present for art lovers or beginners on special occasions such as birthdays, parties, festivals, and holidays, and also as a return gift.</p></li></ul>', 449, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/150-piece-color-art-set/1ba2ec8f-9438-4ee1-b459-6bc01617db30.jpg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.76041+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.76041+00', 'cat_b5e5b995-e9b1-49ee-913a-a07cb90b83e4', 'col_04bb80c5-eeb4-4ae7-bfdd-2c8f71f76f95', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/150-piece-color-art-set/2b86a26d-af4a-429b-9c83-687f9f3fd0ca.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/150-piece-color-art-set/1ba2ec8f-9438-4ee1-b459-6bc01617db30.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/150-piece-color-art-set/59dbdd5c-2af4-4349-bd89-e1cc54bd6255.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/150-piece-color-art-set/638bc14d-975