	('prod_71886568-15a3-4ae5-86c0-ca9ce7cfca6a', 'premium-stainless-steel-kitchen-stand-play-set-for-kids-with-dish-rack-gas-stove-and-36-pieces', 'Premium Stainless Steel Kitchen Stand Play Set for Kids with Dish Rack, Gas Stove & 36 Pieces', '<p>Get Ready for Kitchen Adventures!</p><p>Introducing the Kitchen Stand PlaySet – the ultimate pretend play set for LITTLE chefs with BIG imaginations! With 34 exciting pieces, including a cool pretend gas stove, this set will keep you cooking up fun all day long. That''s why every mini chef needs this in their play kitchen!</p><p></p><p>What''s Cooking in the Set?</p><p>Pretend Gas Stove – Sizzle and stir like a real chef with your very own stovetop!</p><p></p><p>36 Pieces of Fun – From pots and pans to utensils and plates, you''ll have everything you need to serve up the perfect imaginary meal.</p><p></p><p>Realistic Kitchen Accessories – whisks, spatulas, ladles, and more to make your pretend cooking feels just like the real deal!</p><p></p><p>Why You''ll Love It:</p><p>Perfect for Little Hands – Each piece is designed for easy handling, so even the smallest chefs can enjoy cooking like pros!</p><p>Encourages Creative Play – Get your imagination cooking as you whip up fun dishes and host your own pretend dinner parties.</p><p></p><p>Fun for Friends &amp; Family – Invite your friends over for make-believe meals, or cook up a storm for your favorite dolls and stuffed animals.</p><p></p><p>Learn While You Play – Practice sharing, role-playing, and problem-solving, all while having loads of fun in the kitchen!</p><p></p><p>Safe, Durable, and Ready for Action:</p><p>Kid-Safe Materials – Made from high-quality, child-friendly materials, so parents can rest easy while the fun goes on.</p><p>Built to Last – Durable enough to handle all the excitement of pretend play – even the busiest little chefs!<br></p><p>Product Contents List :</p><p>Item Name Quantity</p><p>Kitchen Stand 1 no</p><p>Gas Stove 1 no</p><p>Cylinder with Pipe 1 no</p><p>Toy Cooker 1 no</p><p>Container 2 nos</p><p>Bucket 1 no</p><p>Pot 1 no</p><p>Pot Lid 1 no</p><p>Tea Cup 4 nos</p><p>Tea Saucer 4 nos</p><p>Plates 4 nos</p><p>Vattis 4 nos</p><p>Glass 4 nos</p><p>Spoon 4 nos</p><p>Pakkad 1 no</p><p>Patla 1 no (Free)</p><p>Belan 1 no (Free)</p><p>--- ---</p><p>Total 36 nos<br></p>', 2099, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cfc6833b-9463-45fa-b5d5-56bddc65737a.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2599}', '2026-04-04 12:34:08.465989+00', '2026-04-04 12:34:08.465989+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cfc6833b-9463-45fa-b5d5-56bddc65737a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0b9ffb45-bf11-4203-9158-865752f165c8.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3ff895b9-53cc-4cb0-8dd0-c7bb287ccaf4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5a69eb75-198a-415e-a77a-1f9b621c19d8.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d7561416-65e5-41b6-8955-607255e49cf6.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a17e2259-0f0d-4d45-8283-462d17837c1e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f75f0072-df7b-4142-9ae6-28d8f1a1099b.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Get Ready for Kitchen Adventures!,
