	('prod_b363bac8-ab54-41aa-83b6-aa5d552a7119', 'kids-ride-on-push-car-with-music-lights-and-storage-comfortable-seat-toy', 'Kids Ride-On Push Car with Music, Lights & Storage – Comfortable Seat Toy', '<p>Make your child’s playtime more fun and active with this Kids Ride-On Push Car. Built with a lightweight yet strong body, this ride-on toy is perfect for toddlers to enjoy smooth and safe riding indoors and outdoors.</p><p>It features a comfortable seat that provides better balance and support, making it an ideal toy for beginners. The attractive car design with a sporty look adds excitement, while the built-in music and lights keep kids entertained during play.</p><p>The ride-on also includes a hidden storage compartment under the seat, allowing kids to carry their favorite small toys and essentials wherever they go. The thickened anti-slip wheels ensure better grip and stability, making it safe for everyday use.</p><p>This ride-on toy helps improve balance, coordination, and motor skills while encouraging active play. It is a perfect gift choice for birthdays, special occasions, and daily fun.</p><p></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lightweight and durable body</p></li><li><p>Comfortable seat for better balance</p></li><li><p>Built-in music and lights</p></li><li><p>Hidden storage space under the seat</p></li><li><p>Anti-slip wheels for safety and stability</p></li><li><p>Attractive sporty car design</p></li><li><p>Suitable for indoor and outdoor use</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1599, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/021f0b25-3acf-45b7-9e10-f72c7c4b774b.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2099}', '2026-04-11 10:20:05.521065+00', '2026-04-11 10:20:05.521065+00', 'cat_708a2e4c-0188-4975-bb35-61045f1c32bd', 'col_d27f16c3-8935-41d9-90af-5895ffef1e0c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/021f0b25-3acf-45b7-9e10-f72c7c4b774b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/29a9c9b6-453f-43d5-a0c3-7b424ea4c2e0.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2079ac32-cf47-42ca-b02e-34ba180cc0fe.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ab38fac8-4ac2-40cd-b1ac-d4f0c3582a5c.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a243d671-ecb8-4ba8-afee-58bb1352f4b4.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Stylish ride-on push car for kids with music, lights, and under-seat storage. Designed with a comfortable seat and anti-slip wheels for safe and fun playtime.', '', '[0.01017105,-0.020232575,0.014707275,0.01576334,0.09107188,0.011428169,0.042427823,0.017504342,-0.028766032,0.009137831,0.024950624,-0.0035408356,0.025625024,-0.027011557,0.06971926,-0.01642881,0.05347654,0.020208154,0.016707838,-0.021270648,0.022755142,0.02211578,0.0199914,0.047918573,0.027743604,-0.0042923377,0.050770905,0.010833086,-0.027967349,-0.026213206,0.026857598,-0.014093648,0.0072353836,0.019959854,-0.012037312,-0.03206496,-0.021920126,-0.006219346,0.063200705,0.021442462,-0.024079172,0.07066222,0.0005092726,-0.040499076,0.009931288,-0.080843806,0.021415949,-0.066512726,-0.017515823,-0.010848999,-0.029593505,-0.021587575,-0.00673778,-0.0025400901,-0.028063511,-0.0650574,-0.014870491,-0.029912867,0.005747969,-0.028618453,0.042791113,-0.041598637,-0.032771137,0.033759896,-0.020688178,-0.0021216024,-0.020756138,0.016394638,0.034462858,-0.02352008,-0.013505136,-0.016929377,-0.008781735,-0.03465617,0.014922147,0.0016730585,0.015934493,-0.01525398,0.041002464,0.006037493,0.02633179,0.01769473,-0.037297044,-0.01787182,-0.020688737,0.011931284,0.043029167,0.007145736,-0.005975299,-0.0019355837,0.017897954,-0.11670385,-0.54233485,0.016315497,-0.019137407,-0.02501374,-0.028417932,0.030533463,0.01815292,0.08640317,0.065907344,-5.4568693e-05,0.034154408,0.029329084,-0.09294941,-0.06310522,-0.13169242,0.01539691,0.051557023,-0.03385142,0.06717284,0.048596725,0.01829438,0.02536803,0.030693648,0.0407312,-0.0022967577,-0.017679423,0.025885029,-0.040713307,0.039681707,0.03567096,-0.103240885,0.0054393937,-0.0046826433,0.009523124,-0.017724289,0.017104834,-0.0057274317,-0.0143379215,-0.013228481,-0.07109645,-0.01632357,0.08