	('prod_1629d94d-9d1a-4645-b4c8-f9fda51514ba', '5d-flashing-light-musical-balance-toy-with-dancing-girl-360-rotating-bump-and-go-car', '5D Flashing Light Musical Balance Toy with Dancing Girl – 360° Rotating Bump & Go Car', '<p>Make playtime magical with this 5D Flashing Light Musical Balance Toy featuring a cute dancing girl. Designed with vibrant LED lighting effects and built-in music, this toy creates a fun and engaging environment for kids.</p><p>The smart bump-and-go technology allows the toy to automatically change direction when it hits obstacles, while the 360° rotating wheels ensure smooth movement in all directions. The adorable girl figure on top adds charm and excitement as it moves along with the toy, making it visually appealing for children.</p><p>With glowing lights on both the wheels and side elements, this toy creates a stunning visual effect, especially in dim lighting. It operates on 3 AA batteries, making it easy to use anytime, anywhere.</p><p>Made from safe, durable, and child-friendly materials, this toy helps improve hand-eye coordination, motor skills, and sensory development. It is an ideal gift for birthdays, festivals, or special occasions and guarantees hours of fun for kids.</p>', 550, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/14f8ace9-7ace-4f1e-91df-e296876a65fa.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2026-04-14 11:55:52.396734+00', '2026-04-14 11:55:52.396734+00', 'cat_be92f917-7267-474d-9af6-69564702507a', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/14f8ace9-7ace-4f1e-91df-e296876a65fa.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/572cce65-ba40-4570-b8ca-5fc806dbf500.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/31b06f98-28c8-425b-845f-562d9d22899b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4a867fa2-2e44-4de1-8719-145c945c0eaf.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1a382966-6a36-49dc-87e8-bbd86fe52b23.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Colorful musical balance toy with 5D flashing lights and a cute dancing girl. Features 360° sp