	('prod_fb73a6d3-91a3-4265-b6f6-f5c0b10c280e', 'durable-musical-mother-duck-ducklings-toy-crawling-baby-development-tummy-time-gift-made-of-plastic-for-valentines-baby-shower', 'Durable Musical Mother Duck & Ducklings Toy Crawling Baby Development Tummy Time Gift Made of Plastic for Valentines Baby Shower', '<ul><li><p>Soft Light, Fun Music and Lullabies: press the start button, it will play a cheerful melody and swing forward to move forward; at night you can start the light button with lullabies. This will exercise your baby''s sense of hearing and also bring good sleep.</p></li><li><p>Multiple Modes for Fun: Two modes of play: 1. Follow mode, where three ducks are connected to each other and the two ducklings follow the mummy duck as they move forward together; 2. Spin mode, where the two ducklings are placed together with the switch on and will perform a fun spin together. Multiple modes encourage baby to discover, crawl and chase.</p></li><li><p>Waddling Cute Duck: The duck waddles and glides across the floor, bringing curious fun to your baby. Your baby will love the duckling with the cheerful tune of the children''s song. This fun toy is suitable for 18+ months and up.</p></li><li><p>Durable Shock-Proof Material: This duck baby musical toy is made of shock-proof material, which will not be easily damaged even if it is bumped or accidentally dropped on the floor by your baby, and it is sturdy enough to be durable.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1099, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/07edf827-1bcd-446c-b2ae-4f80bbb03a36.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": null}', '2026-01-28 05:02:55.744932+00', '2026-01-28 05:02:55.744932+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/07edf827-1bcd-446c-b2ae-4f80bbb03a36.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/667aeee9-60d6-496f-a1ee-732909aa35a5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fba75e97-3aad-46eb-a60d-6730d6d7fdd9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in