	('prod_19440bd6-37e0-47c8-b6bb-f8b1ceb2af22', 'premium-die-cast-off-road-jeep-toy-car-with-light-sound-openable-doors-pull-back-action-model-suv-for-kids-collectors', 'Premium Die-Cast Off-Road Jeep Toy Car with Light & Sound, Openable Doors, Pull Back Action Model SUV for Kids & Collectors', '<p>Bring adventure home with this premium die-cast off-road SUV Jeep toy car, crafted for both play and display. Designed with a strong metal body and rugged detailing, this model delivers a realistic experience with openable doors, bonnet, and trunk, along with removable roof accessories that enhance its off-road appeal.</p><p>The car features interactive light and sound effects activated by pressing the steering wheel, making it engaging and fun for kids. Equipped with pull-back action, four-wheel shock absorbers, and detailed interiors, it ensures smooth movement and durability.</p><p>Perfect for gifting, kids’ playtime, or collectors, this stylish SUV model combines performance, realism, and premium quality in one unique piece.</p>', 1699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a800de2e-ed1d-4697-87f6-36e3d9dc9979.jpeg', 100, '{"compare_at_price": null}', '2026-03-25 07:28:47.041097+00', '2026-03-25 07:28:47.041097+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a800de2e-ed1d-4697-87f6-36e3d9dc9979.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/578b86ea-0516-4e02-bdf6-80777e78ae1f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/346dd019-316e-4473-93c5-ed42f7800cbb.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e62de869-2d41-45cf-b92e-6113ac829a23.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/86a9db44-4cb1-44ee-8a9a-9c6cc38b6eff.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1c8af763-6b66-4073-98f1-f9a4c43394e4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/25d3a599-421b-4d25-b65b-6cf448bcec39.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5b38c999-b11c-432b-9124-033ebe7f9090.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Realistic die-cast off-road Jeep toy car with openable do