	('prod_57fb31b0-6968-4c64-b105-17f874811e1e', 'attacker-6-gun', 'Attacker 6 Gun', '<ul><li><p>This toy gun Or air gun promotes skill development by improving hand-eye coordination and precision. Children can hone their aiming abilities by shooting at imaginary targets or creating their own target board, Automatic Muzzle Rotates When you Pull Loader, Games for kids fostering skill improvement through play. bullet gun boy is the first choice for gun toys for kids 7 – 15 Yrs</p></li><li><p>6-DART ROTATING DRUM: Shake up the competition with the DartX Attacker Blaster, unleashing a rapid-fire onslaught of 6 darts in succession from its rotating, 6-dart drum! Load up the front of the drum with 6 darts, then dive into a whirlwind of excitement. Designed with safety in mind, it includes 6 soft bullets Dart that have a harmless impact. That great for indoor Games and outdoor play and are tested and approved for performance and quality.</p></li><li><p>RAPID SLAM-FIRE ACTION: Fire one dart at a time or unleash all 6 darts in rapid succession! Pull back the Loader slide and press the trigger for single shots, or hold down the trigger while pumping the Loader slide for rapid slam-fire action.The Super Cool Shooting fun provided by this toy gun is suitable for the whole family. The Hot Fire soft bullets can reach a range of 30ft, providing a real fun and engaging shooting experience.</p></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/attacker-6-gun/8617fe7b-0d68-4ee7-abe1-4dd1ac411ba8.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 499}', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.879041+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.879041+00', NULL, 'col_aa4de5eb-e030-4296-a866-7520c2b1a3e6', 'draft', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/attacker-6-gun/56224343-c5a2-451e-aabf-9259b3c10f3a.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/attacker-6-gun/8617fe7b-0d68-4ee7-abe1-4dd1ac411ba8.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/attacker-6-gun/0dbb6217-af56-4453-bce0-c06d01af1d7e.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/attacker-6-gun/112e9d6a-d5