	('prod_4d305db1-5f1d-4719-8918-829e0de7cef4', 'electronic-piano-keyboard', 'Electronic Piano Keyboard', '<p>INTRODUCE YOUR CHILD TO THE WONDERFUL WORLD OF MUSIC WITH THIS ELECTRONIC KEYBOARD PIANO. THIS ELECTRONIC KEYBOARD HAS 37 KEYS AND IS DESIGNED FOR BOTH BOYS AND GIRLS.37 KEY KEYBOARD PIANO IS A PROFESSIONAL EDUCATIONAL MUSICAL PIANO TOY, CAN DEVELOP THE KIDS SENSITIVITY OF MUSIC AND CULTIVATES MUSIC INTEREST AND SENSE OF MUSIC.8 RHYTHMS, INCLUDING ROCK, SLOW ROCK, TWIST, DISCO, MARCH, WALTZ, SAMBA, BLUES, ENCOURAGING KIDS TO EXPLORE DIFFERENT SOUND COMBINATIONS. THIS TOY HELPS YOUR CHILD WITH HAND-EYE COORDINATION, MUSICAL THEORY AND FINE MOTOR SKILLS AMONG OTHER IMPORTANT SKILLS</p><p>. FEATURES:- 37 KEYS, 8 TONES, 8 RHYTHMS, MP3 FUNCTION, 6 DEMOS, VOLUME CONTROL, TEMPO CONTROL, SONG RECORDER, SONG PLAY.</p><p>. ONE SIDE IS SPEAKER AND OTHER SIDE IS JUST FOR SHOW,COMES WITH ONE SPEAKER BEST FOR KID.</p><p>. CONNECT DC POWER ADAPTER TO PLAY ON DC POWER. POWER SAVING MODE: IT CAN BE EASILY POWERED ON BY CONNECTING DC POWER ADAPTER OF 5V OR BY USB CABLE CONNECTED WITH ANY COMPUTER OR EVEN POWER BANKS</p>', 699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6e728390-5d7f-4169-898d-06e231e445a1.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 899}', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.489958+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.489958+00', 'cat_8db61611-edb7-441f-92a1-5bc5dd91b15b', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/electronic-piano-keyboard/9ab021e0-10d2-4ab2-b7aa-27df62b31091.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6e728390-5d7f-4169-898d-06e231e445a1.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2a7e137f-baf9-4359-af08-0531806834ba.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/83c51d8e-5a15-4b08-98e4-b51e2692ae58.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e93a2aa7-3d98-4cc9-8d41-8e8ec7741260.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.064890474,-0.009757376,0.008861958,0.0019996425,0.0534728,0.009358909,0.018793618,0.0077200215,-0.029373813,-0.00055900967,0.0034673864,-0.0011348963,0.02902389,-0.0