	('prod_7cdcc8ea-6954-4236-837a-2ea2e6b11c08', 'crinkling-fabric-book-6-part-1', 'Crinkling Fabric Book 6 ( part 1 ) ', '<p>Make learning fun for your little one with this <strong>Crinkling Fabric Book Set for Kids</strong>. This set includes <strong>6 soft cloth books</strong> designed specially for babies and toddlers to explore the world around them. Each book features bright colors, cute illustrations, and crinkling sounds that attract children’s attention and make learning interactive.</p><p>The set covers different learning topics such as <strong>Animals, Fruits, Vehicles, Body Parts, Birds, and Shapes &amp; Colors</strong>, helping kids build strong basic concepts at an early age. The soft fabric material is <strong>safe, lightweight, and easy for little hands to hold</strong>, making it perfect for both home learning and preschool activities.</p><p>These books help improve <strong>language development, visual recognition, and sensory skills</strong> while encouraging curiosity and creativity. It is an ideal educational toy for <strong>early childhood learning and brain development</strong>.</p>', 549, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9ae54feb-6613-4910-8889-15956e2fa1a0.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 849}', '2026-03-11 11:53:02.754111+00', '2026-03-11 11:53:02.754111+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9ae54feb-6613-4910-8889-15956e2fa1a0.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ab444a91-dfb6-45d0-bcc2-87b966c5fe40.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4e55c9e2-e54a-4b8b-8688-bd9654dddc02.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9bdb1fcb-49d4-4905-b0cd-9e3ed0b373e0.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/74bc4466-7696-47b6-956b-e51ecdd07b9c.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fb8407e4-62e8-4e46-a644-08af097fc732.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Introduce your child to fun learning with this Crinkling Fabric Book Set of 6. These soft cloth books help kids learn about animal