	('prod_e3de203a-746a-4602-b7c1-8f704e0ae71c', 'bugatti-atlantic-model-car-sports-car', 'Bugatti Atlantic Model Car Sports Car', '<ul><li><p>➤【ALLOY DIECAST METAL CAR】: The collectible toy car model has the powerful functions, which the Childhood, tail and the doors can be opened. Also have the standard quality pull back function, you can pull back the car and then it will driving with strong Power. The simulation of the car makes the car look beautiful and cool!</p></li><li><p>➤【OPENING FEATURES OF METAL CAR TOY】: Car doors and trunk can be opened on the metal car toy, accompanied by lights and sounds. The rear wheels are equipped with pull-back power.</p></li><li><p>➤【LIGHT SOUND AND MUSIC】: Front and tail lights activate, along with sounds, when the doors of the metal car toy are opened.</p></li><li><p>➤【GREAT GIFT AND DECORATION】: Diecast Metal Toy Car Very sturdy, fine workmanship, nice toy car, not big, not small. Birthday present Vacation Diwali Holiday Gift and Christmas gifts Toy for boy’s age 2 and Above years old. Perfect gifts for kids. Colors will be dispatched as per availibility.</p></li><li><p>➤【MADE OF PREMIUM METAL CAR】: The material of the metal car toy Made of Premium Metal Car Toy ensures a flawless finish .</p></li></ul>', 1649, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d2987e73-1e20-4074-9609-c4ff7e9a5fa6.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:07.533116+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:07.533116+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bugatti-atlantic-model-car-sports-car/1cd4ab68-9dfb-4dfc-9a07-bceca20419dc.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d2987e73-1e20-4074-9609-c4ff7e9a5fa6.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/09d743d7-1ed6-4548-b06b-60abf21c408a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6ec7a573-3c35-4302-a011-fabebb15c84a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fd3137fb-1e2c-42b1-bc11-2322b97d7e1b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2005dcd3-e8