	('prod_2629ed71-94fe-4b08-b2f2-94de2998b76a', 'die-cast-metal-farm-truck-with-trolley', 'Die Cast Metal Farm Truck With Trolley', '<ul><li><p>Farm Truck: Push the friction truck forward slightly then it go and last for quite a long distance. It is made according to the model of a real farm truck which can give children a real experience and a better understanding of the world. No battery required. children can play the vehicles freely and safely without parent’s supervision.</p></li><li><p>★Endless Fun For your Kids: It does not require any batteries. It’s a fun and handy toy set for kids. With a good push and automatic rotating function, this toy cars can easily run for a long distance. This Farm park tuck is useful for training and development of hands and fingertips.</p></li><li><p>★Educational Toy: It is an educational toy that fosters imagination, practical skill, cognitive ability and creativity at the same time as pleasure to complete. With small and perfect size for children little hands, easy to grasp and no sharp edges, suitable for children over 3 years old – young children, preschool children, kindergartens</p></li><li><p>★Perfect Gift For Your Kids: This makes the perfect gift truck car set for any young farming and construction. This Farm Truck Toy set will help develop creativity and analytical skills as they set a goal to build their own farm. This truck boasts bright colors and working moveable parts to early motor skills and sensory processing development</p></li><li><p>★Friction powered (NO Batteries Required) for a fun and handy toy set for kids. With a good push and automatic rotating function, this toy cars can easily run for a long distance.</p></li></ul>', 469, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/37e22a7b-69d4-4dcb-a10b-144311f9df82.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 699}', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.298188+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:11.298188+00', 'cat_b5def22d-1e67-41f1-be01-69546a25ce20', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', 'https://cd