	('prod_3bcf71e9-7c5b-41ea-a857-5276296ae779', 'kids-ride-on-balance-car-with-music-lights-and-storage-lightweight-2kg-baby-push-car-toy', 'Kids Ride-On Balance Car with Music, Lights & Storage – Lightweight 2kg Baby Push Car Toy', '<p>Make your child’s playtime more fun and active with this Kids Ride-On Push Car. Built with a lightweight yet strong body, this ride-on toy is perfect for toddlers to enjoy smooth and safe riding indoors and outdoors.</p><p>It features a comfortable seat that provides better balance and support, making it an ideal toy for beginners. The attractive car design with a sporty look adds excitement, while the built-in music and lights keep kids entertained during play.</p><p>The ride-on also includes a hidden storage compartment under the seat, allowing kids to carry their favorite small toys and essentials wherever they go. The thickened anti-slip wheels ensure better grip and stability, making it safe for everyday use.</p><p>This ride-on toy helps improve balance, coordination, and motor skills while encouraging active play. It is a perfect gift choice for birthdays, special occasions, and daily fun.</p><p></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lightweight and durable body</p></li><li><p>Comfortable seat for better balance</p></li><li><p>Built-in music and lights</p></li><li><p>Hidden storage space under the seat</p></li><li><p>Anti-slip wheels for safety and stability</p></li><li><p>Attractive sporty car design</p></li><li><p>Suitable for indoor and outdoor use</p></li></ul><p></p>', 950, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/02a5d49f-c858-4202-9cec-686d0aff859e.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2026-04-11 10:22:30.973338+00', '2026-04-11 10:22:30.973338+00', 'cat_708a2e4c-0188-4975-bb35-61045f1c32bd', 'col_d27f16c3-8935-41d9-90af-5895ffef1e0c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/02a5d49f-c858-4202-9cec-686d0aff859e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5a29bb63-7c9f-4584-8129-274990f6f124.jpeg,https://cdn.toycke