	('prod_ee7bbe84-e097-4303-b2b9-091b41e5a823', 'barbie-kitchen-and-dining-stainless-steel-play-set-for-kids-24-piece-mini-cooking-toy-set-with-stove-cooker-and-utensils', 'Barbie Kitchen & Dining Stainless Steel Play Set for Kids – 24 Piece Mini Cooking Toy Set with Stove, Cooker & Utensils', '<h1>Bring home the perfect pretend play experience with the Barbie Kitchen &amp; Dining Play Set. This premium 24-piece kitchen toy set is specially designed for kids who love cooking and role play. The set includes a realistic mini gas stovetop, pressure cooker, frying pan, saucepan, lidded pot, stainless steel bowls, cups, spoons, spatula and decorative Barbie stickers.</h1><p></p><p>Made from high-quality stainless steel, each piece is strong, safe and reusable, giving children a realistic feel while they play. The attractive Barbie-themed box and colorful stickers make this set even more exciting for young girls. It helps improve imagination, creativity, hand-eye coordination and social skills through fun kitchen role play.</p><p></p><p>Perfect for gifting on birthdays, return gifts or special occasions, this Barbie kitchen set is ideal for kids who dream of becoming little chefs.</p><p></p>', 1899, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/115a5dc6-1165-49f0-b405-3579c6b79358.jpeg', 100, '{"compare_at_price": 2599}', '2026-04-03 12:08:22.256071+00', '2026-04-03 12:08:22.256071+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/115a5dc6-1165-49f0-b405-3579c6b79358.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9ee77541-823e-45c9-b8f9-e082e39790f8.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/999ae14b-3e93-4070-9d62-f746f46f40b1.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b3d48daf-6d93-42d9-bc89-aedbcf8d6851.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/307fdbe9-0c3e-4e94-836c-26cb78aa9933.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/94eeea01-e45e-4630-b549-c2698e29f4f6.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/542d1f67-8783-4243-9bbb-1e7d