	('prod_2df98744-423b-4aac-bcaf-a2f14bf2eca5', 'cute-turtle-shell-shin-chan-plush-toy-childrens-bed-doll-pillow', 'Cute Turtle Shell Shin-Chan Plush Toy, Children''s Bed Doll Pillow', '<p>Meet the adorable TinyTotem Shinchan Soft Toy in Turtle Costume, the perfect blend of fun, nostalgia, and softness! Designed with attention to every detail, this plush toy brings everyone’s favorite cartoon character to life in a cute, cuddly, and creative form. Whether you’re a fan of Shinchan or just love collecting cute plushies, this toy will instantly become your favorite cuddle buddy. 🌟 Playful &amp; Unique Design This plush features Shinchan in an adorable turtle costume — a creative twist that makes it stand out from ordinary toys. From the big expressive eyes to the surprised facial expression and green turtle shell, every feature captures the mischievous charm of Shinchan perfectly. It’s a delightful collectible for kids, anime fans, and plush lovers. 💖 Premium Softness &amp; Comfort Made with ultra-soft velvet plush fabric, this toy offers an incredibly gentle and fluffy feel. The PP-cotton filling provides the perfect huggable texture, making it comforting to hold and play with. Its squishy design is ideal for kids to snuggle during bedtime or for adults looking for a stress-relief plushie. 🧵 Safe for Kids &amp; Toddlers At TinyTotem, safety always comes first. This plush toy is made with non-toxic, BPA-free materials and carefully embroidered features — no sharp edges, no plastic eyes, and no detachable parts. Suitable for children 6 months and above, it’s soft, safe, and hypoallergenic. 🧺 Easy to Clean &amp; Maintain Keeping your plush toy clean is simple! It’s machine-washable and hand-washable, designed to retain its shape, softness, and color even after multiple washes. The high-quality dyes ensure long-lasting brightness without fading or damage.</p>', 249, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ea754f5b-dd42-4deb-83f9-df3f99505d76.jpeg', 0, '{"compare_at_price": 299}',