	('prod_e42f61a0-9488-4227-a215-ebb2015cc9a4', 'exclusive-alloy-metal-pull-back-model-toy-vehicle-with-openable-doors-lights-music-premium-collectible-sports-car-gift', 'Exclusive Alloy Metal Pull Back Model Toy Vehicle with Openable Doors, Lights & Music | Premium Collectible Sports Car Gift', '<ul><li><p><strong>Premium Alloy Build:</strong> Made from high-quality metal + ABS parts for durability, realistic body lines, smooth wheels &amp; long-lasting play value for kids and collectors.</p></li><li><p><strong>Realistic Detailing:</strong> Sporty grille, headlights, rims, brake calipers &amp; sleek paint give an authentic Mercedes AMG GT-R look for display or imaginative racing.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lights &amp; Sound Features:</strong> Interactive sound effects and flashing headlights create a lifelike driving feel that excites young racers.</p></li><li><p><strong>Pull Back Action:</strong> Simple pull-back mechanism launches the car forward, supporting hand-eye coordination and fun indoor racing.</p></li><li><p><strong>Openable Doors:</strong> Both side doors open smoothly, revealing a detailed interior replica with realistic seat, dashboard &amp; steering.</p></li><li><p><strong>Perfect Gift Choice:</strong> Ideal collectible toy for kids, boys, car lovers, display shelves, model collectors &amp; birthday or festival gifting.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9b191f3a-984a-4e3a-aa66-28fe9f4f453f.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2599}', '2026-03-25 05:30:53.430491+00', '2026-03-25 05:30:53.430491+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9b191f3a-984a-4e3a-aa66-28fe9f4f453f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/829f5aaa-da1d-4dca-ab85-52cbfe3cbe0f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1eff35fd-1501-409f-bd4d-c730fbb90fef.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/358ac2aa-5d24-419f-b66c-f0cb37f12421.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7bf024