	('prod_76db833d-dcf2-4096-acb9-cfff58860fc8', 'dancing-fun-dog', 'Dancing Fun Dog', '<p>Children’s electric dog can walk and sing simulation can call puppy 1-2 years old 3 baby boy girl toy. The Awesome Musical Toy dogfeatures a range of different music and sounds to keep your child entertain for hours. The elephant feature cool moves, music and lights which will attract your child’s attention and help keep them entertained and having fun. As an added bonus, this musical toy can also help with baby’s muscle development as they attempt to move and copy the goose.</p>', 649, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/26456054-5d24-4447-9adf-4fee0869b08a.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.012738+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:09.012738+00', 'cat_63fdb535-cbf5-4b66-a236-2e323942c03f', NULL, 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/dancing-fun-dog/6be1adb4-1ad3-4bdf-a727-59d058a3172d.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/26456054-5d24-4447-9adf-4fee0869b08a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c4f3f7a1-2ec0-4c30-ace0-692be041990d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/da2c77c6-4d22-4d91-9370-e8c44f76bbcd.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b7154972-3bd1-44e3-9578-d8848aa119c3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d8c4c8be-0124-4346-b637-d3e1223fbd05.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.018613085,-0.017108193,0.01803902,0.0011981378,0.026046002,0.0030674078,0.05685139,0.02896517,0.0030502637,0.033422902,-0.012224193,0.005638939,-0.023144653,-0.0022141987,0.051280696,0.019294366,-0.02177747,0.0002900519,-0.021862976,-0.014603022,-0.026286138,0.04277091,0.05925395,0.06959914,-0.02378392,0.009000364,-0.023175092,0.038433492,0.0031594231,-0.007987929,0.029808557,-0.011733692,-0.027265128,-0.032075133,-0.01481778,-0.019031584,0.031136917,0.047180038,0.0036104606,0.024878621,-0.039232366,0.059266493,0.041378044,0.06059424,-0.009749985,0.041100755,-0.026520621,0.007901786,-0.033804774,0.016382104,-0.024558883,-0.019779379,0.0042193527,0.008362714,-0.044219654,-0.04528223,