	('prod_aef79ce0-42cc-4907-91f5-adc4c4fe7abc', 'crawling-baby', 'Crawling Baby', '<p>Durable and strong enough for children to play with this toy freely to withstand throwing, Toys will not stop working even after throwing them on the tile floor. The toy is visually quite attractive. Every child will enjoy it everywhere, even in the playroom. Made of non-toxic material and design of this crawling baby toy has no sharp points, so it is safe and reliable for people.<br>• Pleasant sounds and beautiful lights get produced through cap and milk bottle by this crawling baby toy.<br>• This cute Baby toy crawls and encourages your child to follow, which helps in promoting interaction and develops motor skills.<br>• The toy encourages ability training, interest development, emotion, hearing, grasping, sensory, vision, and other abilities.</p><p>A crawling toy is a playful, interactive toy designed to move or “crawl” on the ground, often mimicking the actions of a baby or small animal. Typically powered by motors or simple mechanisms, these toys are often aimed at engaging young children by encouraging them to follow or interact with the toy as it moves. Some crawling toys feature lights, sounds, or movements to enhance the play experience, fostering motor skills and curiosity.</p><p><br></p>', 499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4d407546-cf0b-46ef-b539-ae613c6a58ea.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 799}', '2025-12-28 10:59:08.709888+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:08.709888+00', 'cat_e8d304ee-124d-409f-b02f-9a0b6824b9de', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/crawling-baby/2f1dd418-6a44-4fc1-bed1-cd1ac1979c30.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4d407546-cf0b-46ef-b539-ae613c6a58ea.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/46171d72-19a9-4723-b40a-e7f5b6b86041.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0430292c-b1ab-4bb6-a6df-5a3642984a53.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8cd22f01-f355-4a43-8e5a-1e79af327199.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/produc