	('prod_3ebd75d6-ba8f-41af-a814-46b4f4878200', 'attacker-foam-dart-blaster-automatic-6-dart-rotating-barrel-toy-gun-with-6-foam-bullets-blue-and-orange-for-rapid-fire-guns-for-boys-7-14-years', 'Attacker Foam Dart Blaster, Automatic 6-Dart Rotating Barrel, Toy Gun with 6 Foam Bullets, Blue and Orange for Rapid Fire Guns for Boys 7-14 Years', '<p>Make playtime more exciting with this <strong>Kids Foam Dart Blaster Toy Gun</strong>, designed for safe and fun shooting games. This toy blaster comes with <strong>soft foam darts with suction tips</strong>, making it safe for children while still delivering thrilling action.</p><p></p><p>The toy features a <strong>stylish design, easy grip handle, and smooth trigger action</strong>, allowing kids to easily aim and shoot the darts. Whether playing alone or with friends, this toy encourages <strong>active play, focus, and hand-eye coordination</strong>.</p><p></p><p>Perfect for <strong>birthday gifts, return gifts, and fun family playtime</strong>, this dart blaster provides hours of entertainment for kids.</p><p></p><p>Soft Foam Suction Darts – Safe for kids<br>Easy Grip Handle for comfortable play<br>Lightweight and durable design<br>Encourages active play and coordination<br>Perfect for indoor &amp; outdoor fun</p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/638b7bb6-8076-4d3b-875d-a9b054c75e58.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2026-03-19 04:25:41.645689+00', '2026-03-19 04:25:41.645689+00', 'cat_e438d2a2-49e0-47b5-9dd0-3872f8b0f452', 'col_37cccc82-dee7-4ce4-9d1f-cf6b20863ad0', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/638b7bb6-8076-4d3b-875d-a9b054c75e58.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3a1026bc-e609-40b4-832a-f178253f3e36.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/96ba217a-3bda-41b8-987a-7921d16f74d2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ac8525a8-38d6-42c4-a666-195a372e4074.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1bdc4c1e-c534-4d3e-9d3f-3fb243462dfd.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9fd9f05b-7691-48b9-b279-07eb