	('prod_d2f4c593-f36c-4b57-8148-4fadff1ffc3c', 'childrens-repair-kit-screw-kit', 'Children`s repair Kit ( Screw Kit )', '<p>Introduce your child to the world of engineering and creative design with our comprehensive <strong>DIY Screw &amp; Repair Kit</strong>. This set transforms playtime into a productive learning experience, encouraging kids to build, experiment, and problem-solve.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li><p><strong>Limitless Creative Construction:</strong> Includes a variety of geometric shapes (squares, triangles, circles), strips, and angle irons that allow children to bring their imagination to life.</p></li><li><p><strong>Realistic Tooling:</strong> Features a battery-operated toy drill, giving children a fun, hands-on way to "fix" their creations and improve their motor skills.</p></li><li><p><strong>Abundant Accessories:</strong> With over 200+ pieces, including 70 mushroom nails, 60 screws, and 30 nuts, there are endless building possibilities.</p></li><li><p><strong>Organized &amp; Portable:</strong> All components fit neatly inside a charming, bear-shaped carrying case, helping children learn responsibility by organizing their own toys.</p></li><li><p><strong>Guided Learning:</strong> Comes with illustrated guide cards to inspire new designs and help children get started.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1149, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f3c97577-b1f8-4a93-8275-f9990f95e2af.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1749}', '2026-03-12 10:31:48.349113+00', '2026-03-12 10:31:48.349113+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f3c97577-b1f8-4a93-8275-f9990f95e2af.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/28f45d7e-f003-4fe6-b63f-6eefa5ee999d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9d972314-2339-432c-a2b7-e6709bed50cf.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ce0cbf0c-94aa-40da-be61-82bc7329cbae.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/89c4841e-31e1-4359-8f00-4026f488f451.jpeg,https://cdn.t