	('prod_66f9fe64-8d9a-446a-afd0-6b32121bef14', 'kids-pretend-play-kitchen-set-101-pcs-stainless-steel-utensils-gas-stove-and-chef-apron', 'Kids Pretend Play Kitchen Set 101 PCS – Stainless Steel Utensils, Gas Stove & Chef Apron', '<p>Let your child enjoy a complete cooking adventure with the Junior Chef 101-Piece Stainless Steel Kitchen Set. Designed for kids aged 3 years and above, this premium pretend play kitchen set includes everything needed for hours of creative and educational fun.</p><p>The set features high-quality stainless steel utensils such as frying pans, dosa pan, wok, bowls, pressure cooker, cooking pots, ladles, spatula, whisk, tongs, and more. It also comes with a realistic mini gas stove and gas cylinder connection, a wooden rolling board with rolling pin, reusable play food tokens, and a storage container for organized play.</p><p>To make the experience even more exciting, the set includes a free colorful chef apron and cap so your little one can feel like a real chef while playing. The durable stainless steel construction offers a realistic look, long-lasting quality, and easy cleaning after use.</p><p>This kitchen play set helps improve imagination, creativity, hand-eye coordination, and social skills through role play. It is a perfect gift for boys and girls on birthdays, festivals, return gifts, and special occasions. Ideal for indoor play, home learning, and pretend cooking fun.<br><br>CONTENTS:</p><p>Item Name Quantity</p><p>ROTI TAVA 1</p><p>FRY PAN 1</p><p>DOSA TAVA 1</p><p>KADAI 1</p><p>WOK KADAI 1</p><p>TASLA 1</p><p>TOPE 1</p><p>SAUCE PAN 1</p><p>COOKER 1</p><p>COOKER CONTAINER 2</p><p>GAS STOVE 1</p><p>CYLINDER 1</p><p>ROUND STAND 1</p><p>WHISK 1</p><p>SANSI 1</p><p>COOKING SPOON 3</p><p>MINI TONG 1</p><p>UTILITY CUP 1</p><p>PATLA 1</p><p>VALAN 1</p><p>Playfood 76</p><p>APRON 1 (FREE)</p><p>CHEF HAT 1 (FREE)<br>-------------------------------------<br>total - 101 pcs</p>', 2299, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a79ec437-e19a-4678-ac8d-7b7b0ffba638.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2999}', '2026-04-07 04:20:33.625526+00', '2026-04-07 04:20:33.625526+00', 'cat_2e74411c-18bf-42c3-9e9d-4d86d22008d5', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a79ec437-e19a-4678-ac8d-7b7b0ffba638.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3b242ddc-cc0a-4872-a0c3-2aa41bf6be15.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/13ec5223-558a-4d8c-b0b2-df8a314dd309.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f513ec91-effc-442f-ba29-823aa6de94e6.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c2afa812-b4ae-442c-8f7c-2596ce55a405.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/90b19f77-ec9d-4e3f-8fa0-983f71407c01.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a39ef65e-1f2b-4bfb-a315-8422f4fc7b45.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Make playtime extra fun with this 101-piece Junior Chef Kitchen Set for Kids. Made from premium stainless steel, this pretend play set includes a gas stove with connection, pressure cooker, frying pans, wok, rolling board and pin, kitchen tools, reusable food tokens, and a free chef apron with cap. Perfect for children aged 3+ who love cooking and role play.', 'https://youtu.be/iJwNUWFcgx8', '[-0.030736519,0.02132496,0.04138346,-0.03230806,0.04283535,0.024029417,0.002263735,-0.0006020147,-0.031450886,0.006563502,-0.01387947,0.017011885,0.06685092,0.004728841,0.016279727,-0.06967905,-0.014164169,0.03563144,0.025894655,-0.02451182,-0.04693702,-0.012879307,0.02502384,0.0092670005,-0.009904506,-0.020032233,0.013617921,0.007434666,0.07614477,0.042882636,0.045866296,0.0049133915,-0.06218312,-0.009075385,-0.06112626,-0.079674594,-0.086349614,0.051223032,0.021501781,0.060503744,-0.034042705,0.06811781,0.03415613,-0.006471442,-0.0034021612,-0.198823,0.018593542,-0.04602934,-0.03572562,-0.02241377,-0.004263215,0.03523631,0.043699622,0.026209384,-0.01924749,-0.05217073,-0.089206696,0.010812235,0.023773108,-0.0077415435,-0.062468104,0.003305015,0.005049929,0.03014394,0.015504229,0.025032755,0.0045328303,0.031190049,-0.059072852,-0