	('prod_6f33f96f-88cc-469c-b81f-69ab5f7bedbe', 'play-mat-deluxe-2-in-1-fabric-board-game-snakes-ladders-ludo-for-kids-washable-durable-portable-travel-toy', 'Play Mat Deluxe 2-in-1 Fabric Board Game | Snakes & Ladders + Ludo for Kids | Washable, Durable & Portable Travel Toy ', '<h3><strong>Classic Fun, Anytime, Anywhere! 2-in-1 Play Mat Deluxe</strong></h3><p>Bring back the joy of traditional board games and give your children a break from digital screens. Our <strong>Play Mat Deluxe</strong> is more than just a game; it’s a premium experience designed for family bonding. Featuring two evergreen classics—<strong>Snakes &amp; Ladders</strong> and <strong>Ludo</strong>—all on one high-quality, soft fabric mat!</p><p></p><h3><strong>Why You’ll Love It:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Dual-Sided Entertainment:</strong> Enjoy the thrill of Ludo on one side and the excitement of Snakes &amp; Ladders on the other. Double the games, double the fun!</p></li><li><p><strong>Premium &amp; Safe Material:</strong> Crafted from high-quality, non-toxic fabric that is completely safe for children. The edges are soft, and the material is built to last through years of play.</p></li><li><p><strong>100% Washable &amp; Easy Care:</strong> Don''t worry about spills or stains! This play mat is fully <strong>washable</strong>, making it easy to keep clean and hygienic for your little ones.</p></li><li><p><strong>Perfect Travel Companion:</strong> With a compact <strong>10" x 10"</strong> size, it is incredibly lightweight and portable. Simply fold it and tuck it into a bag for picnics, road trips, or vacations.</p></li><li><p><strong>Vibrant &amp; Engaging Design:</strong> Featuring bright colors and adorable animal characters like the friendly Elephant, Lion, and Monkey, this mat is designed to spark creativity and keep kids engaged for hours.</p></li><li><p></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Product Specifications:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Size:</strong> 10" x 10" (Perfectly sized for travel and small hands)</p></li><li><p><strong>Material:</strong> High-Durable Washable Fabric</p></li><li><p><strong>Inside the Box:</strong> 1 Double-Sided Fabric Mat, 1 Dice, and Colorful Pawns (Goti)</p></li><li><p><strong>Recommended Age:</strong> 4+ Years</p></li><li><p></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Perfect For:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Best Gift Idea:</strong> An ideal choice for birthdays and special occasions.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Skill Development:</strong> Helps children develop logic, social interaction, and counting skills.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Family Bonding:</strong> Perfect for indoor game nights or outdoor picnics.&nbsp;</p></li></ul><p></p>', 199, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/928a1558-d4ec-4060-aa7a-176a356685d0.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2026-03-19 04:29:43.209957+00', '2026-03-19 04:29:43.209957+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_d3648e6d-cf26-493f-9cd3-1803de78bf8c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/928a1558-d4ec-4060-aa7a-176a356685d0.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/870ff5d0-e2b3-471d-982f-7fa9af5774c4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dd8f7d8f-f1d8-425a-9281-5f3c78278bf2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7651583c-f916-4506-bce8-ad0b44839c72.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/59808428-97f2-47b1-b5a4-26e2a8024af5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/765f3e08-f17f-4751-a546-76a3065fcc5b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0e882b9b-8f03-43ab-814e-e6fc9d052cf6.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Bring back the joy of traditional board games and give your children a break from digital screens. Our Play Mat Deluxe is more than just a game; it’s a premium experience designed for family bonding. Featuring two evergreen classics—Snakes &amp; Ladders and Ludo—all on one high-quality, soft fabric mat!', '', '[0.036989845,-0.037148435,0.040502105,-0.07786181,0.051041503,-0.021212075,0.017183358,0.01408117,0.0069063655,0.059187036,-0.00948792,0.057626523,0.015505309,0.0005728382,0.0232880