	('prod_a99d4838-e006-45f4-83ef-01433f5000d7', 'toyota-vellfire-alphard', 'Toyota Vellfire Alphard', '<ul><li><p>Powerful Pull Back Function Has sound and light. Toyota Vellfire Alphard Doors, trunk and hood open; Fully working suspension; Has sound and light Pull Back Function.</p></li><li><p>Elegant Design: Accurate replica of the Toyota Vellfire Alphard, showcasing its sleek body, bold front grille, and sharp headlights.</p></li><li><p>Flawless Finish: High-quality paint job reflecting the premium and luxurious nature of the Vellfire Alphard.</p></li><li><p>Luxurious Interior: Realistic seating, detailed dashboard, and center console that mirror the original vehicle’s upscale features.</p></li><li><p>Functional Elements: Opening doors, hood, and trunk for added interactivity and realism.</p></li></ul>', 3699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2d9987a8-b2e6-4db0-9478-73da7f750764.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 3999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:21.952987+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:21.952987+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/toyota-vellfire-alphard/25f3033c-1c3a-4269-832f-cdd374df44ae.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2d9987a8-b2e6-4db0-9478-73da7f750764.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e56f46af-e53d-4191-8cf4-982e964efca1.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/908208d8-9c16-4a21-a3f1-e29bdf59d1d3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/20cddb9f-a720-42b2-8e62-a2932413817c.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.017297547,-0.025102908,-0.023194384,-0.014696923,0.07966823,0.03375943,0.050040353,0.009225139,0.019066371,0.015399639,0.033901084,0.009265528,0.025159398,-0.03826824,0.0500227,0.032350972,0.025049629,0.0039393744,0.011848153,-0.024147619,0.06782524,0.048746247,0.011787756,-0.0101320725,-0.013276941,-0.007649531,0.04010419,0.0346079,0.002421278,0.02174672,0.0102398135,-0.021747774,0.012721141,-0.006346277,-0.05797942,-0.023972137,-0.021758433,0.015137607,0.030309567,0.080