	('prod_4f3524b8-cc7a-4f1e-bb47-1d5ab773f25b', 'defender-1-24-scale', 'Defender 1:24 Scale', '<ul><li><p>1:24 Diecast for Land Rover Defender 110 metal car and rubber tires, Four doors, hood and rear fender can be opened. Wheels simulates shock absorption.</p></li><li><p>The model car has detailed interior, Off-road model truck has power wheels with rubber tires, which is with pullback function.</p></li><li><p>The car was made well and lights and sound made it extra special for kids. Working headlights and a realistic engine sound.</p></li><li><p>This toy car is very detailed interior and exterior. the wheel, the seats, the tires, the headlight, every detail makes the toy vehicle a great replica of the real car.</p></li><li><p>Great item for collector, home decoration, office decoration, display. Great choice of gift for kids, Suitable as a gift for 3 years old boys and up</p></li></ul>', 1499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/148b65c1-cf43-4522-bd0d-46c734f0af1e.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1699}', '2025-12-28 10:59:08.810716+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:08.810716+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/defender-1-24-scale/249a62e2-12c3-4eb4-8e9e-5cfb92dc0b23.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/148b65c1-cf43-4522-bd0d-46c734f0af1e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/06131c5b-12f4-46e8-a490-13122870bbe2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6c1adad9-f0aa-4bf3-9b4d-c9d0438f4382.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cf054e9a-793c-430f-9f28-d781db462155.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.027823063,-0.011505656,-0.029181257,-0.0012194515,0.038824163,-0.021043018,0.055840846,0.024189478,-0.015286375,0.010904911,0.014390494,0.038979765,0.036068656,0.0030483012,0.0562202,-0.008085052,0.035452336,0.030541081,-0.022881282,-0.06276784,0.0555645,0.020099841,0.029178487,-0.0033579252,-0.031505607,0.0139115425,-0.002704372,0.01879295,-0.04579661,0.033285163,0.0144360345,-0.037323106,-0.