	('prod_dcb7bb01-8f35-4b18-b9a8-9b4e3608b7ac', 'double-barreled-gun', 'Double Barreled Gun', '<ul><li><p>This Toy Gun features a unique manual loading mechanism. Press the barrel release button at the rear, then use your hand to break down the barrel for easy loading. This interactive feature adds realism to the play experience.</p></li><li><p>Designed for an authentic feel, the toy gun allows for cartridge installation, enhancing the playtime experience with a touch of realism.</p></li><li><p>Ensuring durability and safety, the toy gun is equipped with double shell protection, making it a sturdy and reliable choice for kids’ play.</p></li><li><p>Adding to its appeal, the toy gun has a cool shell throwing feature that ejects shells, mimicking the action of a real shotgun and providing a more engaging play experience.</p></li><li><p>This toy gun boasts a double-barreled shotgun design, doubling the fun and excitement for kids during playtime.</p></li></ul>', 799, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a92eccd8-ebff-4801-8653-8e9b703b52c4.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1200}', '2025-12-28 10:59:10.82437+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:10.82437+00', 'cat_aef0da25-a920-495d-af0a-9ce132e7c89c', 'col_37cccc82-dee7-4ce4-9d1f-cf6b20863ad0', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/double-barreled-gun/558cd9ec-f5dc-407c-a05b-01580a7f7140.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a92eccd8-ebff-4801-8653-8e9b703b52c4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c9b46f43-f910-4655-a406-67ca6f12dcb5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b8902b73-883f-4c40-ab51-2c8b685bbf40.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5be3920f-f09f-423c-8230-d137b85e1382.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/714cb447-c32b-4a32-8356-6cb475f70294.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.025221335,-0.0010638688,0.051413994,0.02977823,0.029851772,0.051025257,0.028970443,0.04398626,-0.0058466573,-0.0004688174,0.017396903,-0.022231186,0.031041067,-0.020290246,0.03753182,-0.0010349278,0.020037645,0.031722143,-0.0024173823,-0.059220076,-0.0654