	('prod_d737dda1-5ac0-4995-b5d2-051a7e4244bf', 'cute-musical-dancing-bear-toy-with-led-lights-baby-learning-toy-with-saxophone-and-360-movement', 'Cute Musical Dancing Bear Toy with LED Lights – Baby Learning Toy with Saxophone & 360° Movement', '<p>Make your child’s playtime joyful and engaging with this Cute Musical Dancing Bear Toy. Designed with an adorable bear face and stylish headphones, this toy plays cheerful music while holding a glowing saxophone, creating a fun and interactive experience for kids.</p><p>Equipped with colorful LED lights on the headphones and saxophone, it produces beautiful lighting effects that capture children’s attention. The toy features 360° movement with a universal wheel, allowing it to move, spin, and change direction automatically when it hits obstacles.</p><p>This toy also has a gentle swinging motion that adds to its charm, encouraging kids to watch, follow, and interact. It helps in developing hand-eye coordination, sensory skills, and early learning abilities in toddlers.</p><p>Made from safe, durable, and child-friendly materials, it is perfect for babies and toddlers. An ideal gift for birthdays, festivals, or special occasions, this musical bear toy ensures hours of fun and learning.</p>', 499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ce0f8eba-8528-4189-b5df-d7b58d113169.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2026-04-15 12:56:13.936654+00', '2026-04-15 12:56:13.936654+00', 'cat_e8d304ee-124d-409f-b02f-9a0b6824b9de', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ce0f8eba-8528-4189-b5df-d7b58d113169.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/da41e343-023f-4850-b110-e67d5999f098.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/70a73caf-9d65-460c-99b8-1c3b294c8dbd.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/901e7dcd-3a61-4ac6-9ed6-6ca7f4349756.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5e2107c8-86d0-4580-be13-0bf2f23e604f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4bbf847f-a50c-4dfd-9d02-496283845f91.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL,