	('prod_9469719b-21a5-46e5-83ae-8f16d6be7a53', 'stunt-car-4-function', 'Stunt Car 4 Function', '<p>Age : 2+ Years</p><p>USB Rechargeable</p><p>Remote Control Rechargable</p><p>Acrobatic 360 Degree</p><p>Music&amp;Light</p><p>Rotating &amp; Rolling&nbsp;</p><p>Remote Control Rechargable Acrobatic 360 Degree Twisting Stunt Car with Music &amp; Lights for Kids</p><p>AMAZING FUNCTIONS: 360 degree front wheel rotation designed, make it easily to flips and spin at any angles and perform all kinds of cool stunt action such as move forward, backward, front left reverse,right reverse, upright 90 degree walking like robot</p><p>FULL OF CHILD FUN: This Toy Looks Amazing when it Bling the Light with Music. Its is a Musical Car Toy for Children Entertainment</p><p>PREMIUM MATERIAL: Toy Car is made by high quality plastic and rubber, firm and durable car body. Toy is lightweight and proper size to store and Kids can carry and play with it anywhere and anytime.</p><p>EASE OF USE: The remote control car has features such as ease of use, safety and durability. Amazing rapid response by radio remote control system makes it a enjoyable toy for kids.</p><p>USB RECHARGEABLE: This toy car comes with a rechargeable Micro USB charging port. Even though this stunt car has a 2-wheel-drive double motor engine with a powerful gear box it offers a staggering play time.</p><p>PERFECT GIFT: It can be a Great Gift Idea . You Can gift this Car to Kids on Various Occasions like Birthday.</p><p>BIS Certified-The product complies with BIS Standards to ensure the safety</p>', 499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5a0699b0-84bc-422f-95a6-49a51207cf8c.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 650}', '2025-12-28 10:59:18.755169+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:18.755169+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/stunt-car-4-function/3d5e5564-5313-442f-a81f-62a2cc55e341.png', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5a0699b0-84bc-422f-95a6-4