	('prod_e2894d38-f79e-4855-ad44-051bcfa99177', 'baby-inflatable-sofa-seat-with-back-support-portable-baby-chair-air-sofa', 'Baby Inflatable Sofa Seat with Back Support | Portable Baby Chair (Air Sofa)', '<p>Give your little one a cozy and secure seating space with the <strong>Inflatable Baby Sofa Chair with Back Support (Little Bear)</strong>. Specially designed for babies aged <strong>6 to 18 months</strong>, this soft air sofa provides excellent back and side support to help your baby sit comfortably.</p><p></p><p>Made from <strong>high-quality, baby-safe material</strong>, the chair is lightweight, soft, and easy to inflate. Its cute <strong>Little Bear design</strong> makes it attractive for babies while the supportive structure helps keep them stable during feeding, playing, or bathing time.</p><p></p><p>The <strong>portable and compact design</strong> makes it perfect for home use, travel, or outdoor activities. It can be easily deflated and stored when not in use, saving space. This baby sofa chair is a practical and comfortable solution for parents who want a safe seating option for their little ones.</p><h3></h3><p>✔ Suitable for <strong>6–18 months babies</strong><br>✔ <strong>Soft inflatable design</strong> with back support<br>✔ Perfect for <strong>feeding, bathing, and playtime</strong><br>✔ Lightweight, portable &amp; easy to inflate<br>✔ Cute <strong>Little Bear pattern</strong><br>✔ Easy to <strong>inflate and deflate</strong></p>', 899, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/897c4ba6-da3e-412e-9d44-a4e7b375e60f.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1399}', '2026-03-14 10:04:15.964406+00', '2026-03-14 10:04:15.964406+00', 'cat_ebbe45ea-9a06-4cad-9319-3e51620a3c88', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/897c4ba6-da3e-412e-9d44-a4e7b375e60f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dd87124e-64ed-4dab-9487-6c77e9a7a171.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dd4d3500-f16d-498e-ae43-dedaadaa0d9d.jpeg,https://cdn.toyck