	('prod_a41014a6-9c83-4d9a-b8f6-cf52dc9bd2dc', 'barbie-stainless-steel-play-tea-set-for-kids-17-pieces-pretend-play-kitchen-set-with-teapot-cups-and-tray', 'Barbie Stainless Steel Play Tea Set for Kids – 17 Pieces Pretend Play Kitchen Set with Teapot, Cups & Tray', '<p>Bring home the fun of tea time with this beautiful Barbie 17-piece play tea set for kids. Designed with a stylish Barbie theme and made using shiny stainless steel pieces, this set is perfect for pretend kitchen and tea party games. Children can create their own tea party experience while improving creativity, social interaction, and role-playing skills.</p><p>This complete set includes 1 teapot with lid, 1 sugar bowl with lid, 1 creamer pitcher, 4 teacups with matching coasters, 4 teaspoons, 1 serving tray, and a Barbie character sticker sheet. The bright Barbie packaging and cute accessories make it a wonderful gift for girls aged 3+ years.</p><p>Ideal for indoor play, birthday gifts, return gifts, and Barbie fans, this toy tea set encourages imagination and hours of fun with friends and family. The overall style closely matches Genie''s TOY BUS Barbie Tea Party Set.<br><br>Include:</p><p>4 Cups , 4 Saucers , $ Spoons , 1 Teapot , 1 Tary , 1 CookieBowl , 1 Lid , 1 Breasdtick Holder </p>', 1299, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/398e62fa-d7e9-4dda-bd3a-5cef392dc551.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2026-04-08 11:18:29.761457+00', '2026-04-08 11:18:29.761457+00', 'cat_2e74411c-18bf-42c3-9e9d-4d86d22008d5', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/398e62fa-d7e9-4dda-bd3a-5cef392dc551.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/46d8f898-5356-44f4-bd01-9f8a47fd00e5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/36215524-ad97-42d9-b49b-6f9bd2b170ae.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3eb502f1-892c-414c-b3a2-71321aa61bfb.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ad09b265-ebd5-4905-aa91-ba9c2ba31db5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/62a251f8-54af-4981-aebc-d03cf6786