	('prod_80a5364d-c98c-416a-aede-d8a93f8e2e92', 'diecast-metal-rolls-royce-cullinan-masory-car-toy-for-kids-with-openable-doors-and-lights-sounds', 'Diecast Metal Rolls Royce Cullinan Masory Car Toy for Kids with Openable Doors and Lights, Sounds', '<p>Bring home luxury with this <strong>Collector’s Edition Die-Cast SUV Toy Car</strong>, inspired by the iconic Rolls-Royce Cullinan. Designed with <strong>high-quality alloy metal body and premium finish</strong>, this toy delivers a realistic and stylish look that stands out.</p><p></p><p>This model features <strong>openable doors, bonnet, and rear trunk</strong>, giving kids an interactive play experience while also making it a perfect collectible piece. The <strong>pull-back function</strong> allows smooth movement, and the <strong>front &amp; rear lights</strong> enhance the realistic feel. Built with <strong>durable rubber tires and detailed interior</strong>, it ensures long-lasting fun.</p><p></p><p>Ideal for <strong>kids, gifting, and collectors</strong>, this luxury toy car combines elegance with entertainment. Whether for playtime or display, it adds a premium touch to your collection.</p>', 1699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/57a6eac9-5a37-47e7-b1c2-cfce08a44c68.jpeg', 100, '{"compare_at_price": null}', '2026-03-25 05:02:52.851035+00', '2026-03-25 05:02:52.851035+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/57a6eac9-5a37-47e7-b1c2-cfce08a44c68.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/969d4ca7-1a2f-48ca-a61a-318c65dc65ec.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6e74cc13-aa4b-4c38-a3a3-a4a811efa646.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/365c04aa-369b-44fb-b980-8b0bb0f0e549.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/956b1eec-bc4c-4f17-8424-a5d2545185ab.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/26539859-8de1-40b9-b217-15566871c6f0.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f7743903-c5f7-4082-a99e-469903a5ea37.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/pro