	('prod_539a6e7f-1fa1-40f7-a3b5-91958f310f35', 'kids-ride-on-push-car-with-storage-music-and-lights-comfortable-seat-toy', 'Kids Ride-On Push Car with Storage, Music & Lights – Comfortable Seat Toy', '<p>Make playtime exciting and active with this stylish Kids Ride-On Push Car. Designed with a lightweight yet sturdy body, this ride-on toy is perfect for toddlers to enjoy smooth and safe riding both indoors and outdoors.</p><p>It features a comfortable seat that helps maintain balance, making it an ideal first ride-on toy for young children. The built-in music and lights add extra fun and keep kids engaged while playing.</p><p>One of the best features is the hidden storage compartment under the seat, allowing kids to store their small toys and essentials while riding. The thickened anti-slip wheels ensure better grip and stability, providing a safe riding experience.</p><p>With its attractive design, smooth handling, and multifunction features, this ride-on car helps improve motor skills, coordination, and balance. It’s a perfect gift choice for birthdays, special occasions, and everyday fun.</p><p></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Lightweight and durable body design</p></li><li><p>Comfortable seat for better balance</p></li><li><p>Built-in music and lights for fun play</p></li><li><p>Hidden storage space under the seat</p></li><li><p>Anti-slip wheels for safety and stability</p></li><li><p>Easy to use and child-friendly design</p></li><li><p>Ideal for indoor and outdoor use</p></li></ul><p></p>', 850, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ba56c86c-00a5-47d4-a9e2-102fabb66741.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1299}', '2026-04-11 10:17:43.115927+00', '2026-04-11 10:17:43.115927+00', 'cat_708a2e4c-0188-4975-bb35-61045f1c32bd', 'col_d27f16c3-8935-41d9-90af-5895ffef1e0c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ba56c86c-00a5-47d4-a9e2-102fabb66741.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/44f9fce3-042f-434c-b9e6-acf3e73ff7c2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/produ