	('prod_559dc235-6c40-4c34-8fec-833adbbbad19', 'remote-control-off-road-jeep-toy-car-for-kids-4x4-rechargeable-rc-car-with-speaker', 'Remote Control Off Road Jeep Toy Car for Kids – 4x4 Rechargeable RC Car with Speaker', '<p>Let your kids enjoy an exciting driving adventure with this <strong>Remote Control Off Road Jeep Toy Car</strong>. Designed with a strong <strong>4x4 wheel system and rugged off-road tyres</strong>, this RC jeep can easily run on sand, grass, and rough surfaces.</p><p></p><p>The car comes with an <strong>easy-to-use remote controller</strong> that allows forward, backward, left and right movement. It also includes a <strong>USB rechargeable battery</strong>, making it convenient to charge and play anytime. The <strong>built-in speaker feature</strong> adds extra entertainment while driving.</p><p></p><p>Made with <strong>durable and high-quality material</strong>, this RC jeep is safe and long-lasting for kids. Whether playing indoors or outdoors, this toy car</p><p>provides hours of fun and helps improve hand-eye coordination.</p><p></p><p>This <strong>off-road RC jeep toy</strong> is a perfect gift for <strong>kids, boys and girls</strong> on birthdays, holidays and special occasions.</p><p></p><ul><li><p>4x4 Powerful Off-Road Driving</p></li><li><p>USB Rechargeable Battery</p></li><li><p>Easy Remote Control Operation</p></li><li><p>Strong Off-Road Tyres</p></li><li><p>Built-in Speaker Sound</p></li><li><p>Durable &amp; Kid-Friendly Design</p></li></ul><p></p>', 799, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8aea1c7a-e12f-4111-9f78-66239a4026c3.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1499}', '2026-03-14 12:05:03.414784+00', '2026-03-14 12:05:03.414784+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8aea1c7a-e12f-4111-9f78-66239a4026c3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3ca86f84-2c6b-4f1e-8adb-1caccb300c11.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cf34c2a5-d518-4cfb-885