	('prod_a96fd9a7-84ff-488c-a1c1-a3da198903da', 'business-game-senior-5-in-1', 'Business Game Senior (5 in 1)', '<p>Multiple Games in One: The board game includes five different games to keep players entertained – Ratna’s Business, snake and ladders, Ludo, car rally, and cricket.</p><p>2-4 Player Game: The game can be played with 2 to 4 players, making it perfect for small groups of friends and family members.</p><p>Real Estate Game: Ratna’s Business game is a game of buying, selling, banking, and mortgaging properties, which makes it a great way to learn about business and real estate.</p><p>Develops Problem Solving Skills: The game requires players to make strategic decisions on buying and selling properties, which helps to develop their problem-solving skills.</p><p>Develops Social Skills: Playing the game helps players learn how to interact with other players and negotiate deals, which helps to develop their social skills.</p>', 279, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/business-game-senior-5-in-1/7eec9bac-9096-4aae-8ef8-d4d640e71e30.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 399}', '2025-12-28 10:59:07.935535+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:07.935535+00', 'cat_faea0711-a3b3-422e-a496-772919c14df6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/business-game-senior-5-in-1/e2ca544d-25c6-4e4a-bb4d-da311a0ac417.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/business-game-senior-5-in-1/7eec9bac-9096-4aae-8ef8-d4d640e71e30.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/business-game-senior-5-in-1/914c4a82-93af-4852-a96d-d4f209eac351.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/business-game-senior-5-in-1/b9714697-9ada-4a44-aeb4-0ccaa6bc267c.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/business-game-senior-5-in-1/c035ca2a-ffa9-42e5-aceb-db570fe72024.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/business-game-senior-5-in-1/660715ce-be83-4304-b8d1-cb2ab320453f.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/business-game-senior-5-in-1/8b7eecb8-7e5a-4aaa-9ef4-fc7bb4015803.jpg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.017876795,-0.02