	('prod_f31436ed-53af-493e-8701-da9885e640cc', 'range-rover-suv-metal-model-with-openable-doors-light-sound-pull-back-features-for-play-gift', 'Range Rover SUV Metal Model with Openable Doors Light Sound Pull Back Features for Play & Gift ', '<ul><li><p>Range Rover SUV Design: 1:24 Scale die-cast model of the iconic Super Sport, meticulously designed with stunning attention to detail. From its aerodynamic curves to its sleek paint finish, this model mirrors the luxury supercar’s authentic design for an unparalleled look and feel.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Functional Features for Realistic Play: The Range Rover SUV Super Sport features functional doors that open, smooth-rolling wheels, and a detailed interior, providing a fully immersive and realistic experience. Kids and collectors alike can enjoy interactive play while appreciating the car''s intricate design.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Durable &amp; Safe for Kids: Designed with safe, non-toxic materials, this Range Rover SUV toy car is perfect for children. It offers both playability and durability, ensuring hours of fun while allowing kids to explore their passion for sports cars in a safe, engaging way.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>High-Quality Die-Cast Metal Construction: Built with premium die-cast metal, this toy car offers a realistic weight and a sturdy build. The durable metal material ensures longevity, making it perfect for both display and play. Its superior craftsmanship is ideal for die-cast collectors and enthusiasts.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Perfect for Display and Collection: This 1:24 scale Range Rover SUV model is the perfect addition to any collection or display. Whether placed on a shelf, desk, or in a display case, it’s an eye-catching, conversation-starting piece. Its larger size and high-quality finish make it ideal for showcasing in your home or office.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1799, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/41a6c740-1093-4bd3-92b2-c9f5f6dbbc8d.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2999}', '2026-03-25 06:34:41.989961+00', '2026-03-25 06:34:41.989961+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/41a6c740-1093-4bd3-92b2-c9f5f6dbbc8d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dccae65b-30f6-477f-a2b3-2afd73aa156b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a1409c04-57c5-473a-a248-cdaf9b3ded87.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b2b28646-cd29-4d54-8a5f-6c78c47f5aad.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ddb7b2d7-acee-43bd-9eef-dfb26b0bf3c5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0dde51aa-3ac0-4d9c-9c77-79204286adcc.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/36c279bc-8971-4366-a1f2-cb4b741caa20.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Premium die-cast SUV toy car with openable doors, bonnet & trunk, realistic lights and sound effects.,
