	('prod_1d261017-8b0f-441b-9ef1-c2a5b4fb079b', 'sbe-smart-kids-rabbit-phone-musical-sound-toys-best-gift-for-kids-light-sound-multicolor', 'SBE Smart Kids Rabbit Phone, Musical Sound Toys, Best Gift for Kids | Light | Sound (Multicolor)', '<p>Introduce your child to a world of fun and learning with the <strong>Intelligent Baby Musical Mobile Phone Toy</strong>! 📱✨</p><p>This adorable toy phone is specially designed for little hands, featuring a <strong>cute baby-friendly design with smooth, colorful buttons</strong> that are safe and easy to press. It comes with <strong>soft music (below 65dB)</strong> to protect your baby’s delicate hearing while still providing an engaging play experience.</p><p>The toy includes <strong>cartoon number keys</strong> with different modes like digital sound effects, phone button sounds, and song mode—helping kids learn numbers, sounds, and rhythm in an interactive way. With <strong>20 built-in children’s songs (MIDI)</strong>, your child will stay entertained while developing sensory and listening skills.</p><p>It also has a <strong>music button, switch key for multiple modes, and fun chat button</strong> with voice messages to keep kids engaged. Its compact size (approx. 16cm x 11cm) makes it easy to carry and perfect for play at home or on the go.</p><p></p><ul><li><p>Soft &amp; safe sound (&lt;65dB) for baby ears</p></li><li><p>Cute and colorful cartoon design</p></li><li><p>Multiple modes: sound effects, phone sounds, songs</p></li><li><p>20 built-in children’s songs</p></li><li><p>Interactive buttons for learning &amp; fun</p></li><li><p>Lightweight and portable</p></li></ul><p>🎁 A perfect educational toy gift for babies and toddlers!</p>', 199, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1e9f2fdb-129d-45bb-bd28-44ea6aa10090.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2026-04-17 10:56:00.872876+00', '2026-04-17 10:56:00.872876+00', 'cat_e8d304ee-124d-409f-b02f-9a0b6824b9de', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', NULL, '{https: