	('prod_1672f09a-cd4f-43bf-b954-6989365c2c82', '2-in-1-soft-aqua-blaster-gun-shoots-foam-darts-and-water-absorbing-gel-bullets-for-indoor-and-outdoor-play', '2 in 1 Soft Aqua Blaster Gun - Shoots Foam Darts and Water-Absorbing Gel Bullets for Indoor and Outdoor Play', '<p>Make playtime more exciting with this <strong>Manual Gel Blaster Toy Gun for Kids</strong>. This toy gun shoots <strong>soft water gel beads (hydrogel balls)</strong> that break instantly on impact and disappear, keeping play clean and safe.</p><p></p><p>The blaster features a <strong>strong and stylish design with a comfortable grip</strong>, allowing kids to easily hold and aim while playing. Simply soak the gel beads in water and load them into the gun to start the fun shooting game.</p><p></p><p>Made from <strong>durable high-quality plastic</strong>, this toy gun is lightweight and easy to use for kids. It is perfect for <strong>outdoor games, backyard battles, birthday parties, and adventure play</strong>.</p><p></p><p>This <strong>gel beads shooting toy</strong> helps improve <strong>focus, hand-eye coordination, and active play</strong> while giving kids hours of entertainment.</p><p></p><ul><li><p>Manual Gel Blaster Toy Gun</p></li><li><p>Soft Water Gel Beads Shooting</p></li><li><p>Safe &amp; Kid-Friendly Design</p></li><li><p>Strong Plastic Body</p></li><li><p>Perfect for Outdoor Games</p></li><li><p>Great Gift for Boys &amp; Girls</p></li></ul><p></p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/eb8d9579-4cb5-4c0e-aa24-ab81547c1184.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2026-03-14 12:20:04.439877+00', '2026-03-14 12:20:04.439877+00', 'cat_061cfdbf-29d0-4ad7-97b1-39fb9aaf1ca0', 'col_37cccc82-dee7-4ce4-9d1f-cf6b20863ad0', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/eb8d9579-4cb5-4c0e-aa24-ab81547c1184.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/45ee74d1-eee9-4849-989a-69f8149f666e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cebaa779-0bf7-4324-a95a-d1d0b97a2715.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7b