	('prod_6a71d5cd-1620-4442-9734-1b84fd800b4a', 'f004-car-rider', 'F004 Car Rider', '<ul><li><p>Give your child the best start with the kidsROAR Push Ride-On Car for Kids 1-5 Years. This baby push car is specially designed for toddlers and growing kids, combining comfort, safety, and interactive fun in one stylish package. Ideal for both boys and girls, it’s the perfect ride on car for kids who love to explore!</p></li><li><p>This ride on car for kids comes with built-in music, dynamic front and rear lights, and colorful 3D light effects to make every ride exciting. Whether your little one is riding indoors or outdoors, the lights and music turn a regular trip into an engaging adventure. A must-have push car for kids who love lights and sounds!</p></li><li><p>Unlike many other baby push cars, the kidsROAR ride-on car supports up to 35kg. Built from strong, child-safe materials, it offers a sturdy and stable ride-on toy for toddlers and young kids alike. It’s a heavy-duty kids push car designed to grow with your child.</p></li><li><p>Equipped with a comfortable and easy-to-use push handle, this baby push ride-on car allows parents to steer and control the car while the child enjoys the ride. This makes it ideal for walks, outings, and mall visits. A perfect blend of fun and safety in one ride-on car for kids 1-5 years.</p></li><li><p>From the vivid color scheme to the eye-catching lights, this baby push car is designed to delight. The stylish curves and high-gloss finish make it a standout car for kids, while the engaging features help boost your child’s motor skills and sensory development. One of the most attractive push cars for toddlers on the market!</p></li></ul>', 949, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/f004-car-rider/2bd5e410-a029-4403-b241-8273b18d014c.png', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1499}', '2025-12-28 10:59:10.934708+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:10.934708+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_d27f16c3-8935-41d9-90af-5895ffef1e0c', 'active', 'https://