	('prod_ac929b54-ee18-43a5-a375-2794b33041d1', 'play-mat-duo-2-in-1-reversible-ludo-snakes-and-ladders-fabric-board-game-for-kids-17-x-17', 'Play Mat Duo: 2-in-1 Reversible Ludo & Snakes and Ladders Fabric Board Game for Kids (17" x 17")', '<h3><strong>Double the Fun with the Ultimate 2-in-1 Play Mat!</strong></h3><p>Bring home the perfect blend of traditional gaming and modern durability. The <strong>Play Mat Duo</strong> features two all-time favorite board games—<strong>Ludo</strong> and <strong>Snakes &amp; Ladders</strong>—printed on a premium, reversible fabric mat. Designed with vibrant colors and cute animal characters, it’s the perfect way to keep kids engaged away from screens.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Why You’ll Love the Play Mat Duo:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Dual-Sided Entertainment:</strong> Switch between Ludo and Snakes &amp; Ladders in seconds. Just flip the mat and start a new game!</p></li><li><p><strong>Premium Washable Fabric:</strong> Made from high-quality, durable cloth that is 100% washable. No more worrying about spills or stains during playtime.</p></li><li><p><strong>Safe &amp; Kid-Friendly:</strong> Soft edges and non-toxic materials ensure a safe environment for toddlers and young children.</p></li><li><p><strong>Travel-Friendly &amp; Portable:</strong> Fold it, roll it, or pack it in your bag. The lightweight design makes it the perfect companion for picnics, vacations, or visits to the grandparents.</p></li><li><p><strong>Educational &amp; Interactive:</strong> Helps improve counting skills, strategic thinking, and social interaction between parents and children.</p></li><li><p></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Technical Specifications:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 17 x 17 Inches</p></li><li><p><strong>Material:</strong> High-Grade Washable Textile</p></li><li><p><strong>Age Group:</strong> 3+ Years</p></li><li><p><strong>Design:</strong> Reversible (Ludo on one side, Snakes &amp; Ladders on the other)</p></li><li><p><strong>Includes:</strong> 1 Reversible Game Mat, Colorful Pawns, and Dice.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/021ad8f8-93c7-424b-a54c-c491a99e138d.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2026-03-19 04:32:45.858692+00', '2026-03-19 04:32:45.858692+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_d3648e6d-cf26-493f-9cd3-1803de78bf8c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/021ad8f8-93c7-424b-a54c-c491a99e138d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/5ddb275b-8ece-42d2-8088-112882319f19.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/13610eec-37ff-43a1-8b16-bcb94fcca9d9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6c9d3733-989e-4339-9c19-a007ef1f414d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6f5f35ce-e6c1-4892-a915-260d0cf97e16.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3ced0de8-b878-43d3-b397-a44a4f5d9065.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ef858454-fa18-4699-849c-d7bee8d8e7d7.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d86a8eaf-9010-4e96-95d8-7f6ec644bdf9.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Bring home the perfect blend of traditional gaming and modern durability. The Play Mat Duo features two all-time favorite board games—Ludo and Snakes &amp; Ladders—printed on a premium, reversible fabric mat. Designed with vibrant colors and cute animal characters, it’s the perfect way to keep kids engaged away from screens.', 'https://youtu.be/_OItKYam_KA', '[0.00078155694,-0.006009878,0.044705324,-0.051506672,-0.019031022,-0.034905374,0.026625898,-0.008770748,-0.06966583,-0.013701172,-0.025051367,0.032168012,0.029075813,-0.030522663,0.061404873,-0.038431883,-0.03262253,-0.005533667,0.026063949,-0.08143623,0.006155545,-0.008926729,0.013366179,0.010476736,-0.07461817,-0.032071583,-0.011630394,0.018263306,0.015523849,-0.002706072,0.042899035,-0.009697274,0.014245449,0.046041615,-0.054548923,-0.019752024,-0.08021641,0.028834142,-0.012747388,-0.061505426,-0.095814526,0.06139568,0.00300538,0.0036612586,-0.021442419,-0.0041552945,0.0077749537,-0.06006315,0.03205365,0.00670753,0.021490702,-0.0