	('prod_2811dfa9-c71b-4e28-9b36-3945a74fcc4e', '5d-flashing-light-balance-car-toy-with-music-360-rotating-stunt-car-with-dancing-boy-figure', '5D Flashing Light Balance Car Toy with Music – 360° Rotating Stunt Car with Dancing Boy Figure', '<p>Bring excitement and fun to your child’s playtime with this 5D Flashing Light Balance Car Toy. Designed with vibrant multi-color LED lights and built-in music, this toy creates an engaging and entertaining experience for kids.</p><p>The unique balance design allows the car to rotate 360 degrees smoothly, while the bump-and-go feature ensures it automatically changes direction when it hits obstacles. The adorable boy figure on top adds extra charm as it moves along with the car, making it even more attractive for children.</p><p>Powered by 3 AA batteries, this toy is easy to operate and perfect for indoor play. It helps improve kids’ motor skills, hand-eye coordination, and visual tracking while keeping them entertained.</p><p>Made from durable, child-safe materials, it is ideal for kids and makes a perfect gift for birthdays, festivals, or special occasions.</p>', 550, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/83ea8f65-a1b7-426c-830e-c6553188760a.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2026-04-14 11:51:27.607538+00', '2026-04-14 11:51:27.607538+00', 'cat_27725163-6cf3-426f-8aad-bc2ebc05dadd', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/83ea8f65-a1b7-426c-830e-c6553188760a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3c3279a4-9017-4a00-92ab-33eabee74baf.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b6a3950f-af09-4fad-a2f1-051842e5ca9f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9a554782-66bf-48f1-84c1-6e7442eb1311.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/88113fb9-1e2e-4b4f-bd68-2d9ab419da48.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/225024fa-c298-447c-a50a-b94f8934ea2b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2f63c5b2-8ae6-4e28-be33-3552dc133051.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Exciting balance car toy with 5D flashing lights, music, 