	('prod_2915dd89-37f5-471f-9013-c602bf3afb21', 'spiyat-1954-mercedes-benz-300sl', 'Spiyat 1954 Mercedes-Benz 300SL', '<ul><li><p>Limited edition miniature model Collectible scale model Steerable / Posable front wheels Opening parts as shown in pictures Made of diecast metal, Plastic and Rubber Excellent decoration for Home/Office The perfect product to gift to an automobile enthusiast</p></li><li><p>Iconic Design: This diecast model replicates the legendary 1954 Mercedes-Benz 300SL, famous for its revolutionary gullwing doors and aerodynamic silhouette.</p></li><li><p>Premium Exterior Detailing: Features a sleek paint finish, realistic headlights and taillights, and signature chrome accents on the grille, bumpers, and trim.</p></li><li><p>Gullwing Doors: Includes fully functional gullwing doors that open upwards, showcasing one of the most defining features of the original car.</p></li><li><p>Detailed Interior: The cabin is meticulously crafted with accurate seats, a realistic dashboard with vintage-style gauges, and a classic steering wheel, reflecting the luxury and sportiness of the 300SL.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6b7bafec-9a2d-4306-ac3f-a2220a22f890.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1999}', '2025-12-28 10:59:19.251062+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:19.251062+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/spiyat-1954-mercedes-benz-300sl/abe31ffa-bc22-4c97-8595-b787ca6d9169.webp', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6b7bafec-9a2d-4306-ac3f-a2220a22f890.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4cbbd926-696b-4e0f-b1f4-361d521e923a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2e136f83-b610-469b-814a-183eb254cad7.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2a46c357-fbbb-47d2-b9a0-56a4891b6078.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/97f27a2e-0a5e-4275-a5e8-f9272a488be5.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Limited edition miniature model Collectible scale model Steerable / Posable front wheels 