	('prod_36ce7eb4-fc6a-4bd3-9178-7ed3d91106fe', 'baby-balance-bike-rider-astro-455', 'Baby Balance Bike Rider Astro 455', '<p>“Introduce your little one to the joys of riding with our Baby Balancing Scooter with Music and Lights. Perfectly designed for toddlers aged 1 to 3 years, this scooter combines fun and function, encouraging your child’s balance and coordination development while keeping them entertained. Featuring interactive music and dazzling lights, this scooter turns every ride into an exciting adventure. Its sturdy, anti-slip design ensures safety, allowing your child to play confidently indoors or outdoors. The adjustable seat and handlebars grow with your child, making it a lasting companion through their early years. Crafted from eco-friendly, durable materials, this scooter is safe for little hands and feet. The smooth wheels ensure a quiet, comfortable ride, making it ideal for indoor play without disturbing the household. Ready to ride right out of the box, it’s the perfect gift to inspire your toddler’s first steps into independent play.”</p>', 1249, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/baby-balance-bike-rider-astro-455/8a37586b-0254-4d21-9ba6-60792a80cb52.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1499}', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.766616+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:04.766616+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_d27f16c3-8935-41d9-90af-5895ffef1e0c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/baby-balance-bike-rider-astro-455/11bcde7f-a599-49dc-9e55-fcddb4c79b19.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/baby-balance-bike-rider-astro-455/8a37586b-0254-4d21-9ba6-60792a80cb52.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/baby-balance-bike-rider-astro-455/c8e1df4b-09f3-4b05-b4db-7f41b37ac89e.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/baby-balance-bike-rider-astro-455/a9a1d782-df85-453c-b9a8-e8f38a7c6973.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/baby-balance-bike-rider-astro-455/618ba0c9-2dd2-45c6-b1a4-41b4dd91b91b.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/baby-balance-bike-rider-astro-455/7309e0ee