	('prod_81763a45-6f75-49fc-ad04-ed40b312c84e', 'kids-diy-drill-construction-board-toy-educational-creative-building-set-junior-engineer', 'Kids DIY Drill Construction Board Toy – Educational Creative Building Set ( Junior Engineer )', '<p><strong>Kids DIY Drill Construction Puzzle Board – Creative Educational STEM Toy</strong></p><p></p><p>Encourage creativity and hands-on learning with this exciting <strong>Kids DIY Drill Construction Board Toy</strong>. This fun <strong>educational STEM toy for kids</strong> allows children to build colorful patterns, shapes, and designs using screws, tools, and different puzzle pieces.</p><p></p><p>The set includes a <strong>toy electric drill, screwdriver, wrench, screws, and colorful plates</strong> that children can assemble on the board to create animals, flowers, vehicles, and many other creative designs. This <strong>DIY construction toy for kids</strong> helps improve imagination, motor skills, and problem-solving abilities.</p><p></p><p>This <strong>creative building puzzle board</strong> is designed to keep kids engaged while developing important learning skills. It also helps reduce screen time by encouraging hands-on play and creativity.</p><p></p><p>The convenient <strong>portable storage box design</strong> makes it easy to carry and store all the pieces safely after playtime.</p><h3><br></h3><ul><li><p><strong>DIY Drill Construction Toy Set</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Educational STEM Learning Toy</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Colorful Creative Puzzle Board</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Improves Creativity &amp; Problem Solving</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Includes Toy Drill, Screws &amp; Tools</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Portable Storage Box Design</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Safe &amp; Durable Material</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Perfect Gift for Kids Age 3+</strong></p></li></ul><p></p>', 1250, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7b198549-20bc-4f54-a849-161d21c6000b.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1999}', '2026-03-14 12:32:49.736027+00', '2026-03-14 12:32:49.736027+00', 'cat_061cfdbf-29d0-4ad7-97b1-39fb9aaf1ca0', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7b198549-20bc-4f54-a849-161d21c6000b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6fd118b2-eb5d-470b-8d02-89f25bd7b1a5.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ad6cc962-909a-4c67-ac83-a5648b22a3df.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1688be16-c2ed-42c6-84d5-219186701230.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f3d59d9d-4e40-4779-9359-98819266ef01.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/bffa22be-67b0-471c-b5e2-42befabc7c90.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/74c1703f-4607-4c1e-97b0-a7a10bf62f08.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b35ad9ab-3ad3-456a-8ca2-9b060b514403.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'This DIY Drill Puzzle Board Toy for Kids is a fun and educational construction set that helps children build creative shapes and designs using colorful screws and tools. This STEM learning toy for kids improves creativity, problem-solving skills, and hand-eye coordination. Perfect educational toy for kids age 3+.', '', '[0.017359959,-0.031203816,0.04258726,-0.010328361,0.07511207,-0.0110320235,0.023460712,-0.002504007,-0.025936838,0.01099839,-0.01629393,0.02132032,0.031767014,-0.0035878439,0.05415256,-0.012785093,-0.004853602,-0.0020856105,0.042532444,-0.044913474,-0.079439215,0.02260005,-0.024611969,0.024603775,-0.03362508,0.012682245,-0.0010396029,0.028224066,0.014480749,0.01052134,0.029969236,0.04797122,-0.0065840813,0.037467185,-0.06316716,0.0004398948,-0.01683727,0.041798025,0.010568524,0.023153052,-0.04814492,0.06760248,0.0060071615,-0.0036924782,-0.022927439,-0.061665777,0.052610878,-0.006309541,-0.03088179,-0.017112892,0.023068765,0.009174764,-0.011137206,-0.02777618,-0.043433838,-0.054999053,-0.06245325,-0.03728135,0.008382778,0.003123201,0.083430275,-0.052409984,-0.029157434,0.057543173,-0.009607983,-0.013860145,-0.0029079374,0.11212266,-0.01863698,-0.048418876,-0.03300562,-0.