	('prod_e307f759-714e-4bf3-a8f4-0e00c1b99d02', 'premium-stainless-steel-barbie-kitchen-set-with-travel-bag-and-utensils-for-kids', 'Premium Stainless Steel Barbie Kitchen Set with Travel Bag & Utensils for Kids', '<p>Make playtime more exciting with this Premium Stainless Steel Barbie Kitchen Set for kids. Specially designed for little chefs, this adorable pretend play set comes with high-quality stainless steel utensils and cookware packed inside a beautiful Barbie-themed carry bag.</p><p>The set includes different types of spoons, pots, pans, a bowl, cooking tools, and colorful Barbie stickers to decorate and personalize the play experience. The strong metal finish gives the set a realistic look, helping children enjoy imaginative kitchen role play while developing creativity and hand-eye coordination.</p><p>The included travel-friendly storage bag makes it easy to carry the complete set anywhere—whether at home, during travel, or at a friend’s house. This kitchen set is ideal for gifting on birthdays, return gifts, festivals, and special occasions.</p><p></p><p><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Premium stainless steel mini kitchen set</p></li><li><p>Includes pots, pans, bowl, spoons, and spatula</p></li><li><p>Comes with colorful Barbie stickers</p></li><li><p>Travel-friendly Barbie storage bag included</p></li><li><p>Encourages imaginative and pretend play</p></li><li><p>Suitable for kids aged 5 years and above</p></li></ul><p></p>', 1399, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/18e609c3-42a9-4644-b2f6-f9d3b64d057b.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1599}', '2026-04-09 12:21:44.469942+00', '2026-04-09 12:21:44.469942+00', 'cat_2e74411c-18bf-42c3-9e9d-4d86d22008d5', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/18e609c3-42a9-4644-b2f6-f9d3b64d057b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b3698ad1-ad5c-4065-b2e7-8edfe9e90cb9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e8eb0c9a-1ed4-4842-b123-89758a86750e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.