	('prod_7289a65d-093e-4263-ab7f-cae17e94ada9', 'mercedes-benz-amg-g63-benz-model-car-gwagon-132-exclusive-alloy-metal-pull-back-die-cast-car-diecast-metal-pullback-toy-car', 'Mercedes-Benz AMG G63 Benz Model Car Gwagon 1:32 Exclusive Alloy Metal Pull Back Die-cast Car Diecast Metal Pullback Toy car', '<ul><li><p>Full-Featured Car Toy ： The doors and the hood,The Tail can be opened,Press the two wheels of the front car to trigger the engine sound and lights, and open the door to trigger the lights of the front and rear lights. Place the car on the ground, hold down the car body and pull it back, the car will drive forward.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Toys is one of the premium brands currently selling Educational And Child Development Toys on Amazon. We started in the year 2016 and have ever grown since than. Thousands of Amazon customers have bought, and their children have used toys and have given heaps of good reviews. However, we have not lost focus to always maintain good quality and provide quality products. Our vision to become household name for toys. We are thankful to our customers who have helped us to grow.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Suitable For Gift or Collectible : you choose the model car for dear childrens or friends Precious interesting driving memory will be remained,you also can collect put in your home or office</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Exquisite structure : Our model car interior is rich in detail, exquisite workmanship, simulation cab, steering wheel dashboard and other various details are available, simulation restore real car details in all directions to give a better experience.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>powerful function : four door design, press the front wheels or open the door can trigger the sound and light effect, back force function, the car will pull back, the car will slide forward a distance.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>We are the world''s leading manufacturer of high-quality models, kits and die-casting products. If you need other models of products, please contact us, we will serve you wholeheartedly!</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Function: Press the two wheels of the front car to trigger the engine sound and lights, and open the door to trigger the lights of the front and rear lights. Place the car on the ground, hold down the car body and pull it back, the car will drive forward. (With pull back function)</p></li><li><p>AlloyMade Metal Alloy material, which makes it very difficult to be damaged. Non-toxic water-based paint spray and doesn''t contain formaldehyde or any other harmful substances. Not easy to Scratches with delicate touches</p></li></ul><p></p>', 449, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0a60da31-47c3-4d0b-8682-2a72cbec1401.jpeg', 150, '{"compare_at_price": null}', '2026-03-25 07:51:58.457134+00', '2026-03-25 07:51:58.457134+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0a60da31-47c3-4d0b-8682-2a72cbec1401.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/b103c434-0c4c-4637-80d6-50305cc27e1a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3563d253-20b1-46a2-9194-a5bbc295e6f2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/acbf66f4-2318-4c61-b979-b0488f6fd057.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f3c7f514-b40a-43aa-b0cd-cafba3aee2a7.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cd392567-b131-479a-b87c-e400b508e032.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/66811bac-2656-428f-b0fd-96afa2fb79f3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/aa44484c-b1b8-4070-84db-bb90784a487c.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a419e96d-81df-448f-b6ac-62d0bc3b54a8.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f4c3b141-bb82-4d4c-a49e-736ce6d230a9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/845ba81d-9f3e-4998-890d-fde7f727b64d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/72f41f3d-3313-4465-9d59-3006bcf142ae.png}', 'inr', NULL, ' The doors and the hood,The Tail can be opened,Press the two wheels of the front car to trigger the engine sound and lights, and open the d