	('prod_4bb78b8b-3a0e-44bb-bcd2-d52c170b3ae2', '2-in-1-construction-truck-toy-excavator-and-loader-with-movable-arms-for-kids', '2-in-1 Construction Truck Toy – Excavator & Loader with Movable Arms for Kids', '<p>Let your child enjoy endless construction fun with this 2-in-1 Construction Truck Toy featuring both a loader and excavator! Designed for realistic play, this toy comes with fully movable arms, adjustable joints, and smooth-rolling wheels, allowing kids to dig, scoop, and transport materials just like a real construction vehicle.</p><p>Made from high-quality, non-toxic plastic, it is completely safe for small hands and built to last through active play. The 180-degree rotating excavator arm and flexible joints enhance creativity and improve hand-eye coordination.</p><p>Perfect for both indoor and outdoor play, this construction toy encourages imaginative role-play while helping children develop motor skills and problem-solving abilities.</p><p></p><ul><li><p>2-in-1 design: Loader + Excavator</p></li><li><p>Adjustable and movable joints</p></li><li><p>180° rotating excavator arm</p></li><li><p>Smooth rolling wheels</p></li><li><p>Safe, non-toxic material</p></li><li><p>Ideal for kids aged 3+</p></li></ul><p></p>', 199, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/34733153-72f0-49ac-bcef-79026e941416.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2026-04-14 12:00:21.858213+00', '2026-04-14 12:00:21.858213+00', 'cat_d2e2c9f0-67f5-4bf8-978b-fbdc1cc5cc1a', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/34733153-72f0-49ac-bcef-79026e941416.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fb73b960-77ad-41ac-bcb5-520ae8ec6736.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/237f17a7-5bf6-48a4-ae15-299bc6848b49.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0d14fc3c-5749-453d-b5d3-3dab4408a2d8.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Fun and durable 2-in-1 construction truck toy with adjustable excavator and loader arms. Made from safe, non-toxic materials, perfect for kids’ indoor and out