	('prod_5cd3f2bb-b7b5-49b5-a7e9-24f0f29770a2', 'stunt-car-5-function', 'Stunt Car 5 Function', '<p>Age : 2+ Years</p><p>USB Rechargeable</p><p>Remote Control Rechargable</p><p>Acrobatic 360 Degree</p><p>Music&amp;Light</p><p>Rotating &amp; Rolling</p><ul><li><p>360° Rotating R/C Stunt Car With Demo Feature: Now Gooyo Stunt Toy Car comes with DEMO feature. This cool racing car can do all sorts of tricks. Double sides running, moving forward, backward, turning left, right, 360 degree tumbling flip for different playing experience on this electric remote control stunt car. You can control the RC cars for kids in any direction with its remote controller. This remote control car can race, and, perform double-sided driving, 360° spins and flip with its LED dazzling headlights.</p></li><li><p>Shockproof / Anti-Skid off Road Car: Designed with Anti-crash durable tires, RC rock Crawler car fits for indoor and outdoor like Sandy beach, wetlands, grasslands, etc. Equipped with flexible wheels, the race toy car allows high speed and better flexibility.</p></li><li><p>Anti-interference Wireless Control: The remote control car has an exclusive frequency wireless control. So it supports multiple cars playing at the same time without interference between each other. With 2.4GHz interference-free control frequency, the high speed 12km/h RC toy car enables multiple RC stunt cars to race together at the same time and place for about 40 meters remote control.</p></li><li><p>Perfect Gift for Kids: Kids will surprise when receiving this attractive hover soccer as a birthday present, Christmas gift, etc. Let the kids exercise and make friends in the game.</p></li><li><p>Rechargeable and Long Battery Life: Built in long life rechargeable batteries, the Gooyo remote control car can run for 25-30 minutes and provides longer play time after full charge of 1.5 hours. We provide a strong lithium rechargeable battery and its best thing is that it won’t dead/damage if you do not charge it till a year.</p></li><li><p>It requires 2xAA batteries for Remote Controller (not included)</p></li></ul>', 599, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ef6bb820-332d-4ac3-970a-c24432f56342.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 750}', '2025-12-28 10:59:19.534973+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:19.534973+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/stunt-car-5-function/3b6df59b-0e8b-4332-85d0-ea15cc4da396.png', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ef6bb820-332d-4ac3-970a-c24432f56342.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4a93823e-e660-4389-8566-98732aa20611.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/244be127-7d4d-4ba7-a65d-e13c4c2cd831.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1776ddf7-3be8-4313-ac84-b8ff4b5c1823.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.023099799,-0.033330083,0.008317595,0.029430065,0.021778887,-0.035258476,0.016466614,0.025706906,-0.047047578,-0.022621358,0.026513051,-0.0054290444,-0.0066402587,-0.0047961217,0.061273895,0.03130435,0.010631236,0.029617451,-0.018037891,-0.014611918,0.032094866,0.030989604,0.04064464,0.017694509,-0.013164613,-0.013974573,0.034309197,0.01788243,-0.032450344,-0.015408387,0.03096387,0.026572624,-0.019499278,0.002835326,-0.09570771,0.0044417763,-0.0786148,0.020568522,-0.007211317,-0.047915846,-0.04770429,0.051076,0.018897766,-0.004946762,-0.012163095,-0.06266838,0.035499517,-0.03198605,-0.06961553,0.010119476,-0.013782864,0.0047637396,-0.018256005,0.00067586324,-0.057126842,-0.06360764,0.012646756,0.0084804,0.022500383,-0.0070641167,0.02379493,0.0075261416,-0.0071856175,0.003081716,0.0067473655,-0.0439356,-0.008790377,0.09661246,-0.02774493,-0.016149595,0.00901182,-0.05026902,0.0048284074,-0.009779846,-0.01973001,-0.007109035,0.0016648538,-0.024255592,0.01332923,-0.013535556,0.015525859,-0.0036033276,-0.030848237,-0.03306171,-0.017319512,-0.006016035,-0.02244288,-0.033555645,0.009713013,-0.02293757,0.020421917,-0.043884058,-0.56361985,0.020131178,-0.032267362,-0.0012541733,0.007710027