	('prod_d2e2eb35-a015-49ef-bd82-d1b1aa531d24', 'rechargeable-remote-control-stunt-car-for-kids-360-rotation-rc-toy-car-with-led-lights-type-c-charging-high-speed-racing-car', 'Rechargeable Remote Control Stunt Car for Kids | 360° Rotation RC Toy Car with LED Lights | Type-C Charging High Speed Racing Car', '<p>🚗 <strong>Ultimate Remote Control Stunt Car for Kids</strong><br>Let your kids enjoy endless fun with this high-speed RC stunt car designed for action-packed play. With smooth controls and powerful motors, it delivers an exciting driving experience both indoors and outdoors.</p><p></p><p><strong>360° Stunt &amp; Spin Action</strong><br>Perform cool flips and spins easily — perfect for fun racing and tricks.</p><p><strong>Easy-to-Use Remote Control</strong><br>Simple buttons for forward/backward and left/right movement — kids can control it easily.</p><p><strong>Rechargeable Battery (Type-C Charging)</strong><br>No need to buy batteries again and again. Just charge and play anytime.</p><p><strong>Dual Motor Power (Front &amp; Back)</strong><br>Strong motors give better speed and performance on different surfaces.</p><p><strong>Durable &amp; Safe Design</strong><br>Made with high-quality plastic and strong wheels for long-lasting use.</p><p><strong>Attractive Colors Available</strong><br>Comes in multiple colors like Green, Red, Yellow, Blue &amp; Purple.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Product Specifications:</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Car Size: Approx. 10–12 cm</p></li><li><p>Control Type: Wireless Remote</p></li><li><p>Charging: Type-C USB</p></li><li><p>Material: Durable ABS Plastic</p></li><li><p>Recommended Age: 3+ Years</p></li><li><p></p></li></ul><h3>🎁&nbsp;<strong>Perfect Gift for Kids</strong></h3><p>Ideal gift for birthdays, return gifts, or special occasions. Kids will love the speed, lights, and stunt features!</p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/090e7819-edfb-4f7c-87a4-75db470c070b.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1299}', '2026-03-19 04:03:09.545586+00