	('prod_0c8153e8-9078-4773-ab40-1236f4f325d3', 'kids-doctor-set-toy-with-suitcase-medical-pretend-play-kit-with-stethoscope-tools-and-accessories-3-years', 'Kids Doctor Set Toy with Suitcase – Medical Pretend Play Kit with Stethoscope, Tools & Accessories (3+ Years)', '<p>Make playtime exciting and educational with this Kids Doctor Set Toy with Suitcase. Designed for children aged 3 years and above, this colorful medical kit includes a variety of realistic doctor tools such as a stethoscope, injection, dental mirror, thermometer, scissors, goggles, and more.</p><p>The set comes in a convenient suitcase with an attached handle and smooth-rolling wheels, making it easy for kids to carry and store their tools. This pretend play toy helps develop creativity, confidence, and social skills as children role-play as doctors and learn about basic medical concepts in a fun way.</p><p>Made from safe, durable, and child-friendly materials, this doctor set is perfect for both boys and girls. Ideal for gifting, home play, or educational activities, it keeps kids engaged while enhancing their imagination and learning abilities.<br><br><strong>Complete Doctor Set:</strong> Includes stethoscope, injection, scissors, dental mirror, thermometer, goggles &amp; more</p><ul><li><p><strong>Portable Suitcase Design:</strong> Easy to carry with handle &amp; wheels for travel and storage</p></li><li><p><strong>Attractive &amp; Colorful Design:</strong> Bright colors that grab kids’ attention</p></li><li><p><strong>Educational Toy:</strong> Helps improve imagination, creativity &amp; role play skills</p></li><li><p><strong>Safe for Kids (3+):</strong> Made from non-toxic, child-friendly materials</p></li><li><p><strong>Social Skill Development:</strong> Encourages interaction &amp; pretend play with friends/family</p></li><li><p><strong>Easy to Use Tools:</strong> Lightweight and perfectly sized for small hands</p></li><li><p><strong>Perfect Gift Option:</strong> Ideal for birthdays, return gifts &amp; special occasions</p></li></ul><p></p>', 299, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2ee0be71-1234-4602-8224-25ea72d50bb2.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 699}', '2026-04-13 12:24:59.120199+00', '2026-04-13 12:24:59.120199+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2ee0be71-1234-4602-8224-25ea72d50bb2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8b916f07-53d9-451a-9729-4be100b9d406.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/596156a3-c6cf-44fb-8d95-364ce40a68aa.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8b59ac53-9117-432a-a91a-e066cf207120.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d4fe370a-1158-42e5-974b-d1b6b526fb73.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/bb5ec76e-86f6-4a58-aafc-d85e8261b0f8.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Fun and educational doctor play set for kids with a portable suitcase. Includes stethoscope, injection, scissors, goggles, and more to encourage imagination and role play.', 'https://youtu.be/s-BBkkZNlVg', '[-0.020318812,0.024186516,0.020563833,0.07683807,0.01633164,0.022269187,0.01608004,0.035924986,-0.025644766,0.016209166,0.0011369339,-0.0030106492,0.0020769176,-0.0040702713,0.026244316,-0.0021687767,-0.034518257,0.027499486,-0.006056937,-0.056591563,-0.10905034,0.0023890922,-0.035568815,0.0531009,0.023479337,0.046034347,0.0321115,0.016584111,-0.0041055917,-0.011147293,-0.04674048,0.010919239,0.0041930475,0.01377757,-0.04464445,-0.025663087,-0.024843521,0.03320188,-0.004605531,-0.025555953,-0.02334157,-0.01381528,0.010964444,-0.022327378,-0.018090842,0.049619894,0.05659194,-0.0019346395,-0.059797592,0.004999421,0.066750884,0.0024552129,0.011806849,-0.03395938,-0.025436549,-0.0063489066,-0.069718085,-0.011851999,0.055604104,-0.045293696,-0.0006010008,-0.036127802,-0.039444286,0.016623944,0.009767492,0.022163771,-0.032463614,0.1326931,-0.031836104,-0.050849985,-0.0144387735,-0.06313305,-0.007396994,0.038682252,-0.059478037,0.009662563,0.017545998,0.016057154,-0.008320021,-0.026019