	('prod_6170470e-045a-485f-b53e-c800ccc3d5e6', 'kids-tool-set-with-suitcase-3year-diy-construction-toy-kit-with-tools-and-accessories', 'Kids Tool Set with Suitcase – 3+Year DIY Construction Toy Kit with Tools & Accessories', '<p>Encourage creativity and hands-on learning with this Kids Tool Set with Suitcase! Specially designed for children aged 3+, this DIY construction toy kit comes with a variety of safe and durable tools, including a hammer, screwdriver, bolts, measuring scale, and more.</p><p>The compact suitcase design makes it easy to carry and store, allowing kids to take their favorite tools anywhere. With interactive parts like a hand crank gear, mini screws, and assembly pieces, children can enjoy building and fixing activities while improving their motor skills, problem-solving ability, and imagination.</p><p>Made from high-quality, child-safe materials with smooth edges, this tool kit ensures safe playtime. It’s the perfect gift for young builders and curious minds.</p><p></p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Complete tool set with suitcase storage</p></li><li><p>Includes hammer, screwdriver, bolts &amp; accessories</p></li><li><p>Safe, smooth &amp; durable materials</p></li><li><p>Enhances creativity &amp; problem-solving skills</p></li><li><p>Easy to carry with attachable handle &amp; wheels</p></li><li><p>Perfect for kids aged 3+</p></li></ul><p></p>', 299, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d0b29e39-cfce-43c1-a1eb-7e1643ce9430.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 699}', '2026-04-11 10:28:30.939107+00', '2026-04-11 10:28:30.939107+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d0b29e39-cfce-43c1-a1eb-7e1643ce9430.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fe9817ec-106c-438e-8466-0f27ed862e1e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a70b4578-b4c4-4e8f-9f20-031accf9246d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/35b5db74-69d6-4386-b68b-536594313a17.jpeg,https://cdn