	('prod_e78d7bd3-34f6-4ff4-862e-d78088d4becb', 'f1-riser-car', 'F1 Riser Car', '<ul><li><p>Classic Formula 1 Racing Design – The J2k Brothers F1 Riser Car is crafted in an iconic Formula 1 style with a sleek and aerodynamic body. Its high-glow glossy finish adds a premium touch, making it look like a miniature version of a real racing car that kids will instantly fall in love with.</p></li><li><p>Strong &amp; Durable ABS Plastic Body – Made from high-quality, non-toxic ABS plastic, this racing car is designed to withstand rough play and last longer. The sturdy build ensures that it remains intact even during energetic play sessions, giving parents peace of mind about durability and safety.</p></li><li><p>Soft Rubber Wheels for Smooth Play – The car is equipped with soft, anti-slip rubber wheels that provide excellent grip and stability. These wheels are gentle on indoor surfaces, protecting floors from scratches, while also ensuring smooth rides on outdoor surfaces.</p></li><li><p>Perfect Gift for Kids Who Love Cars – Whether it’s a birthday, holiday, or just a surprise gift, this toy car makes an excellent choice for children who enjoy cars and racing. Its attractive design, bright red color, and easy-to-use features make it a favorite among both boys and girls.399</p></li></ul>', 399, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ddd6cf8b-2b51-42b3-a460-c8931ecfb9da.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 599}', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.288476+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:12.288476+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/f1-riser-car/db32020d-a16e-4d77-b458-46523c36665e.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ddd6cf8b-2b51-42b3-a460-c8931ecfb9da.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/98d2e87d-810d-4fda-802a-b9b9442084b3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7535b49e-fe2e-447c-89af-7cae1b6205f4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cab7f176-27c3-4f80-a966-0462b2ea8fcd.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.0448