	('prod_6ee37145-3a47-4767-b8d2-26b2e81cba48', 'monkeytail-mr-rock-dancing-guitar-toy-for-kids-light-and-music-electric-cartoon-guitar-led-flashing-musical-toy-with-dance-and-rhythm-interactive-robot-birthday-gift-for-boys-girls-age-3', 'MONKEYTAIL Mr. Rock Dancing Guitar Toy for Kids | Light & Music Electric Cartoon Guitar | LED Flashing Musical Toy with Dance & Rhythm | Interactive Robot | Birthday Gift for Boys Girls Age 3+', '<ul><li><p>Interactive Dancing Guitar Toy: Mr. Rock moves, dances, and sways while playing music—engaging kids with fun movement and rhythm.</p></li><li><p>LED Flashing Lights: Equipped with bright multicolor LEDs on the guitar and body, enhancing visual excitement during play.</p></li><li><p>Realistic Guitar Sounds &amp; Multi-Rhythm Music: Features music switching, dance rhythm modes, and volume control for a dynamic musical experience.</p></li><li><p>Easy Operation: One-button control and simple function keys make operation effortless for children; power switch included.</p></li><li><p>Safe &amp; Durable Build: Made with eco-friendly, non-toxic plastic and smooth edges suitable for kids'' daily play.</p></li><li><p>Educational Play Value: Helps improve memory, hand–eye coordination, motor skills, and sound-based learning through interactive features.</p></li><li><p>Perfect Gift for Any Occasion: Ideal for birthdays, Christmas, Diwali, celebrations, school events, and musical pretend-play activities for boys and girls aged 3+.</p></li><li><p>Battery Operated: Runs on 3 AA batteries (not included); durable electronic components ensure long-lasting fun.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 649, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f40ed91d-ddca-4a20-bd14-ee3a277c7e4e.png', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2026-04-17 10:47:46.63818+00', '2026-04-17 10:47:46.63818+00', 'cat_e8d304ee-124d-409f-b02f-9a0b6824b9de', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f40ed91d-ddca-4a20-bd14-ee3a277c7e4e.png,https://cdn.to