	('prod_7235a50a-aac8-41b9-94f2-b5e97478d291', 'dash-remote-control-car-24ghz-164-scale-rc-cars-remote-control-car-toy-rc-drifting-cars-interchangable-wheel-sleeves-4-light-2-speed-modes', 'Dash Remote Control Car | 2.4Ghz, 1:64 Scale | Rc Cars, Remote Control Car Toy, Rc Drifting Cars, Interchangable Wheel Sleeves, 4 Light & 2 Speed Modes', '<h3><strong>Experience the Thrill of Precision Drifting in the Palm of Your Hand!</strong></h3><p></p><p>Don’t let the size fool you. The <strong>Micro Drift RC Series</strong> is engineered for high-speed indoor racing and professional-grade drifting. Designed with a sleek, minimalist aesthetic and premium finishes, this isn''t just a toy—it''s a high-performance miniature machine perfect for enthusiasts, collectors, and kids alike.</p><p></p><ul><li><p><strong>Precision Steering:</strong> Equipped with a professional wheel-based remote controller for pinpoint accuracy and smooth drifting maneuvers.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p><strong>Ultra-Compact 1:64 Scale:</strong> Small enough to race on a desk, kitchen counter, or floor, making any indoor space your personal racetrack.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p><strong>Customizable Style:</strong> Each set comes with premium graphic decals (stickers), allowing you to personalize your racer’s look.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p><strong>Premium Build Quality:</strong> Features a high-gloss finish, realistic tinted windows, and aerodynamic spoilers for a luxury "editorial" look.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p><strong>Complete Racing Kit:</strong> Includes everything you need to start drifting—from spare tires and traffic cones to a dedicated tuning screwdriver.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What’s in the Box?</strong></h3><p></p><ul><li><p>1 x Micro Drift RC Car</p></li><li><p>1 x 2.4GHz Professional Remote Controller</p></li><li><p>1 x USB Quick-Charging Cable</p></li><li><p>1 x Custom Decal/Sticker Sheet</p></li><li><p>4 x Spare Drift Tires</p></li><li><p>1 x Mini Tuning Screwdriver</p></li><li><p>Traffic Cones for obstacle courses</p></li></ul><p></p>', 2499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/eb45e028-33ef-4404-8b06-9b80b51a5ce9.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 3999}', '2026-03-19 05:39:02.207366+00', '2026-03-19 05:39:02.207366+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/eb45e028-33ef-4404-8b06-9b80b51a5ce9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/232d7485-236a-4bf2-a824-eed40e4e1070.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/51613832-bfd1-400c-9619-19c54fe5ad1b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9b02211d-7a67-4cff-b10d-7a42497bb2fc.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/e736b815-6ebd-4952-833b-c0e7b15ce825.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/91a391e4-f34e-4fd1-bac7-047ff7516da0.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/43ea7c3f-233d-48a3-82ec-b6098f4703eb.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7bfa5c77-0a23-49ca-ba0b-6c8cb52a4275.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/46de60c5-a8aa-4439-ac35-723e0829b470.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/80ce753b-8e2d-4586-95b5-1be83a14ea2b.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/cff41d24-7ae9-454a-9e0c-a081a1ca4583.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/43acd2f0-582f-4835-84b7-292e926bf247.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Don’t let the size fool you. The Micro Drift RC Series is engineered for high-speed indoor racing and professional-grade drifting. Designed with a sleek, minimalist aesthetic and premium finishes, this isn''t just a toy—it''s a high-performance miniature machine perfect for enthusiasts, collectors, and kids alike.', 'https://youtu.be/AicGC900eGw', '[0.007724137,-0.032800857,0.011864894,0.023145394,0.024113387,0.02432404,0.033598583,0.010044832,0.055085108,-0.03720256,0.04512853,-0.0019085568,0.024063678,0.0009615037,0.08369909,-0.010621153,0.0023060092,0.016008615,0.012366164,-0.008079206,0.015418144,0.008018817,-0.020831622,0.0428522,-0.026366588,0.013163034,0.027378317,0.015484047,0.009525771,-0.047545202,0.04216051,-0.015