	('prod_f8fdd035-d228-4687-a68b-e2086a31dc69', 'range-rover-scale-model-car-exclusive-alloy-metal-pullback-toy-with-openable-doors-and-back-for-kids', 'Range Rover Scale Model Car - Exclusive Alloy Metal Pullback Toy with Openable Doors and Back for Kids ', '<ul><li><p>ORIGINAL REPLICA: The Land Rover Defender, featuring an original miniature car look. It includes a 2-wheel drive, and doors can be opened.</p></li><li><p>PREMIUM QUALITY: Made with high-quality alloy and ABS materials, this toy car is heavy-duty and durable. The rubber tires have a solid structure for added sturdiness, ensuring it will withstand the test of time.</p></li><li><p>HIGH-QUALITY ALLOY: Crafted from high-quality zinc alloy material, this car model is resistant to damage and scratches. It is coated with non-toxic, water-based paint that is free from harmful substances like formaldehyde, ensuring safe play.</p></li><li><p>COLLECTIBLE PIECE: This authentic car model is not only a fantastic toy for kids but also a valuable addition to any car model collection. The precise detailing and premium finishing touches make it a must-have piece for display in any toy car collection.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 2699, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a174527e-bad2-41f1-b521-4d6f87789c85.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 3999}', '2026-03-25 08:07:11.789628+00', '2026-03-25 08:07:11.789628+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a174527e-bad2-41f1-b521-4d6f87789c85.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/16a81f1f-25bd-4698-9ea5-24c124101315.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c8a4c792-11d6-4134-9406-0523165629b2.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/110d9d13-7069-47ef-a9b9-87fdfeb6754a.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'The Land Rover Defender, featuring an original miniature car look. It includes a 2-wheel drive, and doors can be opened.', 'https://youtu.be/mzypaCcmmJQ', '[-0.01170048,0.006240105,0.027646076,-0.011078008,0.02