	('prod_04960e5d-7c2e-4e61-ba7d-ce4a4003fa2a', '24g-rc-metal-jeep-toy-car-with-smoke-effect-lights-and-opening-doors-rechargeable-4x4-remote-control-suv-for-kids', '2.4G RC Metal Jeep Toy Car with Smoke Effect, Lights & Opening Doors – Rechargeable 4x4 Remote Control SUV for Kids', '<p>Bring home the excitement of driving with this premium 2.4G RC Metal Jeep Toy Car. Designed with a realistic 4x4 SUV look, this remote control car features a strong fully metal body for durability and a stylish finish. The car comes with all doors that open, making it more interactive and fun for kids.</p><p></p><p>This RC Jeep includes bright front lights, smooth forward, backward, left and right movement, and soft rubber tyres for better grip on different surfaces. The special smoke effect adds a realistic driving experience and makes playtime even more exciting. It also includes an easy on/off switch and a user-friendly remote control.</p><p></p><p>The car comes with a rechargeable battery and charging cable, so kids can enjoy longer play sessions without the need for frequent battery changes. Perfect for children aged 3 years and above, this RC Jeep toy is an ideal gift for birthdays, return gifts and special occasions.</p>', 1949, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/24b19b72-915c-4568-83ef-1b603cafa760.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2899}', '2026-04-03 12:13:35.761025+00', '2026-04-03 12:13:35.761025+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/24b19b72-915c-4568-83ef-1b603cafa760.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/da989cb7-588d-4052-bbc1-b4cd45d1db5e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ad0c85c7-981b-4eb7-9df4-d075d41b2862.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/aae24a74-a824-448e-b53c-01d0eda72aa7.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/91f96c1f-80f2-456d-8202-7ebede1924ec.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/00ff6d85-7e77-4e10-a2af-6c34517dd3d8.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/56b8