	('prod_7948f31f-2583-4837-a846-32b4d448ee90', 'toyota-toy-car-fj-land-cruiser', 'Toyota Toy Car Fj Land Cruiser', '<ul><li><p>➽ DUWOL 1:24 Toyota Fj Land Cruiser Toy Car Size: 1/24 scale toyota Fj land cruiser Toy Car metal car die cast car model car with display base, Product size: 21CM * 9CM * 10CM.</p></li><li><p>➽ Function Of Model Car: Pull back model car, engine sound and light. Press the two wheels of the front car to trigger the engine sound and lights, and open the door to trigger the lights of the front and rear lights. Place the car on the ground, hold down the car body and pull it back, the model car will drive forward about 10 meters; Simulation interior, body frosted texture.</p></li><li><p>➽ Die Cast Material: Made of high-quality''s Metal body with plastic parts, rubber tires, detailed interior and exterior trim. These cars are durable, safe, non-toxic and lead-free toys. Metal car can move. You can trust the quality and use it safely without worrying about your child’s safety.</p></li></ul>', 1999, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/08c90bac-124a-419b-879e-01e7a238c636.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 2299}', '2025-12-28 10:59:21.649698+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:21.649698+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/toyota-toy-car-fj-land-cruiser/8dc66ab5-e563-40e9-8be5-f90cc62358ed.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/08c90bac-124a-419b-879e-01e7a238c636.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f99748c5-0b7e-4a1f-b913-d52c4a60f876.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7086f913-b31c-4fa2-9953-94b78b3c7189.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4bd20b2d-6f9b-4f54-a385-b3916c125a58.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.062603325,0.0020425445,-0.0018578557,0.0029058277,0.058216598,-0.05700479,0.033972275,0.012407457,-0.0020557493,-0.010077883,0.010391024,0.01567272,0.026325915,0.009336218,0.07141963,0.0145799415,0.061521586,0.022564901,-0.011615933,-0.039550588,0.09808319,0.04