	('prod_c1a5d2d7-1535-4717-b138-44188e10d095', 'rolls-royce-phantom-diecast-car-model-metal-pull-back-toy-car-with-openable-doors-sound-light-toys', 'Rolls Royce Phantom Diecast Car Model | Metal Pull Back Toy Car with Openable Doors, Sound & Light Toys', '<ul><li><p>Premium Diecast Rolls-Royce Phantom Model – Made from high-quality metal, this 1:32 scale collectible car perfectly captures the elegance and luxury of the iconic Rolls-Royce Phantom.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Realistic Pull-Back Action – Easy-to-use pull-back mechanism for smooth racing and interactive play, perfect for kids, boys, girls, and collectors.</p></li><li><p>Openable Doors &amp; Detailed Design – Features functional doors, realistic interiors, and precise exterior detailing for an authentic supercar collectible experience.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Lights &amp; Sound Effects – Comes with bright lights and engine sound effects, adding a fun and realistic playtime experience for children and enthusiasts alike.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>Perfect Gift for Any Occasion – Ideal as a birthday gift, holiday gift, or collectible car for kids and adults, combining playtime fun with display-worthy luxury car collectible appeal.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 2599, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/424e5cf2-94a6-4da1-802b-ce7f4ca7a7d4.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 3999}', '2026-03-25 08:20:24.012723+00', '2026-03-25 08:20:24.012723+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/424e5cf2-94a6-4da1-802b-ce7f4ca7a7d4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/94b00270-3da8-44af-96ad-d1856f6d3f14.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/41e206e1-a37b-4949-9f74-b49bfc47f621.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/157bb8f1-d5fb-4e9c-aab5-6039ba0be5ab.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d0bec0e1-73f3-4dd7-9670-f2f88726393a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4f772d64-1df4-4e96-8895-56dd040b9fb1.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Pr