	('prod_cf428509-3ac5-4b41-a8af-39b0fd34e20c', 'g-patton-die-cast-off-road-suv-toy-car-with-light-sound-openable-doors-hood', 'G Patton Die-Cast Off-Road SUV Toy Car with Light & Sound, Openable Doors & Hood', '<p>Experience power and style with this premium G Patton die-cast off-road SUV toy car, designed with a bold military-inspired look and high-quality alloy body. This model features openable doors, hood, and trunk, along with detailed interiors and transparent PC material windows for a realistic finish.</p><p>Equipped with working front and rear lights and sound effects, this toy car brings an interactive experience to playtime. The pull-back action ensures smooth and fast movement, while durable rubber tires provide strong grip for off-road style play.</p><p>Perfect for kids, gifting, and collectors, this rugged SUV model combines durability, premium design, and realistic detailing—making it a standout addition to any toy car collection.</p>', 1199, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a54b1767-3368-4baf-b915-8494cb3d34c3.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1999}', '2026-03-25 08:57:12.364724+00', '2026-03-25 08:57:12.364724+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_1a985543-7b4d-4da3-8fb6-b52afcdc234c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a54b1767-3368-4baf-b915-8494cb3d34c3.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/78e936c5-9ecf-4320-9ddb-b9216f0c92c9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/538bbf31-292a-485e-b9b1-ad334a9d703d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2f0b0e97-3056-4d0e-83df-26143b6e5187.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/f130fd5a-2b45-462f-a803-dfdd7a90dd07.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a158eaa8-2148-44d4-8f92-5316634c8098.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Heavy-duty die-cast G Patton SUV toy car with openable doors, hood & trunk, plus light and sound effects.,
