	('prod_c7958644-de63-4e80-8033-7bd5f2154364', 'small-stunt-car-toy', 'Small Stunt Car Toy', '<ul><li><p>RC STUNT CAR: This cool racing car can do all sorts of tricks. It can go forward, backward, left and right easily. It can even drive on its sides and spin around in a full circle (360°). When it''s moving fast, it can spin like a tornado and dance around. It can also walk upright at a 90-degree angle and do cool wheel spins and rolls in the front.</p></li><li><p>Powerful RC Car: Equipped with 2 powerful electric motors, anti-crash durable rubber tires, shock absorption, strong grip, and anti-skid. This toy car has strong grip and flexible turning function; make it easy to pass obstacles. RC car fits for indoor and outdoor like sandy beach, wetlands, grasslands, playground etc.</p><ul><li><p>Endless Fun for Kids: One click to start playing, it’s so simple and easy to operate as well as double-sided driving, repeated jumping, random drift and special effects turning, this toy car for kids will bring endless fun to children.</p></li></ul></li></ul>', 399, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-stunt-car-toy/6c6cc572-9033-4129-b15b-7da9232123a5.png', 18, '{"compare_at_price": 550}', '2025-12-28 10:59:20.297353+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:20.297353+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-stunt-car-toy/6c6cc572-9033-4129-b15b-7da9232123a5.png', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-stunt-car-toy/6c6cc572-9033-4129-b15b-7da9232123a5.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-stunt-car-toy/fb86c5c1-3de9-48fc-af30-fcf7af6af2a7.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-stunt-car-toy/3e77b780-0c66-407e-a2cc-e18070dbfa8b.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-stunt-car-toy/3cc2d7b4-2911-4b14-9b1b-7943d35f2ff5.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-stunt-car-toy/073801dd-0fe6-4d93-bada-11cc4cd78029.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/small-stunt-car-toy/16611cbf-6bcd-44be-983f-8339