	('prod_28f10809-d134-4a46-881c-2f87b1018c18', 'high-speed-rc-drift-car-toy-with-remote-control-led-lights-dual-speed-racing-car-for-kids', 'High Speed RC Drift Car Toy with Remote Control | LED Lights | Dual Speed Racing Car for Kids', '<p>Bring home the ultimate racing experience with this <strong>High Speed RC Drift Car Toy</strong>, designed for thrilling performance and smooth drifting action. This <strong>remote control car for kids</strong> comes with an easy-to-use controller that allows precise movements including forward, reverse, and left-right turns.</p><p></p><p>Equipped with <strong>dual speed mode</strong>, this <strong>RC racing car</strong> delivers exciting speed up to 10 km/h, making it perfect for both beginners and advanced users. The built-in <strong>LED lights</strong> add a stylish look and enhance playtime, especially in low-light conditions.</p><p></p><p>The <strong>drift tyres</strong> ensure smooth sliding and controlled drifting, giving a real racing feel. Made from durable materials, this <strong>electric toy car</strong> is designed for long-lasting fun and safety.</p><p></p><ul><li><p>🚗 High Speed RC Drift Car (Up to 10 km/h)</p></li><li><p>🎮 Easy Remote Control (Forward/Reverse/Turn)</p></li><li><p>💡 Stylish LED Lights</p></li><li><p>⚡ Dual Speed Mode for Better Control</p></li><li><p>🛞 Smooth Drift Tyres for Real Racing Experience</p></li><li><p>👦 Perfect Gift Toy for Kids</p></li></ul><p></p>', 2799, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dcdfdc6f-ca93-47d6-99b4-53a2274f0acf.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 3499}', '2026-03-25 09:02:40.460274+00', '2026-03-25 09:02:40.460274+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dcdfdc6f-ca93-47d6-99b4-53a2274f0acf.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/7a4942d3-7501-4b53-adae-9f246699f59e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6439570b-1518-4d32-899a-49100f90b221.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/1525