	('prod_0f0132ea-2bf7-4b48-8557-2c5a6a46720f', 'racing-sport-mood-car', 'Racing Sport Mood Car', '<p>Equipped with rechargeable battery (Included) for the car. Can be used about 25 minutes after fully charged batteries. Car speed can reach up to 3-4 mph for an exciting driving experience. The bright led headlights will glow with forward motion. It is out of this world when the dazzling headlights glow in the dark. Wheels are made of high quality rubber to prevent slipping. It is also fitted with rubber tires with rims. Non-toxic ABS plastic and a glossy exterior. Smooth flexible wheels with clear patterns and independent suspension system can reduce the friction between the tires and floor and bring the most active suspension, so it can freely run into around the house. Frequency is the updated new feature for this RC car, which provides stable and wider control range for the play, provides a range of up to 80ft &amp; allows you to race at a speed up to 4mph. Included rechargeable Batteries for the car and require Batteries for the remote controller. This Branded Kid Car can move in every direction with the help of a remote, you can move it Forward, Backward, Left and Right you choose to. Best Birthday Gift and Christmas Gift.</p>', 1649, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9c477899-0397-4073-9769-4a64947b3602.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 2099}', '2025-12-28 10:59:18.143801+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:18.143801+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/racing-sport-mood-car/7d63ed8e-2031-4509-b942-c6bf426020f8.png', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9c477899-0397-4073-9769-4a64947b3602.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dd07c02e-d923-4c80-ac71-9ca2778fc738.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/65338d35-f536-4a57-9761-40281a87a41d.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0d9c07d7-8afc-4414-828c-1634ad69109e.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[-0.0019365292,-0.008447272,-0.010205762,-0.0095