	('prod_b78660de-c711-45b2-bde9-e4f2dac70a73', 'trolley-kitchen-set', 'Trolley Kitchen Set', '<ul><li><p>Realistic Looking: Let your kids cook up imaginary feast for the whole family with the Kitchen Playset. The young chefs in your life will sure love this almost realistic kitchen with included kitchen accessories.</p></li><li><p>Pretend as Cooks&nbsp; &amp; Chefs: Interactive Little Chef Kids Kitchen Play Set with Light &amp; Sound. Your kids will love to pretend as chef. While real kitchen is dangerous for kids to play.</p></li><li><p>Durable carry Case: This Kitchen kit set comes with a durable Kitchen carry case, all the Kitchen items can be easily stored. It is suitable for outdoor playing and indoor playing.</p></li><li><p>Compact &amp; Safe: There’s a handle on the side of the kit so that you can lift it, and it’s also a trolley with wheels that you can pull, so kids can easily take it anywhere .Comes In A Compact design</p></li><li><p>Battery operated product</p></li></ul>', 1099, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4539ac09-3508-47fd-96c1-1b20defd4032.jpeg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 1350}', '2025-12-28 10:59:20.963884+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:20.963884+00', 'cat_185bd7d1-cf69-4bde-ad84-d073ce5b8915', 'col_64ba526c-0c27-4be8-bea3-3fbc9d30ffc2', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/trolley-kitchen-set/afb15539-2b42-4f41-8d37-11af5a1ffc7d.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4539ac09-3508-47fd-96c1-1b20defd4032.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/56c613a3-2191-4d06-9d12-e98c1dfd4616.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/77b5332b-7692-4f1a-9c4e-bc620a7fc783.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/201eb5bc-55d8-4ba7-8465-f3fac8390714.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, '', '', '[0.023458602,-0.00012308543,0.007873571,0.02603764,0.05913708,-0.0023475229,0.059436776,0.014925194,-0.043695275,0.030241298,-0.0110164955,0.01341846,0.004017186,-0.03168988,0.027247338,-0.0041873767,-0.051545855,0.02821752,-0.00838719,-0.0482319,0.00574266,0.011771953,0.014991804,0.0204351,-0.0205372