	('prod_b6d57d83-2e1b-4cc4-9e86-213f77304d5f', 'bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke', 'Bluetooth Speaker with Mic Karaoke', '<p>This professional bluetooth karaoke speaker equipped with the best acoustic speaker for high volume and quality sound.Rechargeable battery provide 5-6 hours continuous use to keep your party going.<br>The karaoke machine and bluetooth karaoke microphone designed with 5 different voice change effects.Provide endless fun to your kids.Just enjoy your happy out with singing music.<br>The bluetooth kids microphone karaoke machine has fun LED light effects and comes in a few different colors fora fun party atmosphere no matter where you are.Top 2024 christmas gifts for kids.</p><p>Compact and easy to carry, perfect for kids to take anywhere—whether it’s a party, sleepover, or family gathering.<br>Seamlessly connects with smartphones, tablets, and other Bluetooth-enabled devices, so kids can sing along to their favorite songs.</p>', 499, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke/dae5bd24-effd-403c-b452-120591a7273e.jpg', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 699}', '2025-12-28 10:59:06.822313+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:06.822313+00', 'cat_e8d304ee-124d-409f-b02f-9a0b6824b9de', 'col_2c27fef3-dfee-42ef-8d1f-d08d41a2aad7', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke/dae5bd24-effd-403c-b452-120591a7273e.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke/dae5bd24-effd-403c-b452-120591a7273e.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke/d09ae441-a5f9-4b54-b93d-c4a024cbf0d9.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke/54e47734-ce54-455c-89ab-7ca1aa1be8ea.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke/bf9b99d5-9f5f-45d6-adc1-74e57e2c1c3f.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke/31dc3af6-b0c1-4ce6-9030-37d09f33ac68.jpg,https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/bluetooth-speaker-with-mic-karaoke/fa7d93a2-2