	('prod_aa10ba2b-b6d6-42d5-8d2e-510bb5c7060f', 'kids-makeup-set-trolley-suitcase-3year-beauty-play-kit-with-mirror-hair-dryer-and-accessories', 'Kids Makeup Set Trolley Suitcase – 3+Year Beauty Play Kit with Mirror, Hair Dryer & Accessories', '<p>Let your little one explore creativity and imagination with this adorable Kids Makeup Set Trolley Suitcase! Designed for children aged 3+, this fun beauty play kit includes a variety of accessories like a mirror, toy hair dryer, lipstick, nail polish, rings, brush, and more.</p><p>The stylish trolley suitcase comes with an attachable handle and smooth wheels, making it easy to carry anywhere. Kids can enjoy pretend play while learning basic grooming habits and enhancing their creativity, social skills, and confidence.</p><p>All items are made from safe, non-toxic materials with smooth edges, ensuring a safe play experience. The compact design also helps keep everything organized in one place after playtime.</p><p></p><p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Complete makeup toy set with trolley suitcase</p></li><li><p>Includes mirror, hair dryer, lipstick, nail polish &amp; more</p></li><li><p>Lightweight and travel-friendly design</p></li><li><p>Encourages creative and imaginative play</p></li><li><p>Safe, smooth &amp; child-friendly materials</p></li><li><p>Easy storage and carry with handle &amp; wheels</p></li><li><p>Ideal for kids aged 3+</p></li></ul><p></p>', 299, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4ceea790-d7f0-4a64-a0d3-f4322b6d945c.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 699}', '2026-04-11 10:28:24.037393+00', '2026-04-11 10:28:24.037393+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_151b58e4-30fe-431c-8a44-bd622c4c1c6e', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/4ceea790-d7f0-4a64-a0d3-f4322b6d945c.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/aef1a755-f769-49a6-843b-dbc51323819a.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/779f8178-2f51-4e79-8b70-ae7a9cbcebe1.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/2c1c1c59-f933-42a0-8d