	('prod_a894993c-0da8-4773-98e9-37dbdd454b05', '1-24-audi-a8-die-cast-model-car', '1:24 Audi A8 Die-Cast Model Car', '<ul><li><p>➤ Realistic Die-Cast Audi A8 Design – This 1:24 scale model replicates the sleek and premium look of the iconic Audi A8 sedan. Detailed headlights, rims, and logo branding offer authenticity for collectors and young auto lovers.</p></li><li><p>➤ Durable Alloy Metal Body – Made with high-quality die-cast alloy and durable plastic parts, the Audi A8 model car is built to last. The robust construction ensures long-term play and display for kids and collectors alike.</p></li><li><p>➤ Interactive Light &amp; Sound Features – Designed to enhance playtime fun, the car includes built-in lights and realistic engine sounds. Simply press down to activate, adding excitement for imaginative play and display setups.</p></li><li><p>➤ Openable Doors &amp; Pull Back Action – Both front doors can be opened manually to reveal a detailed interior. Equipped with pull-back function, just pull it backward and release for a smooth, self-propelled zoom forward.</p></li><li><p>➤ Ideal Gift for Kids &amp; Collectors – Whether for birthdays, holidays, or car model enthusiasts, this Audi A8 diecast car makes a thoughtful and impressive gift. Suitable for kids aged 3+ and hobbyists who love miniature collectibles.</p></li></ul>', 1799, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a84a2abd-7bf6-45a6-a599-222e2e5baf41.png', 20, '{"compare_at_price": 2199}', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.160864+00', '2025-12-28 10:59:02.160864+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_4d51f80f-e115-49f5-9990-8277b8b5a8b3', 'active', 'https://cdn.toycker.in/uploads/1-24-audi-a8-die-cast-model-car/17b6d1a3-dc24-43bc-9cfd-f0d2c990b98d.jpg', '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a84a2abd-7bf6-45a6-a599-222e2e5baf41.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/699c846c-8555-423c-b5b3-e5c50d55abc6.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/c0be85c8-c977-43ee-855f-7e6a4d218df1.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a2b42ad4-