	('prod_d06e3f62-8776-43dc-9de4-03719b1cfb2e', 'car-rivals-24ghz-remote-control-stunt-car-with-mist-spray-effect-rgb-led-lights-360-rotating-rubber-tyres', 'Car Rivals 2.4GHz Remote Control Stunt Car with Mist Spray Effect, RGB LED Lights & 360° Rotating Rubber Tyres', '<p>Experience the next level of racing with the <strong>Car Rivals RC Stunt Car!</strong> This isn''t just a remote-controlled car; it’s a high-performance stunt machine designed to thrill. With its unique <strong>Mist Spray</strong> feature and vibrant <strong>LED lighting</strong>, it turns every room into a futuristic racing track.</p><p></p><h3><strong>Key Features:</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Realistic Mist Spray:</strong> Equipped with a built-in water tank, this car emits a cool "smoke-like" mist from the rear at the push of a button, mimicking a real nitro-boost effect!</p></li><li><p><strong>360° Stunt Action:</strong> The high-grip <strong>Rubber Tyres</strong> allow for incredible 360-degree spins, flips, and high-speed drifting on various surfaces.</p></li><li><p><strong>Dazzling RGB Lights:</strong> Features built-in <strong>Colourful Lights</strong> that illuminate the car body and wheels, making it look spectacular during night-time play.</p></li><li><p><strong>Precision Remote Control:</strong> The easy-to-use controller features dedicated buttons for:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Forward/Backward &amp; Left/Right</strong> navigation.</p></li><li><p><strong>One-Key Spray Toggle</strong> for the mist effect.</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Durable &amp; Stylish:</strong> Made from high-quality, non-toxic ABS plastic with a sleek red and white finish, built to withstand bumps and crashes.</p></li><li><p></p></li></ul><h3><strong>What’s in the Box?</strong></h3><ul><li><p>1 x <strong>Car Rivals RC Stunt Car</strong></p></li><li><p>1 x <strong>Remote Controller</strong> (Batteries not included)</p></li><li><p>1 x <strong>Water Dropper</strong> (For filling the spray tank)</p></li><li><p>1 x <strong>charging cabel</strong> ( tyep c )</p></li></ul><p></p>', 599, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0eaf04dc-1f4e-42ab-a2c8-d7ba2eebb886.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 999}', '2026-03-27 12:15:55.043037+00', '2026-03-27 12:15:55.043037+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0eaf04dc-1f4e-42ab-a2c8-d7ba2eebb886.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/fa2854f6-dd36-4165-a520-6402a4428773.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3247da0b-72a0-4ff8-948b-02a1f94747d6.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/70c9a018-2c19-4fae-ba93-73734fab96de.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/45f43ffd-febc-4ba3-9374-25c090beef06.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/8b877c20-0466-4630-83de-a74c0ca014b9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/030f7aee-7629-4cc1-8bea-fd9cd4dc84c4.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/260461a2-1bd2-4561-8dc0-ed3bd65ce18c.jpeg}', 'inr', NULL, 'Experience the next level of racing with the Car Rivals RC Stunt Car! This isn''t just a remote-controlled car; it’s a high-performance stunt machine designed to thrill. With its unique Mist Spray feature and vibrant LED lighting, it turns every room into a futuristic racing track.', 'https://youtu.be/cKrMJ2wzpag', '[0.02474542,-0.023240725,0.014469215,0.0010917805,0.027174618,0.022841683,0.06346336,0.035021283,0.0018408959,-0.0038813965,-0.011924121,0.017193634,-0.065526225,-0.010848309,0.075576484,0.0021634384,0.031452127,0.02536549,-0.028312368,-0.031014867,-0.016686779,-0.014871019,0.011643478,0.07723014,-0.007867025,0.010125366,0.018049994,0.020350825,-0.0077164886,0.0048854393,0.0073373998,0.007528384,-0.00895156,0.025407083,-0.11980689,-0.047754463,-0.061367173,0.016584601,0.01659436,0.029633472,-0.03459697,0.020440074,0.03003782,-0.01012447,0.01772282,-0.14302988,0.0073458934,-0.008589862,-0.019296797,-0.03830169,0.0183757,0.030616075,-0.04151514,0.03174207,-0.038480688,-0.068969,-0.027526585,-0.0063610277,0.025002