	('prod_8fe87354-546b-47e9-809f-40679d2fa592', 'luxury-sweet-shopping-battery-operated-plastic-ice-cream-trolley-pretend-role-play-educational-toy-set-led-music-for-kids', 'Luxury Sweet Shopping Battery Operated Plastic Ice Cream Trolley Pretend Role Play Educational Toy Set, LED, Music for Kids', '<ul><li><p>Multifunctional Toy Kitchen Sets: Kitchen Sets Toys includes toy sink, cooking playset with mini pot and pan, with Realistic Lights &amp; Sounds, Simulation of Spray, microwave oven and other accessories. Has everything children need to get their toy kitchen up and running for which add to the fun of the game and perfectly simulate the real Kitchen Toys.(requires 3 AA batteries not included）</p></li><li><p>Fun and Educational Electronic Kitchen Toy: The Kitchen Playset with light and music, along with the cooking sound and realistic light, press the switch, the induction cooker will emit simulated sounds and lights, Steam effect with simulated spray, it can increase the realistic cooking effect when children are playing. Your little ones can learn to identify the colors and names of food toy by playing the matching food game.</p></li><li><p>Water Circulation System: The kitchen toy set has a faucet with a water circulation system, Water will flow out when you press the faucet. Children can wash vegetables, fruits, tableware and other accessories in the sink. Your children can store all the kitchen accessories after playing, it will develop the habit of organizing things and keeps the room tidy, improve children''s hands-on ability and sense of responsibility.</p></li><li><p>Mini Blackboard &amp; Safe Quality: The kitchen playset made of durable plastic that will withstand endless hours of delightful play. comes with 1 Chalk Eraser and 2 Chalk Sticks, which is convenient for you and your children to record some nouns or draw graphics. Safe, nontoxic kids’ kitchen toy set is safe for kids ages 3 years Plus.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 599, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/prod