	('prod_de34e5bf-52d9-4d3f-8b0b-a82ee246b973', 'baby-school-bus-xylophone-toy-for-toddlers-1-3-baby-musical-bus-toys-for-1-year-old-girl-shape-sorting-toys-knocking-xylophone-educational-musical-instruments', 'Baby School Bus Xylophone Toy for Toddlers 1-3, Baby Musical Bus Toys for 1 Year Old Girl, Shape Sorting Toys Knocking Xylophone Educational Musical Instruments', '<ul><li><p>Interactive Learning Experience: This musical bus combines a xylophone, shape sorter, and push &amp; go vehicle, providing endless hours of educational fun for your toddler.</p></li><li><p>Educational Benefits: Enhance your child''s cognitive development, fine motor skills, and sense of rhythm. The xylophone introduces musical concepts while the shape sorter improves hand-eye coordination and shape recognition.</p></li><li><p>Vibrant and Engaging: With bright colors and a friendly animated face, this toy is designed to captivate and entertain, making learning enjoyable. Durable and Safe: Crafted from high-quality, non-toxic materials, ensuring a safe playtime experience for your little one.</p></li><li><p>Perfect Size for Little Hands: Easy to grasp and play with, this toy is designed with your child''s comfort in mind. Push &amp; Go Feature: Simply push the bus forward, and watch it zoom across the floor, encouraging active play and exploration.</p></li><li><p>Abacus for Added Fun: The included abacus on the roof introduces early counting skills, making this toy a comprehensive educational tool. Ideal Gift for Toddlers: Perfect for birthdays, holidays, or just because, this multifunctional bus toy is sure to become a favorite in any toddler''s toy collection.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 549, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/44116efa-e117-4a84-b4d6-d85ad3bad5ba.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1299}', '2026-04-20 12:30:01.3234+00', '2026-04-20 12:30:01.3234+00', 'cat_94b4dcf4-745a-4430-a23c-e10f79594fa6', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/prod