	('prod_f3b6146b-2fbd-4627-bf67-b9bfb140eeb8', 'wild-republic-paws-laying-jumbo-yellow-lab-babies', 'Dog- Laying Jumbo Yellow LAB & Babies', '<p><strong>The Ultimate Snuggle Buddy</strong> Experience the love of a canine family with the Wild Republic Mom &amp; Baby Golden Retriever set. This beautifully crafted plush set includes a large, gentle mother dog resting on a soft white cushion, accompanied by two miniature puppies. Whether it''s for a gift or for your own little one, this set brings warmth and comfort to any room.</p><p></p><p><strong>Handmade Quality &amp; Premium Comfort</strong> Every piece in this collection is made with "Handmade Quality," ensuring that the fur is super soft to the touch and the stitching is durable for years of play. We use only premium materials to ensure the plush remains huggable and retains its shape.</p><p></p><p><strong>Designed for Real Life</strong> We know that well-loved toys can get messy. That’s why this set is designed to be <strong>Machine Washable</strong>, making it easy for parents to keep the puppies clean and fresh.</p><p></p><p><strong>Specifications &amp; Safety:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li><p><strong>Generous Dimensions:</strong> The set measures approximately <strong>78 cm in length</strong> and <strong>42 cm in height</strong>, making it a significant and impressive gift.</p></li><li><p><strong>Safety First:</strong> Fully safety tested to meet high standards, making it suitable for infants and toddlers.</p></li><li><p><strong>Multi-Piece Set:</strong> Includes the large mother dog and two detachable baby puppies for interactive play.</p></li><li><p></p></li></ul><p><strong>Package Includes:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li><p>1 x Large Mom Golden Retriever</p></li><li><p>2 x Baby Golden Retriever Puppies</p></li></ul><p></p>', 3099, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6c8aaa01-0d2b-4bbb-9170-0155e6ce2d82.jpeg', 0, '{"compare_at_price": 3299}', '2026-01-28 05:03:09.315941+00', '2026-01-28 05:03:09.315941+00', NULL, 'co