	('prod_67233152-e356-4cfa-972a-bffad1583cd4', 'infrared-gun-shooting-rollover-interactive-set-multiplayer-battle-toy-car-remote-control-rc-car-indoor-use', 'Infrared Gun Shooting Rollover Interactive Set Multiplayer Battle Toy Car Remote Control Rc Car Indoor Use', '<ul><li><p>2.4G Stable Remote Control Advanced 2.4GHz anti-interference technology allows multiple cars to race together without signal disruption. Smooth four-way control (forward/backward/left/right) ensures fast response and precise handling.</p></li><li><p></p></li><li><p>1. Exciting 2-Player Battle Action Comes with two remote control cars &amp; dual remotes for real head-to-head racing and shooting competition. Perfect multiplayer fun for siblings &amp; friends.</p></li><li><p>2. Shoot &amp; Knock-Down Game Feature Infrared battle system lets players shoot opponent’s car and score hits. Car stops temporarily when hit – realistic knock-down action for thrilling gameplay.</p></li><li><p>3. Time-Bound Dodge &amp; Target Mode Fast-paced timed battle mode increases excitement. Players must dodge shots and strategically aim to win.</p></li><li><p>4. Stable Remote Control Performance Responsive remote control system ensures smooth driving, quick turns and accurate targeting.</p></li><li><p>5. Realistic Lights &amp; Sound Effects Built-in sound effects and flashing lights enhance the interactive gaming experience.</p></li><li><p>6. Encourages Strategy &amp; Coordination Improves reflexes, hand-eye coordination, focus and competitive play skills in kids.</p></li><li><p>7. Perfect Gift for Kids Great birthday gift for boys &amp; girls 5+ years. Ideal indoor game toy for parties, playdates and family fun.</p></li></ul><p></p>', 3299, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/00843511-898d-475a-800c-9b3e60537727.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 4699}', '2026-04-18 12:25:22.584365+00', '2026-04-18 12:25:22.584365+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL