	('prod_8995e9f5-657b-41e5-9a18-fbbf75ffcc01', 'mini-metal-suv-toy-car-scorpio-style-pull-back-action-openable-doors-premium-die-cast-model-for-kids', 'Mini Metal SUV Toy Car (Scorpio Style) – Pull Back Action, Openable Doors, Premium Die-Cast Model for Kids', '<p>Bring home this stylish and powerful-looking mini metal SUV toy car, inspired by a bold Scorpio-style design. Made with high-quality die-cast metal, this toy offers durability along with a premium finish that feels realistic and attractive. It features a smooth pull-back action—just pull it back and watch it zoom forward with speed, making playtime more fun and engaging.</p><p>The car also comes with openable doors, adding an extra interactive element for kids. Its compact size makes it easy to carry and perfect for both indoor and outdoor play. The rubber tires provide better grip and smooth movement on different surfaces.</p><p>Available in multiple attractive colors like black, white, red, and yellow, this toy is ideal for kids, gifting, or even as a collectible display piece for car lovers. A perfect combination of style, strength, and fun!</p>', 349, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/115596fc-189f-4364-9b62-30fa09287932.png', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 649}', '2026-04-24 12:21:38.465143+00', '2026-04-24 12:21:38.465143+00', NULL, 'col_8174576c-6bdf-4212-9448-708c00935aee', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/115596fc-189f-4364-9b62-30fa09287932.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/3f91322a-5638-46c2-9176-549ceee1189d.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/dd718b67-6c42-4df9-9cd6-6d8af65d54e1.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9062e4e8-b1df-4412-86e2-6e11f3cccd5d.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/35b3e217-9ccf-41a6-9ae6-0edb52f75643.png,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/9bd7c734-a49d-47ed-bf82-df1061781acf.png}', 'inr', NULL, 'Premium mini metal SUV toy car with pull-back action and openable doors. Strong build, realistic design, and smooth rubber tires make it perfect for kids and collectors.