	('prod_4daab58f-5dd3-4d73-a951-f02222abb49e', '4wd-rc-drift-racing-car-with-smoke-effect-led-lights-and-dual-tires', '4WD RC Drift Racing Car with Smoke Effect, LED Lights & Dual Tires', '<p>Experience thrilling racing action with this advanced 4WD RC Drift Racing Car. Designed for high performance, it features a realistic smoke effect that simulates real drifting, making playtime more exciting and immersive. The powerful motor ensures smooth speed control, while the responsive remote lets kids easily perform sharp turns and drifts.</p><p>This RC car comes with dual tire options—racing tires for speed and drift tires for smooth sliding—allowing you to switch based on terrain and play style. Built with durable materials and stylish LED lights, it delivers both performance and visual appeal.</p><p>The package includes everything you need: the RC car, remote controller, rechargeable battery, charging cable, and extra tires for customization. Ideal for indoor and outdoor play, this toy enhances hand-eye coordination and provides endless entertainment for kids and hobby lovers alike.<br><br>Inside the box: 1 spray injector, 4 extra tires, and 4 roadblock props are included.</p>', 1799, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/588dbe64-c42a-48cc-ac89-90fb0aebf92e.jpeg', 60, '{"compare_at_price": 3399}', '2026-04-07 12:37:38.535316+00', '2026-04-07 12:37:38.535316+00', 'cat_6441a32d-69cc-448f-97bc-48f3bd11a29b', 'col_a0046b19-1ea9-44b4-a49d-9d8e0314e99c', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/588dbe64-c42a-48cc-ac89-90fb0aebf92e.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a3e8d768-2bc5-43d8-b59d-bc5bcde06811.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/ebc5c87d-83cd-44a5-8be3-8d344246f95c.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0196d15d-f402-4bb1-8338-95e990937656.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/108ca8f4-3d78-405b-a31f-e4a52d21f862.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/0ee6b4e2-828e-463f-ac33-3a2346cd903f.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/eb8e20dc-4700-458a-a0b0-baa550cb5186.png