	('prod_10de580b-4ec2-4eb5-b606-bd2e964a0a07', 'small-farmer-tractor-toy-for-kids-monster-wheel-push-play-vehicle-strong-farm-style-tractor-design-made-with-safe-abs-plastics', 'Small Farmer Tractor Toy for Kids | Monster Wheel Push Play Vehicle | Strong Farm Style Tractor Design | Made with Safe ABS Plastics', '<p>Bring farming fun to your child’s playtime with this <strong>Small Farm Tractor Toy with LED Lights&nbsp;</strong>🚜✨. Designed especially for kids aged 3 and above, this toy features <strong>flashing LED wheels</strong> and <strong>built-in music</strong> that keeps children engaged and entertained for hours.</p><p></p><p>Made from high-quality, durable plastic, this tractor toy is safe and perfect for both <strong>indoor and outdoor play</strong>. Its bright colors and realistic design help improve <strong>imagination, motor skills, and creativity</strong> in kids.</p><p></p><p>Whether it''s a gift for birthdays or daily fun, this<strong>&nbsp;tractor toy for toddlers</strong> is a great choice for every little farmer!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li><p>Realistic farm tractor design</p></li><li><p>Flashing LED wheels</p></li><li><p>Suitable for kids 3+</p></li><li><p>Strong &amp; durable material</p></li><li><p>Attractive colors for kids</p></li></ul><p></p>', 649, 'https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a6e19bc6-bd4d-4099-813e-5e5e7530096d.jpeg', 50, '{"compare_at_price": 1999}', '2026-03-19 04:18:43.956561+00', '2026-03-19 04:18:43.956561+00', 'cat_e8d304ee-124d-409f-b02f-9a0b6824b9de', 'col_e5a76b8c-59ac-4ec2-881f-8f2472259122', 'active', NULL, '{https://cdn.toycker.in/products/a6e19bc6-bd4d-4099-813e-5e5e7530096d.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/152e6a73-838b-461a-bfe2-d7a79ff025e9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/97e52918-123e-446a-b379-39abd864f684.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/6a30a7cf-7858-4249-909f-c44c8bdd05c9.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/bcb2d0ec-994d-4e9e-878b-3d5900e303cc.jpeg,https://cdn.toycker.in/products/d1d47d8d-8616-40ff-baf2-5